        "descriptionHTML": "<div class=\"tab-pane active\" id=\"tab-description\">\n<div class=\"detail-tab-desc detail-content-wrap\">\n<p>**Buy CBD Tincture 2000MG online in Canada at Mohawk Medibles**, your trusted Indigenous-owned cannabis dispensary. Shop this premium high-potency CBD isolate tincture and enjoy fast Canada-wide shipping with same-day processing. Order now for discreet delivery of this traditionally-used wellness product, expertly crafted with MCT oil for optimal absorption. Perfect for those seeking natural support for chronic discomfort without the psychoactive effects of THC.</p>\n<p>–</p>\n<h2>💡 Usage Guide</h2>\n<h3>Recommended Dosage</h3>\n<ul>\n<li><strong>Beginners:</strong> Start with 0.25ml-0.5ml (approximately 8-16mg CBD) once daily. Place under tongue and hold for 60-90 seconds before swallowing.</li>\n<li><strong>Regular Users:</strong> 0.5ml-1ml (16-33mg CBD) twice daily, morning and evening.</li>\n<li><strong>Chronic Discomfort:</strong> 1ml-1.5ml (33-50mg CBD) 2-3 times daily. Consult with a healthcare provider for personalized guidance on higher doses.</li>\n</ul>\n<h3>How to Use</h3>\n<ul>\n<li><strong>Sublingual Application:</strong> Use the 1ml dropper to measure your dose. Place drops under your tongue and hold for 60-90 seconds before swallowing for maximum absorption.</li>\n<li><strong>With Food:</strong> Can be taken with or without food. Some users find taking with a small meal improves consistency of effects.</li>\n<li><strong>Consistency is Key:</strong> CBD works best with regular daily use. Allow 1-2 weeks of consistent dosing to experience full benefits.</li>\n</ul>\n<h3>Onset &amp; Duration</h3>\n<ul>\n<li><strong>Onset:</strong> 15-45 minutes when taken sublingually</li>\n<li><strong>Peak Effects:</strong> 1-2 hours after consumption</li>\n<li><strong>Duration:</strong> 4-6 hours of support</li>\n</ul>\n<h3>Best Use Cases</h3>\n<p>Ideal for daily wellness support and managing chronic discomfort associated with conditions like bursitis, rheumatoid arthritis, sciatica, and hip dysplasia. The MCT oil base provides a neutral taste without the sweetness of glycerin-based tinctures. Non-psychoactive formula is safe for daytime use and won’t interfere with work or daily activities. The 60ml bottle with 1ml dropper provides approximately 60 days of use at standard dosing.</p>\n<p><strong>Important:</strong> This product is not intended to diagnose, treat, cure, or prevent any disease. Consult with your healthcare provider before use, especially if you are pregnant, nursing, taking medications, or have a medical condition.</p>\n<h2>❓ Frequently Asked Questions</h2>\n<h3>Is this CBD Tincture 2000MG THC-free?</h3>\n<p><strong>A:</strong> Yes, this is a CBD isolate tincture containing 0% THC. You’ll experience the potential wellness benefits of CBD without any psychoactive effects or intoxication. It’s safe for daily use and won’t cause a “high.”</p>\n<h3>Will this CBD tincture make me feel high?</h3>\n<p><strong>A:</strong> No, CBD is non-psychoactive and will not produce intoxication or impairment. Users report feeling more comfortable and relaxed, but you’ll remain clear-headed and functional. It’s safe to use before work or daily activities.</p>\n<h3>How much CBD should I take for chronic pain?</h3>\n<p><strong>A:</strong> Start with 0.5ml (approximately 16mg CBD) twice daily and gradually increase over 1-2 weeks until you find your optimal dose. Many users with chronic conditions find relief at 33-50mg daily, but individual needs vary. The included 1ml dropper makes precise dosing easy. Consult your healthcare provider for personalized recommendations.</p>\n<h3>What’s the difference between MCT oil and glycerin-based tinctures?</h3>\n<p><strong>A:</strong> MCT (medium-chain triglyceride) oil provides a neutral, non-sweet taste compared to glycerin’s sweetness. MCT oil also offers superior absorption and is preferred by those avoiding sugar or sweet flavours. This makes it ideal for users who want pure CBD benefits without added taste.</p>\n<h3>How long does the 2000mg bottle last?</h3>\n<p><strong>A:</strong> With the recommended dosage of 1ml daily, this 60ml bottle provides approximately 60 days of use (about 33mg CBD per day). If you use less, it will last longer. The dropper is marked at 1ml for easy, consistent dosing.</p>\n<h3>Can I buy this CBD tincture online and have it shipped across Canada?</h3>\n<p><strong>A:</strong> Yes! Mohawk Medibles ships this CBD Tincture 2000MG across Canada with fast, discreet delivery. Orders placed before 2 PM EST are processed the same day. All packages arrive in plain, unmarked packaging to ensure your privacy.</p>\n<h3>How should I store my CBD tincture?</h3>\n<p><strong>A:</strong> Store in a cool, dark place away from direct sunlight and heat. Keep the bottle tightly sealed when not in use. Refrigeration is not necessary but can extend shelf life. Properly stored, your tincture will maintain potency for 12-18 months. Always keep out of reach of children and pets.</p>\n</div>\n</div>",
