        "descriptionHTML": "<div class=\"tab-pane active\" id=\"tab-description\">\n<div class=\"detail-tab-desc detail-content-wrap\">\n<h2 data-end=\"211\" data-start=\"158\"><strong data-end=\"209\" data-start=\"163\">Temple Hash – Premium Imported Temple Ball</strong></h2>\n<p data-end=\"273\" data-start=\"212\"><strong data-end=\"273\" data-start=\"212\">High THC • Hand-Rolled • Traditional Nepalese-Style Resin</strong></p>\n<hr/>\n<p data-end=\"930\" data-start=\"673\">Temple Hash is one of the most well-known and respected traditional concentrates in the cannabis world.<br data-end=\"779\" data-start=\"776\"/><strong data-end=\"809\" data-start=\"779\">Right from the first look,</strong> you’ll recognize its signature shape—dark, polished, sticky balls of resin, each packed with natural oils and trichomes.</p>\n<p data-end=\"1178\" data-start=\"932\"><strong data-end=\"953\" data-start=\"932\">When you open it,</strong> a deep, earthy aroma rises instantly, blending sweet spice, warm resin, and that unmistakable temple-style scent.<br data-end=\"1070\" data-start=\"1067\"/><strong data-end=\"1096\" data-start=\"1070\">As you break it apart,</strong> the inside reveals a soft, rich, and oily texture that melts smoothly under heat.</p>\n<p data-end=\"1422\" data-start=\"1180\"><strong data-end=\"1196\" data-start=\"1180\">Once smoked,</strong> Temple Hash offers a silky, flavorful pull—creamy, earthy, and aromatic, with no harshness at all.<br data-end=\"1298\" data-start=\"1295\"/><strong data-end=\"1331\" data-start=\"1298\">Soon after your first inhale,</strong> the high begins to wash over you: warm, heavy relaxation paired with a dreamy mental calm.</p>\n<p data-end=\"1644\" data-start=\"1424\">With <strong data-end=\"1443\" data-start=\"1429\">55–80% THC</strong>, Temple Hash is extremely potent.<br data-end=\"1480\" data-start=\"1477\"/><strong data-end=\"1506\" data-start=\"1480\">As the effects deepen,</strong> expect a powerful body melt, a meditative mental state, and long-lasting stress relief—perfect for nighttime use or deep unwind sessions.</p>\n<p data-end=\"1767\" data-start=\"1646\">This hash is ideal for users who want <strong data-end=\"1767\" data-start=\"1684\">premium craftsmanship, strong potency, and a smooth, traditional resin flavour.</strong></p>\n<hr data-end=\"1772\" data-start=\"1769\"/>\n<h3 data-end=\"1792\" data-start=\"1774\">🔥 <strong data-end=\"1790\" data-start=\"1779\">EFFECTS</strong></h3>\n<ul data-end=\"1892\" data-start=\"1793\">\n<li data-end=\"1811\" data-start=\"1793\">\n<p data-end=\"1811\" data-start=\"1795\">Deep body melt</p>\n</li>\n<li data-end=\"1832\" data-start=\"1812\">\n<p data-end=\"1832\" data-start=\"1814\">Heavy relaxation</p>\n</li>\n<li data-end=\"1852\" data-start=\"1833\">\n<p data-end=\"1852\" data-start=\"1835\">Meditative calm</p>\n</li>\n<li data-end=\"1874\" data-start=\"1853\">\n<p data-end=\"1874\" data-start=\"1855\">Long-lasting high</p>\n</li>\n<li data-end=\"1892\" data-start=\"1875\">\n<p data-end=\"1892\" data-start=\"1877\">Warm euphoria</p>\n</li>\n</ul>\n<hr data-end=\"1897\" data-start=\"1894\"/>\n<h3 data-end=\"1923\" data-start=\"1899\">🌿 <strong data-end=\"1921\" data-start=\"1904\">MAY HELP WITH</strong></h3>\n<ul data-end=\"2012\" data-start=\"1924\">\n<li data-end=\"1934\" data-start=\"1924\">\n<p data-end=\"1934\" data-start=\"1926\">Stress</p>\n</li>\n<li data-end=\"1946\" data-start=\"1935\">\n<p data-end=\"1946\" data-start=\"1937\">Anxiety</p>\n</li>\n<li data-end=\"1963\" data-start=\"1947\">\n<p data-end=\"1963\" data-start=\"1949\">Chronic pain</p>\n</li>\n<li data-end=\"1976\" data-start=\"1964\">\n<p data-end=\"1976\" data-start=\"1966\">Insomnia</p>\n</li>\n<li data-end=\"1995\" data-start=\"1977\">\n<p data-end=\"1995\" data-start=\"1979\">Muscle tension</p>\n</li>\n<li data-end=\"2012\" data-start=\"1996\">\n<p data-end=\"2012\" data-start=\"1998\">Overthinking</p>\n</li>\n</ul>\n<hr data-end=\"2017\" data-start=\"2014\"/>\n<h3 data-end=\"2037\" data-start=\"2019\">🟤 <strong data-end=\"2035\" data-start=\"2024\">FLAVORS</strong></h3>\n<ul data-end=\"2096\" data-start=\"2038\">\n<li data-end=\"2054\" data-start=\"2038\">\n<p data-end=\"2054\" data-start=\"2040\">Creamy resin</p>\n</li>\n<li data-end=\"2065\" data-start=\"2055\">\n<p data-end=\"2065\" data-start=\"2057\">Earthy</p>\n</li>\n<li data-end=\"2075\" data-start=\"2066\">\n<p data-end=\"2075\" data-start=\"2068\">Spicy</p>\n</li>\n<li data-end=\"2096\" data-start=\"2076\">\n<p data-end=\"2096\" data-start=\"2078\">Sweet undertones</p>\n</li>\n</ul>\n<hr data-end=\"2101\" data-start=\"2098\"/>\n<h3 data-end=\"2121\" data-start=\"2103\">🌬️ <strong data-end=\"2119\" data-start=\"2109\">AROMAS</strong></h3>\n<ul data-end=\"2184\" data-start=\"2122\">\n<li data-end=\"2132\" data-start=\"2122\">\n<p data-end=\"2132\" data-start=\"2124\">Earthy</p>\n</li>\n<li data-end=\"2147\" data-start=\"2133\">\n<p data-end=\"2147\" data-start=\"2135\">Warm spice</p>\n</li>\n<li data-end=\"2167\" data-start=\"2148\">\n<p data-end=\"2167\" data-start=\"2150\">Hashy sweetness</p>\n</li>\n<li data-end=\"2184\" data-start=\"2168\">\n<p data-end=\"2184\" data-start=\"2170\">Natural oils</p>\n</li>\n</ul>\n<hr/>\n<h2>💡 Usage Guide</h2>\n<h3>Recommended Dosage</h3>\n<ul>\n<li><strong>Beginners:</strong> Start with a rice grain-sized piece (approximately 0.025-0.05g). Hash is significantly more potent than flower.</li>\n<li><strong>Experienced Users:</strong> 0.1-0.2g per session, adjusting based on tolerance and desired effects.</li>\n<li><strong>High Tolerance:</strong> Up to 0.3g per session for seasoned concentrate consumers.</li>\n</ul>\n<h3>Consumption Methods</h3>\n<ul>\n<li><strong>Smoking:</strong> Crumble and mix with flower in joints, pipes, or bongs for enhanced potency and traditional experience.</li>\n<li><strong>Vaporizing:</strong> Use hash-compatible vaporizer at 180-210°C for smooth, flavourful vapour with maximum terpene preservation.</li>\n<li><strong>Hot Knives:</strong> Traditional method heating two knives and pressing hash between them for immediate effects.</li>\n<li><strong>Topping Bowls:</strong> Add small pieces atop flower bowls for elevated potency without altering your regular routine.</li>\n<li><strong>Hash Edibles (Advanced):</strong> To make edibles, decarboxylate hash at 110-120°C (230-250°F) for 30-40 minutes to activate THC. Mix into butter or oil-based recipes. Effects take 30-120 minutes and last 6-12 hours. Hash edibles are significantly more potent than flower edibles—start with 1/4 of your normal flower edible dose.</li>\n</ul>\n<h3>Onset &amp; Duration</h3>\n<ul>\n<li><strong>Onset (Smoking/Vaping):</strong> 2-10 minutes</li>\n<li><strong>Onset (Edibles):</strong> 30-120 minutes</li>\n<li><strong>Peak Effects:</strong> 15-45 minutes (inhaled) or 2-4 hours (edibles)</li>\n<li><strong>Duration:</strong> 2-4 hours (inhaled) or 6-12 hours (edibles)</li>\n</ul>\n<p><strong>⚠️ Important:</strong> Hash is significantly more potent than regular flower. Start with minimal amounts and wait to assess effects before consuming more. for experienced users – beginners should start with lower doses or those new to concentrates.</p>\n</div>\n</div>",
