        "descriptionHTML": "<div class=\"tab-pane active\" id=\"tab-description\">\n<div class=\"detail-tab-desc detail-content-wrap\">\n<p>**Buy Fungara Pods online in Canada at Mohawk Medibles**, your trusted Indigenous-owned cannabis accessories dispensary. Shop these premium replacement pods for your large airflow rechargeable device and enjoy fast Canada-wide shipping with same-day processing. Order now for discreet delivery and ensure you always have backup pods ready for uninterrupted vaping sessions. Perfect for vapers seeking reliable, high-capacity pods with superior airflow performance.</p>\n<p>–</p>\n<h2>💡 Usage Guide</h2>\n<h3>How to Install Your Fungara Pods</h3>\n<ul>\n<li><strong>Step 1:</strong> Remove the pod from packaging and check for any protective seals or plugs</li>\n<li><strong>Step 2:</strong> Fill the 8.0ml juice capacity chamber with your preferred vape liquid through the fill port</li>\n<li><strong>Step 3:</strong> Let the pod sit for 5-10 minutes to allow the 0.60Ω coil to fully saturate</li>\n<li><strong>Step 4:</strong> Insert the pod firmly into your rechargeable device until you hear a click</li>\n<li><strong>Step 5:</strong> Start with lower power settings and adjust for optimal vapour production</li>\n</ul>\n<h3>Battery &amp; Maintenance</h3>\n<ul>\n<li><strong>Battery Life:</strong> 950mAh capacity provides full-day use for moderate vapers</li>\n<li><strong>Charging:</strong> Use the included USB cable; full charge takes approximately 60-90 minutes</li>\n<li><strong>Pod Lifespan:</strong> Each pod lasts approximately 3,000-5,000 puffs depending on usage habits</li>\n<li><strong>Cleaning:</strong> Wipe connection points weekly with a dry cloth to maintain optimal performance</li>\n</ul>\n<h3>Best Use Cases</h3>\n<p>The large 8.0ml capacity makes these pods ideal for heavy users who don’t want frequent refills. The 0.60Ω resistance and large airflow design deliver satisfying vapour production perfect for direct-to-lung vaping. The 950mAh battery ensures all-day reliability for on-the-go use.</p>\n<p><strong>⚠️ Safety Note:</strong> Only use compatible vape liquids. Do not overfill pods. Keep away from extreme temperatures. Charge using approved cables only. Keep out of reach of children and pets.</p>\n<h2>❓ Frequently Asked Questions</h2>\n<h3>Are Fungara Pods compatible with my device?</h3>\n<p><strong>A:</strong> Fungara Pods are designed specifically for large airflow rechargeable devices. They feature a 57.35×23×23mm size with 0.60Ω resistance. Please verify your device specifications match these dimensions before ordering. Contact our customer support if you’re unsure about compatibility.</p>\n<h3>How many puffs can I get from each Fungara Pod?</h3>\n<p><strong>A:</strong> With an 8.0ml juice capacity, each pod typically delivers 3,000-5,000 puffs depending on your vaping habits, power settings, and puff duration. The 0.60Ω coil provides consistent performance throughout the pod’s lifespan.</p>\n<h3>What material are Fungara Pods made from?</h3>\n<p><strong>A:</strong> Fungara Pods are constructed from PCTG (Polyethylene Terephthalate Glycol) and other health-conscious materials. PCTG is a premium, food-grade plastic known for durability, chemical resistance, and safety. It’s BPA-free and designed for repeated heating and cooling cycles.</p>\n<h3>How long does the 950mAh battery last?</h3>\n<p><strong>A:</strong> The integrated 950mAh battery typically provides 1-2 days of use for moderate vapers, or a full day for heavy users. Battery life varies based on power settings, puff frequency, and duration. The device features USB charging for convenient recharging anywhere.</p>\n<h3>Does Mohawk Medibles ship Fungara Pods across Canada?</h3>\n<p><strong>A:</strong> Yes! We offer fast, discreet Canada-wide shipping with same-day processing on orders placed before 2 PM EST. Your Fungara Pods will arrive in plain, unmarked packaging. This pack includes 2 pods, giving you a backup for uninterrupted vaping.</p>\n<h3>How do I know when to replace my Fungara Pod?</h3>\n<p><strong>A:</strong> Replace your pod when you notice decreased vapour production, burnt or off-flavours, leaking, or difficulty drawing. Regular signs include muted taste and reduced throat hit. For optimal performance, consider replacing pods every 2-4 weeks depending on usage frequency.</p>\n<h3>Can I refill Fungara Pods?</h3>\n<p><strong>A:</strong> Yes, Fungara Pods feature an 8.0ml refillable capacity. Use the designated fill port and avoid overfilling. Always allow 5-10 minutes after refilling for the coil to properly saturate before vaping. Use quality vape liquids compatible with 0.60Ω resistance coils for best results.</p>\n</div>\n</div>",
