        "descriptionHTML": "<div class=\"tab-pane active\" id=\"tab-description\">\n<div class=\"detail-tab-desc detail-content-wrap\">\n<p>**Buy the Nova Twist 900mAh 510 Battery online in Canada at Mohawk Medibles**, your trusted Indigenous-owned cannabis dispensary. Shop this premium variable voltage vape battery and enjoy fast Canada-wide shipping with same-day processing. Order now for discreet delivery and experience the perfect balance of style, performance, and reliability. Compatible with all standard 510-thread cartridges, the Nova Twist Classic Edition delivers smooth, customizable vaping with long-lasting battery life.</p>\n<p>–</p>\n<h2>💡 Usage Guide</h2>\n<h3>How to Use Your Nova Twist Battery</h3>\n<ul>\n<li><strong>Initial Setup:</strong> Fully charge your battery before first use (2-3 hours). The LED indicator will show charging status and turn off when complete.</li>\n<li><strong>Attaching Cartridges:</strong> Gently screw your 510-thread cartridge clockwise onto the battery connection. Do not overtighten – hand-tight is sufficient.</li>\n<li><strong>Voltage Adjustment:</strong> Twist the dial at the base to adjust voltage between 3.3V-4.8V. Start low (3.3V-3.6V) for flavour, increase (3.8V-4.2V) for balanced hits, or go higher (4.4V-4.8V) for maximum vapour production.</li>\n<li><strong>Activation:</strong> Press the button 5 times rapidly to turn on/off. Hold the button while inhaling to activate. The LED will illuminate during use.</li>\n</ul>\n<h3>Battery Maintenance</h3>\n<ul>\n<li><strong>Charging:</strong> Use the included USB charger. Charge when LED blinks during use (typically every 2-3 days with regular use).</li>\n<li><strong>Cleaning:</strong> Wipe the connection point weekly with isopropyl alcohol on a cotton swab to ensure optimal performance.</li>\n<li><strong>Storage:</strong> Store in a cool, dry place. Turn off when not in use to preserve battery life.</li>\n</ul>\n<h3>Best Use Cases</h3>\n<p>Perfect for on-the-go vaping, discreet use, and cartridge enthusiasts who value customization. The compact design fits easily in pockets or bags, while the variable voltage allows you to optimize your experience based on cartridge type and personal preference. Ideal for both CBD and THC cartridges.</p>\n<h2>❓ Frequently Asked Questions</h2>\n<h3>Is the Nova Twist 900mAh compatible with all vape cartridges?</h3>\n<p><strong>A:</strong> Yes! The Nova Twist features universal 510-thread compatibility, working with virtually all standard vape cartridges including distillate, live resin, and CBD cartridges. Simply screw on your cartridge and you’re ready to vape.</p>\n<h3>How long does the 900mAh battery last on a full charge?</h3>\n<p><strong>A:</strong> With the powerful 900mAh capacity, you can expect 2-4 days of regular use per charge (approximately 200-300 puffs). Battery life varies based on voltage settings, cartridge resistance, and usage frequency. Higher voltage settings will drain the battery faster.</p>\n<h3>What voltage should I use with my cartridge?</h3>\n<p><strong>A:</strong> Start at 3.3V-3.6V for maximum flavour and smooth hits. Increase to 3.8V-4.2V for balanced vapour and potency. Use 4.4V-4.8V for thick clouds and maximum effects. Lower voltages preserve terpenes and prevent burnt taste, while higher voltages produce more vapour.</p>\n<h3>How do I know when the Nova Twist battery needs charging?</h3>\n<p><strong>A:</strong> The LED indicator will blink 10 times when the battery is low. During charging, the LED stays illuminated and turns off when fully charged (typically 2-3 hours). We recommend charging before the battery is completely depleted to maximize lifespan.</p>\n<h3>Does Mohawk Medibles ship the Nova Twist battery across Canada?</h3>\n<p><strong>A:</strong> Absolutely! We offer fast, discreet Canada-wide shipping with same-day processing on orders placed before 2 PM EST. Your Nova Twist battery ships in plain, unmarked packaging with tracking included.</p>\n<h3>What’s included with the Nova Twist 900mAh battery?</h3>\n<p><strong>A:</strong> Each Nova Twist Classic Edition package includes the 900mAh variable voltage battery and a USB charging cable. Cartridges are sold separately. The battery comes ready to use – just charge, attach your favourite cartridge, and enjoy.</p>\n<h3>How do I clean and maintain my Nova Twist battery?</h3>\n<p><strong>A:</strong> Clean the 510-thread connection weekly using a cotton swab dipped in isopropyl alcohol to remove residue buildup. Ensure the battery is turned off during cleaning. Avoid getting liquid inside the device. Proper maintenance ensures consistent performance and extends battery lifespan.</p>\n</div>\n</div>",
