        "metaDescription": "🍨❄️ Ice Cream Hash – Static Sift Hash\nIndica Dominant Hybrid – 60% Indica / 40% SativaTHC: ~19%\nIce Cream Hash delivers smooth flavour, balanced effects, and cl",
        "shortDescription": "🍨❄️ Ice Cream Hash – Static Sift Hash\nIndica Dominant Hybrid – 60% Indica / 40% SativaTHC: ~19%\nIce Cream Hash delivers smooth flavour, balanced effects, and classic comfort from the very first hit....",
        "descriptionHTML": "<div class=\"tab-pane active\" id=\"tab-description\">\n<div class=\"detail-tab-desc detail-content-wrap\">\n<h1 data-end=\"260\" data-start=\"216\">🍨❄️ <strong data-end=\"260\" data-start=\"223\">Ice Cream Hash – Static Sift Hash</strong></h1>\n<p data-end=\"330\" data-start=\"262\"><strong data-end=\"314\" data-start=\"262\">Indica Dominant Hybrid – 60% Indica / 40% Sativa</strong><br data-end=\"317\" data-start=\"314\"/><strong data-end=\"330\" data-start=\"317\">THC: ~19%</strong></p>\n<p data-end=\"692\" data-start=\"332\">Ice Cream Hash delivers smooth flavour, balanced effects, and classic comfort from the very first hit. To begin, this indica-leaning hybrid comes from the popular <strong data-end=\"508\" data-start=\"495\">Ice Cream</strong> strain, known for its creamy sweetness and long-lasting body buzz. Because of this lineage, the experience stays relaxing, soothing, and deeply enjoyable without feeling overwhelming.</p>\n<p data-end=\"1102\" data-start=\"694\">Right away, the smoke feels soft and clean on the inhale. Almost immediately, a gentle wave of euphoria lifts the mood. Shortly after, relaxation spreads evenly through both mind and body. Instead of racing thoughts, calm sets in. At the same time, the body begins to unwind, easing tension and promoting rest. As a result, Ice Cream Hash works especially well in the evening, during downtime, or before bed.</p>\n<p data-end=\"1380\" data-start=\"1104\">Meanwhile, the flavour remains front and centre. First, sweet vanilla and creamy notes hit the palate. Then, hints of honey and nuttiness round things out. Finally, a smooth, dessert-like finish lingers, making each pull feel indulgent and satisfying—just like real ice cream.</p>\n<hr data-end=\"1385\" data-start=\"1382\"/>\n<h2 data-end=\"1412\" data-start=\"1387\">✨ <strong data-end=\"1412\" data-start=\"1392\">What You’ll Feel</strong></h2>\n<ul data-end=\"1515\" data-start=\"1413\">\n<li data-end=\"1440\" data-start=\"1413\">\n<p data-end=\"1440\" data-start=\"1415\">😄 Euphoric and content</p>\n</li>\n<li data-end=\"1462\" data-start=\"1441\">\n<p data-end=\"1462\" data-start=\"1443\">😌 Deeply relaxed</p>\n</li>\n<li data-end=\"1485\" data-start=\"1463\">\n<p data-end=\"1485\" data-start=\"1465\">💤 Calm and sleepy</p>\n</li>\n<li data-end=\"1515\" data-start=\"1486\">\n<p data-end=\"1515\" data-start=\"1488\">🌙 Long-lasting body buzz</p>\n</li>\n</ul>\n<hr data-end=\"1520\" data-start=\"1517\"/>\n<h2 data-end=\"1545\" data-start=\"1522\">🩺 <strong data-end=\"1545\" data-start=\"1528\">May Help With</strong></h2>\n<ul data-end=\"1632\" data-start=\"1546\">\n<li data-end=\"1557\" data-start=\"1546\">\n<p data-end=\"1557\" data-start=\"1548\">Anxiety</p>\n</li>\n<li data-end=\"1568\" data-start=\"1558\">\n<p data-end=\"1568\" data-start=\"1560\">Stress</p>\n</li>\n<li data-end=\"1583\" data-start=\"1569\">\n<p data-end=\"1583\" data-start=\"1571\">Depression</p>\n</li>\n<li data-end=\"1600\" data-start=\"1584\">\n<p data-end=\"1600\" data-start=\"1586\">Chronic pain</p>\n</li>\n<li data-end=\"1613\" data-start=\"1601\">\n<p data-end=\"1613\" data-start=\"1603\">Insomnia</p>\n</li>\n<li data-end=\"1624\" data-start=\"1614\">\n<p data-end=\"1624\" data-start=\"1616\">Nausea</p>\n</li>\n<li data-end=\"1632\" data-start=\"1625\">\n<p data-end=\"1632\" data-start=\"1627\">PMS</p>\n</li>\n</ul>\n<hr data-end=\"1637\" data-start=\"1634\"/>\n<h2 data-end=\"1662\" data-start=\"1639\">🍦 <strong data-end=\"1662\" data-start=\"1645\">Flavour Notes</strong></h2>\n<ul data-end=\"1715\" data-start=\"1663\">\n<li data-end=\"1673\" data-start=\"1663\">\n<p data-end=\"1673\" data-start=\"1665\">Creamy</p>\n</li>\n<li data-end=\"1685\" data-start=\"1674\">\n<p data-end=\"1685\" data-start=\"1676\">Vanilla</p>\n</li>\n<li data-end=\"1695\" data-start=\"1686\">\n<p data-end=\"1695\" data-start=\"1688\">Sweet</p>\n</li>\n<li data-end=\"1705\" data-start=\"1696\">\n<p data-end=\"1705\" data-start=\"1698\">Honey</p>\n</li>\n<li data-end=\"1715\" data-start=\"1706\">\n<p data-end=\"1715\" data-start=\"1708\">Nutty</p>\n</li>\n</ul>\n<hr data-end=\"1720\" data-start=\"1717\"/>\n<h2 data-end=\"1746\" data-start=\"1722\">🌬️ <strong data-end=\"1746\" data-start=\"1729\">Aroma Profile</strong></h2>\n<ul data-end=\"1798\" data-start=\"1747\">\n<li data-end=\"1756\" data-start=\"1747\">\n<p data-end=\"1756\" data-start=\"1749\">Sweet</p>\n</li>\n<li data-end=\"1768\" data-start=\"1757\">\n<p data-end=\"1768\" data-start=\"1759\">Vanilla</p>\n</li>\n<li data-end=\"1781\" data-start=\"1769\">\n<p data-end=\"1781\" data-start=\"1771\">Fragrant</p>\n</li>\n<li data-end=\"1798\" data-start=\"1782\">\n<p data-end=\"1798\" data-start=\"1784\">Dessert-like</p>\n</li>\n</ul>\n<hr data-end=\"1803\" data-start=\"1800\"/>\n<h2 data-end=\"1856\" data-start=\"1805\">❄️ <strong data-end=\"1856\" data-start=\"1811\">Why Static Sift Hash Makes the Difference</strong></h2>\n<p data-end=\"2175\" data-start=\"1857\">To start, producers dry sift the cannabis to collect resin glands.<br data-end=\"1926\" data-start=\"1923\"/>Next, static electricity pulls pure trichome heads away from plant matter.<br data-end=\"2003\" data-start=\"2000\"/>Because no water or solvents are used, the hash stays clean and natural.<br data-end=\"2078\" data-start=\"2075\"/>As a result, the final product delivers <strong data-end=\"2174\" data-start=\"2118\">better flavour, stronger effects, and smoother smoke</strong>.</p>\n<hr/>\n<h2>💡 Usage Guide</h2>\n<h3>Recommended Dosage</h3>\n<ul>\n<li><strong>Beginners:</strong> Start with a rice grain-sized piece (approximately 0.025-0.05g). Hash is significantly more potent than flower.</li>\n<li><strong>Experienced Users:</strong> 0.1-0.2g per session, adjusting based on tolerance and desired effects.</li>\n<li><strong>High Tolerance:</strong> Up to 0.3g per session for seasoned concentrate consumers.</li>\n</ul>\n<h3>Consumption Methods</h3>\n<ul>\n<li><strong>Smoking:</strong> Crumble and mix with flower in joints, pipes, or bongs for enhanced potency and traditional experience.</li>\n<li><strong>Vaporizing:</strong> Use hash-compatible vaporizer at 180-210°C for smooth, flavourful vapour with maximum terpene preservation.</li>\n<li><strong>Hot Knives:</strong> Traditional method heating two knives and pressing hash between them for immediate effects.</li>\n<li><strong>Topping Bowls:</strong> Add small pieces atop flower bowls for elevated potency without altering your regular routine.</li>\n<li><strong>Hash Edibles (Advanced):</strong> To make edibles, decarboxylate hash at 110-120°C (230-250°F) for 30-40 minutes to activate THC. Mix into butter or oil-based recipes. Effects take 30-120 minutes and last 6-12 hours. Hash edibles are significantly more potent than flower edibles—start with 1/4 of your normal flower edible dose.</li>\n</ul>\n<h3>Onset &amp; Duration</h3>\n<ul>\n<li><strong>Onset (Smoking/Vaping):</strong> 2-10 minutes</li>\n<li><strong>Onset (Edibles):</strong> 30-120 minutes</li>\n<li><strong>Peak Effects:</strong> 15-45 minutes (inhaled) or 2-4 hours (edibles)</li>\n<li><strong>Duration:</strong> 2-4 hours (inhaled) or 6-12 hours (edibles)</li>\n</ul>\n<p><strong>⚠️ Important:</strong> Hash is significantly more potent than regular flower. Start with minimal amounts and wait to assess effects before consuming more. for experienced users – beginners should start with lower doses or those new to concentrates.</p>\n</div>\n</div>",
