        "shortDescription": "🍇👽 Purple MAC — $6/Gram Special\nHybrid | 50% Sativa / 50% IndicaTHC: 15% – 16%\n\nPurple MAC, also known as Purple Miracle Alien Cookies, is a beautifully balanced hybrid that blends the best of MAC a...",
        "descriptionHTML": "<div class=\"tab-pane active\" id=\"tab-description\">\n<div class=\"detail-tab-desc detail-content-wrap\">\n<h2 data-end=\"174\" data-start=\"136\">🍇👽 Purple MAC — $6/Gram Special</h2>\n<p data-end=\"232\" data-start=\"175\"><strong data-end=\"211\" data-start=\"175\">Hybrid | 50% Sativa / 50% Indica</strong><br data-end=\"214\" data-start=\"211\"/><strong data-end=\"232\" data-start=\"214\">THC: 15% – 16%</strong></p>\n<hr/>\n<p data-end=\"764\" data-start=\"480\">Purple MAC, also known as <strong data-end=\"538\" data-start=\"506\">Purple Miracle Alien Cookies</strong>, is a beautifully balanced hybrid that blends the best of <strong data-end=\"621\" data-start=\"597\">MAC and Purple Punch</strong> genetics 🌿✨. From the very first hit, the effects roll in quickly, lifting your mood and setting a <strong data-end=\"744\" data-start=\"722\">giddy, giggly tone</strong> that sticks around.</p>\n<p data-end=\"1135\" data-start=\"766\">Almost immediately, happiness takes over 😄. Your mind feels light, playful, and blissfully upbeat, making everything around you feel more entertaining. As the high continues, creativity flows easily, conversations feel effortless, and laughter comes naturally. Meanwhile, a gentle body calm settles in, keeping you relaxed without slowing you down or knocking you out.</p>\n<p data-end=\"1382\" data-start=\"1137\">Because of its moderate THC range, Purple MAC is <strong data-end=\"1222\" data-start=\"1186\">strong enough to feel satisfying</strong> while staying approachable for most users. A mild case of the munchies often follows, making it perfect for snack time, movie nights, or chill social sessions.</p>\n<p data-end=\"1663\" data-start=\"1384\">Flavour is where Purple MAC truly shines 🍪🍋. Expect <strong data-end=\"1477\" data-start=\"1438\">sweet berry cookies and grape notes</strong> up front, followed by touches of sour lemon and spicy diesel on the exhale. The aroma leans bolder, filling the air with <strong data-end=\"1662\" data-start=\"1599\">pungent diesel, citrus zest, earthy herbs, and a spicy kick</strong>.</p>\n<p data-end=\"1797\" data-start=\"1665\">This strain delivers <strong data-end=\"1715\" data-start=\"1686\">fun, flavour, and balance</strong> in every session — no rush, no crash, just smooth enjoyment from start to finish.</p>\n<hr/>\n<h3 data-end=\"1821\" data-start=\"1799\">✨ What You’ll Feel</h3>\n<ul data-end=\"1956\" data-start=\"1822\">\n<li data-end=\"1847\" data-start=\"1822\">\n<p data-end=\"1847\" data-start=\"1824\">😄 Happy and euphoric</p>\n</li>\n<li data-end=\"1873\" data-start=\"1848\">\n<p data-end=\"1873\" data-start=\"1850\">😂 Giggly and playful</p>\n</li>\n<li data-end=\"1902\" data-start=\"1874\">\n<p data-end=\"1902\" data-start=\"1876\">🎨 Creative and uplifted</p>\n</li>\n<li data-end=\"1924\" data-start=\"1903\">\n<p data-end=\"1924\" data-start=\"1905\">🍔 Light munchies</p>\n</li>\n<li data-end=\"1956\" data-start=\"1925\">\n<p data-end=\"1956\" data-start=\"1927\">😌 Calm, balanced body buzz</p>\n</li>\n</ul>\n<hr/>\n<h3 data-end=\"1978\" data-start=\"1958\">🩺 May Help With</h3>\n<ul data-end=\"2058\" data-start=\"1979\">\n<li data-end=\"1995\" data-start=\"1979\">\n<p data-end=\"1995\" data-start=\"1981\">Chronic pain</p>\n</li>\n<li data-end=\"2008\" data-start=\"1996\">\n<p data-end=\"2008\" data-start=\"1998\">Insomnia</p>\n</li>\n<li data-end=\"2029\" data-start=\"2009\">\n<p data-end=\"2029\" data-start=\"2011\">Stress &amp; anxiety</p>\n</li>\n<li data-end=\"2058\" data-start=\"2030\">\n<p data-end=\"2058\" data-start=\"2032\">Appetite loss / anorexia</p>\n</li>\n</ul>\n<hr/>\n<h3 data-end=\"2082\" data-start=\"2060\">🍇 Flavour Profile</h3>\n<ul data-end=\"2153\" data-start=\"2083\">\n<li data-end=\"2092\" data-start=\"2083\">\n<p data-end=\"2092\" data-start=\"2085\">Berry</p>\n</li>\n<li data-end=\"2102\" data-start=\"2093\">\n<p data-end=\"2102\" data-start=\"2095\">Grape</p>\n</li>\n<li data-end=\"2119\" data-start=\"2103\">\n<p data-end=\"2119\" data-start=\"2105\">Sweet cookie</p>\n</li>\n<li data-end=\"2136\" data-start=\"2120\">\n<p data-end=\"2136\" data-start=\"2122\">Lemon citrus</p>\n</li>\n<li data-end=\"2153\" data-start=\"2137\">\n<p data-end=\"2153\" data-start=\"2139\">Spicy diesel</p>\n</li>\n</ul>\n<hr/>\n<h3 data-end=\"2176\" data-start=\"2155\">🌬️ Aroma Profile</h3>\n<ul data-end=\"2247\" data-start=\"2177\">\n<li data-end=\"2195\" data-start=\"2177\">\n<p data-end=\"2195\" data-start=\"2179\">Pungent diesel</p>\n</li>\n<li data-end=\"2212\" data-start=\"2196\">\n<p data-end=\"2212\" data-start=\"2198\">Citrus lemon</p>\n</li>\n<li data-end=\"2230\" data-start=\"2213\">\n<p data-end=\"2230\" data-start=\"2215\">Peppery spice</p>\n</li>\n<li data-end=\"2247\" data-start=\"2231\">\n<p data-end=\"2247\" data-start=\"2233\">Earthy herbs</p>\n</li>\n</ul>\n<p data-end=\"2359\" data-start=\"2249\">Purple MAC is a <strong data-end=\"2293\" data-start=\"2265\">feel-good hybrid classic</strong> — sweet, smooth, and guaranteed to put a smile on your face 🍇🔥.</p>\n<hr/>\n<p><strong>How to Use Marijuana (Responsibly)</strong></p>\n<p><strong>Start Low, Go Slow</strong> – If you’re new to cannabis or trying a strong strain like Blue Comatose, begin with a <strong>small dose</strong> (1–2 puffs or a low-dose edible) and wait 30–60 minutes to gauge the effects.</p>\n<p><strong>Choose the Right Method:</strong></p>\n<ul>\n<li><strong>Smoking or Vaping:</strong> Fast-acting and ideal for experienced users. Use a joint, pipe, or dry herb vape.</li>\n<li><strong>Edibles or Capsules:</strong> Longer-lasting effects but slower onset (30–90 mins). Start with a low dose (5–10mg THC).</li>\n<li><strong>Tinctures or Oils:</strong> Absorbed under the tongue for quicker onset (15–30 mins). Great for controlled dosing.</li>\n<li><strong>Topicals:</strong> Not psychoactive—best for localized relief from aches or inflammation.</li>\n</ul>\n<p><strong>Stay Hydrated &amp; Have Snacks</strong> – Dry mouth and the munchies are common. Keep water and snacks handy.</p>\n<p><strong>Don’t Mix With Alcohol or Other Substances</strong> – Mixing can intensify effects unpredictably.</p>\n<p><strong>Don’t Drive or Operate Machinery</strong> – Wait several hours after using THC-rich products before engaging in any activity that requires focus or coordination.</p>\n<p><strong>Store Safely</strong> – Keep all cannabis products out of reach of children and pets.</p>\n</div>\n</div>",
