        "shortDescription": "🍇💜 Purple Urkle\n$40/OZ or $100/3OZIndica Dominant Hybrid – 70% Indica / 30% SativaTHC: 18% – 21%\n\nPurple Urkle is a legendary California classic with roots going back to the late 1980s 🌿. Often link...",
        "descriptionHTML": "<div class=\"tab-pane active\" id=\"tab-description\">\n<div class=\"detail-tab-desc detail-content-wrap\">\n<h3 data-end=\"145\" data-start=\"123\">🍇💜 Purple Urkle</h3>\n<p data-end=\"244\" data-start=\"146\"><strong data-end=\"168\" data-start=\"146\">$40/OZ or $100/3OZ</strong><br data-end=\"171\" data-start=\"168\"/><strong data-end=\"223\" data-start=\"171\">Indica Dominant Hybrid – 70% Indica / 30% Sativa</strong><br data-end=\"226\" data-start=\"223\"/><strong data-end=\"244\" data-start=\"226\">THC: 18% – 21%</strong></p>\n<hr/>\n<p data-end=\"764\" data-start=\"507\"><strong data-end=\"523\" data-start=\"507\">Purple Urkle</strong> is a legendary California classic with roots going back to the late 1980s 🌿. Often linked to <strong data-end=\"637\" data-start=\"618\">Mendocino Purps</strong> and closely related to <strong data-end=\"682\" data-start=\"661\">Granddaddy Purple</strong>, this indica-leaning hybrid has earned its reputation as a true nighttime staple.</p>\n<p data-end=\"1020\" data-start=\"766\">Right away, Purple Urkle greets you with <strong data-end=\"846\" data-start=\"807\">rich grape and sweet berry flavours</strong>, followed by a slightly skunky, fruity aroma that fills the room 🍇✨. The buds stand out with <strong data-end=\"961\" data-start=\"941\">deep purple hues</strong>, bright orange hairs, and a dense, bushy indica structure.</p>\n<p data-end=\"1325\" data-start=\"1022\">As the effects settle in, a <strong data-end=\"1079\" data-start=\"1050\">strong physical body buzz</strong> takes over. Muscles begin to loosen, stress fades, and the mind drifts into a calm, happy state 😌. Shortly after, the indica side shines through, bringing <strong data-end=\"1273\" data-start=\"1236\">heavy relaxation and sleepy vibes</strong>, making this strain an excellent choice before bed.</p>\n<p data-end=\"1585\" data-start=\"1327\">With <strong data-end=\"1346\" data-start=\"1332\">18–21% THC</strong>, Purple Urkle delivers reliable potency without overwhelming the senses. Because of its soothing nature, many users turn to this strain for <strong data-end=\"1534\" data-start=\"1487\">insomnia, chronic pain, anxiety, and nausea</strong>, especially during the evening or nighttime hours.</p>\n<p data-end=\"1733\" data-start=\"1587\">If you’re looking for a <strong data-end=\"1649\" data-start=\"1611\">grape-flavoured, old-school indica</strong> that truly helps you shut things down for the night, Purple Urkle is a must-try 💜.</p>\n<hr data-end=\"1738\" data-start=\"1735\"/>\n<h3 data-end=\"1753\" data-start=\"1740\">✨ Effects</h3>\n<ul data-end=\"1856\" data-start=\"1754\">\n<li data-end=\"1769\" data-start=\"1754\">\n<p data-end=\"1769\" data-start=\"1756\">😄 Euphoric</p>\n</li>\n<li data-end=\"1782\" data-start=\"1770\">\n<p data-end=\"1782\" data-start=\"1772\">😊 Happy</p>\n</li>\n<li data-end=\"1806\" data-start=\"1783\">\n<p data-end=\"1806\" data-start=\"1785\">🎨 Light creativity</p>\n</li>\n<li data-end=\"1834\" data-start=\"1807\">\n<p data-end=\"1834\" data-start=\"1809\">😌 Deep body relaxation</p>\n</li>\n<li data-end=\"1856\" data-start=\"1835\">\n<p data-end=\"1856\" data-start=\"1837\">💤 Sleep-inducing</p>\n</li>\n</ul>\n<hr/>\n<h3 data-end=\"1878\" data-start=\"1858\">🩺 May Help With</h3>\n<ul data-end=\"1998\" data-start=\"1879\">\n<li data-end=\"1891\" data-start=\"1879\">\n<p data-end=\"1891\" data-start=\"1881\">Insomnia</p>\n</li>\n<li data-end=\"1908\" data-start=\"1892\">\n<p data-end=\"1908\" data-start=\"1894\">Chronic pain</p>\n</li>\n<li data-end=\"1929\" data-start=\"1909\">\n<p data-end=\"1929\" data-start=\"1911\">Anxiety &amp; stress</p>\n</li>\n<li data-end=\"1943\" data-start=\"1930\">\n<p data-end=\"1943\" data-start=\"1932\">Arthritis</p>\n</li>\n<li data-end=\"1957\" data-start=\"1944\">\n<p data-end=\"1957\" data-start=\"1946\">Migraines</p>\n</li>\n<li data-end=\"1968\" data-start=\"1958\">\n<p data-end=\"1968\" data-start=\"1960\">Nausea</p>\n</li>\n<li data-end=\"1989\" data-start=\"1969\">\n<p data-end=\"1989\" data-start=\"1971\">Loss of appetite</p>\n</li>\n<li data-end=\"1998\" data-start=\"1990\">\n<p data-end=\"1998\" data-start=\"1992\">PTSD</p>\n</li>\n</ul>\n<hr/>\n<h3 data-end=\"2022\" data-start=\"2000\">🍇 Flavour Profile</h3>\n<ul data-end=\"2072\" data-start=\"2023\">\n<li data-end=\"2032\" data-start=\"2023\">\n<p data-end=\"2032\" data-start=\"2025\">Grape</p>\n</li>\n<li data-end=\"2050\" data-start=\"2033\">\n<p data-end=\"2050\" data-start=\"2035\">Sweet berries</p>\n</li>\n<li data-end=\"2061\" data-start=\"2051\">\n<p data-end=\"2061\" data-start=\"2053\">Fruity</p>\n</li>\n<li data-end=\"2072\" data-start=\"2062\">\n<p data-end=\"2072\" data-start=\"2064\">Skunky</p>\n</li>\n</ul>\n<hr/>\n<h3 data-end=\"2095\" data-start=\"2074\">🌬️ Aroma Profile</h3>\n<ul data-end=\"2151\" data-start=\"2096\">\n<li data-end=\"2113\" data-start=\"2096\">\n<p data-end=\"2113\" data-start=\"2098\">Grape-forward</p>\n</li>\n<li data-end=\"2123\" data-start=\"2114\">\n<p data-end=\"2123\" data-start=\"2116\">Sweet</p>\n</li>\n<li data-end=\"2134\" data-start=\"2124\">\n<p data-end=\"2134\" data-start=\"2126\">Fruity</p>\n</li>\n<li data-end=\"2151\" data-start=\"2135\">\n<p data-end=\"2151\" data-start=\"2137\">Earthy skunk</p>\n</li>\n</ul>\n</div>\n</div>",
