        "sku": "N/A",
        "metaDescription": "**Buy Gas Gang 1G Terp Sauce online in Canada at Mohawk Medibles**, your trusted Indigenous-owned cannabis dispensary. Shop this premium terp sauce concentrate ",
        "shortDescription": "**Buy Gas Gang 1G Terp Sauce online in Canada at Mohawk Medibles**, your trusted Indigenous-owned cannabis dispensary. Shop this premium terp sauce concentrate with 70%+ THC and enjoy fast Canada-wi...",
        "descriptionHTML": "<div class=\"tab-pane active\" id=\"tab-description\">\n<div class=\"detail-tab-desc detail-content-wrap\">\n<p>**Buy Gas Gang 1G Terp Sauce online in Canada at Mohawk Medibles**, your trusted Indigenous-owned cannabis dispensary. Shop this premium terp sauce concentrate with 70%+ THC and enjoy fast Canada-wide shipping with same-day processing. Order now for discreet delivery of authentic, high-quality concentrates sourced from trusted suppliers. Experience the intense flavour and potency that Gas Gang is known for, delivered straight to your door.</p>\n<h2>🧬 Concentrate Profile</h2>\n<h3>What is Terp Sauce?</h3>\n<p>Terp sauce, also known as terp juice or sauce, is a premium cannabis concentrate prized for its high terpene content and crystalline THCA formations. This extract preserves the full spectrum of cannabinoids and terpenes from the source material, resulting in exceptional flavour profiles and potent effects. The “sauce” consistency comes from a unique extraction and curing process that separates THCA crystals from the terpene-rich liquid, creating a product that delivers both intense potency and authentic strain flavours.</p>\n<h3>Gas Gang Quality Standards</h3>\n<p>Gas Gang concentrates are crafted using premium flower and advanced extraction techniques that preserve the plant’s natural terpene profile. Each batch undergoes careful processing to maintain the delicate balance between THCA crystals and terpene-rich sauce. With multiple strains available, you can explore different flavour profiles while enjoying consistent quality and potency across the Gas Gang line.</p>\n<h3>Cannabinoid Profile</h3>\n<ul>\n<li><strong>THC Content:</strong> 70%+ (high potency)</li>\n<li><strong>Concentrate Type:</strong> Terp sauce with THCA crystals</li>\n<li><strong>Extraction Method:</strong> Hydrocarbon extraction with specialized curing</li>\n<li><strong>Terpene Preservation:</strong> High terpene retention for authentic flavour</li>\n</ul>\n<h3>Appearance &amp; Consistency</h3>\n<p>Gas Gang Terp Sauce features visible THCA crystals suspended in a golden, terpene-rich liquid. The consistency ranges from slightly viscous to syrupy, depending on the strain and terpene content. The crystals may vary in size and can be dabbed separately or mixed with the sauce for a full-spectrum experience. The vibrant colour and aromatic profile are indicators of the high-quality extraction process.</p>\n<p>–</p>\n<h2>💡 Usage Guide</h2>\n<h3>Recommended Dosage</h3>\n<ul>\n<li><strong>Beginners:</strong> Start with much less than Rice gain size (0.01-0.02g) lower potency concentrates first</li>\n<li><strong>Experienced Users:</strong> Rice grain-sized amount (0.03-0.05g) per session</li>\n<li><strong>High Tolerance:</strong> 0.05-0.1g per session, adjust based on individual tolerance</li>\n</ul>\n<h3>Consumption Methods</h3>\n<ul>\n<li><strong>Dabbing:</strong> Use a dab rig with a quartz banger or e-nail at 315-370°C for optimal terpene preservation and flavour</li>\n<li><strong>Vaporizing:</strong> Use a concentrate-compatible vaporizer or dab pen designed for sauce consistency</li>\n<li><strong>Enhanced Flower:</strong> Add small amounts to bowls or joints for significantly increased potency</li>\n<li><strong>Crystal Separation:</strong> Some users prefer dabbing crystals and sauce separately to experience different effects</li>\n</ul>\n<h3>Onset &amp; Duration</h3>\n<ul>\n<li><strong>Onset:</strong> Immediate to 3 minutes</li>\n<li><strong>Peak Effects:</strong> 10-30 minutes after consumption</li>\n<li><strong>Duration:</strong> 2-4 hours depending on dose and tolerance</li>\n</ul>\n<h3>Best Use Cases</h3>\n<p>Ideal for experienced consumers seeking immediate, potent effects with exceptional flavour. Perfect for evening relaxation, creative sessions, or when you need fast-acting relief. The high terpene content provides strain-specific effects alongside the powerful THC content. Best reserved for times when you have no obligations and can fully enjoy the experience.</p>\n<p><strong>⚠️ Important Safety Information:</strong> Terp sauce contains very high THC levels (70%+) and is not suitable for beginners or those with low tolerance. Start with minimal amounts and wait 10-15 minutes before consuming more. Use proper dabbing equipment and never apply flame directly to concentrate. Store safely away from children and pets.</p>\n<h2>❓ Frequently Asked Questions</h2>\n<h3>What strains are available in Gas Gang 1G Terp Sauce?</h3>\n<p><strong>A:</strong> Gas Gang offers various strain options in their terp sauce line. Strain availability may vary, so check the product selection when ordering. Each strain maintains the high 70%+ THC potency while offering unique terpene profiles and flavour experiences specific to that cultivar.</p>\n<h3>How do I use Gas Gang Terp Sauce?</h3>\n<p><strong>A:</strong> Terp sauce is best consumed through dabbing using a dab rig at 315-370°C, or with a concentrate vaporizer. Use a small, rice grain-sized amount to start. You can dab the crystals and sauce together, or separate them for different experiences. Advanced users may also add small amounts to flower for enhanced potency.</p>\n<h3>How potent is Gas Gang Terp Sauce compared to flower?</h3>\n<p><strong>A:</strong> With 70%+ THC, terp sauce is approximately 3-4 times more potent than premium cannabis flower (typically 20-25% THC). This concentrate is designed for experienced consumers with established tolerance. If you’re new to concentrates, start with a very small amount and wait before consuming more.</p>\n<h3>How should I store my Gas Gang Terp Sauce?</h3>\n<p><strong>A:</strong> Store your terp sauce in its original container in a cool, dark place away from direct sunlight and heat sources. A refrigerator is ideal for long-term storage and helps preserve terpenes and potency. Always ensure the container is sealed tightly. Properly stored, terp sauce maintains quality for 6-12 months.</p>\n<h3>Is Gas Gang Terp Sauce suitable for beginners?</h3>\n<p><strong>A:</strong> No, terp sauce is a high-potency concentrate (70%+ THC) recommended only for experienced cannabis consumers. If you’re new to cannabis or concentrates, we recommend starting with flower or lower-potency products to build tolerance and understand your ideal dosage before trying concentrates.</p>\n<h3>Does Mohawk Medibles ship Gas Gang Terp Sauce across Canada?</h3>\n<p><strong>A:</strong> Yes! We offer fast, discreet Canada-wide shipping on all Gas Gang products with same-day processing on orders placed before 2 PM EST. All concentrates are packaged securely in plain, unmarked packaging to ensure safe delivery and complete privacy.</p>\n<h3>What makes terp sauce different from other concentrates?</h3>\n<p><strong>A:</strong> Terp sauce is unique because it preserves high levels of terpenes alongside THCA crystals, offering superior flavour compared to many other concentrates. The extraction and curing process creates a product that delivers both exceptional potency and authentic strain characteristics, making it a favourite among concentrate connoisseurs who value taste as much as effects.</p>\n</div>\n</div>",
