        "descriptionHTML": "<div class=\"tab-pane active\" id=\"tab-description\">\n<div class=\"detail-tab-desc detail-content-wrap\">\n<div><b>24-28% THC</b></div>\n<div>\n<p>**Buy Permanent Marker online in Canada at Mohawk Medibles**, your trusted Indigenous-owned cannabis dispensary. Shop this premium indica dominant hybrid strain and enjoy fast Canada-wide shipping with same-day processing. Order now for discreet delivery of this potent 24-28% THC powerhouse, sourced from Tyendinaga Mohawk Territory. Experience the exceptional quality and relaxing effects that make Permanent Marker a favourite among experienced cannabis enthusiasts across Canada.</p>\n<h2>🧬 Strain Profile</h2>\n<h3>Genetics &amp; Lineage</h3>\n<p>Permanent Marker boasts an impressive three-way genetic cross, combining the legendary Biscotti, the coveted Jealousy, and the flavourful Sherbet BX. This carefully curated lineage brings together the best traits from each parent strain: Biscotti’s rich, dessert-like terpene profile, Jealousy’s potent euphoric effects, and Sherbet BX’s balanced hybrid characteristics. The result is a sophisticated indica dominant hybrid that delivers both recreational enjoyment and therapeutic benefits.</p>\n<h3>Dominant Terpenes</h3>\n<p>The terpene profile of Permanent Marker is dominated by caryophyllene, limonene, and myrcene. Caryophyllene contributes spicy, peppery notes while offering potential anti-inflammatory properties. Limonene adds bright citrus undertones and may enhance mood, while myrcene provides the classic earthy, herbal foundation that amplifies the strain’s relaxing indica effects. This complex terpene combination creates a full-bodied aromatic experience.</p>\n<h3>Cannabinoid Profile</h3>\n<p>With an impressive THC content ranging from 34-35%, Permanent Marker ranks among the most potent strains available at Mohawk Medibles. This high cannabinoid concentration delivers powerful effects that are best suited for experienced consumers with established tolerance levels. The minimal CBD content means the psychoactive effects are pronounced and long-lasting.</p>\n<h3>Appearance &amp; Structure</h3>\n<p>Permanent Marker features dense, resinous buds covered in a thick layer of crystalline trichomes that give the flowers a frosted appearance. The vibrant green colour is complemented by deep purple hues and bright orange pistils, creating a visually striking presentation. The compact bud structure is characteristic of quality indica genetics.</p>\n<h3>Similar Strains</h3>\n<p>If you enjoy Permanent Marker, you might also appreciate Wedding Cake, Gelato, or Biscotti. These strains share similar dessert-like flavour profiles and potent indica dominant effects that promote deep relaxation and stress relief.</p>\n<h2>❓ Frequently Asked Questions</h2>\n<h3>Is Permanent Marker indica, sativa, or hybrid?</h3>\n<p><strong>A:</strong> Permanent Marker is a 70% indica / 30% sativa hybrid strain, offering predominantly relaxing and sedating effects with a subtle cerebral uplift. The indica dominance makes it perfect for evening use and stress relief.</p>\n<h3>What are the effects of Permanent Marker?</h3>\n<p><strong>A:</strong> Users report deep body relaxation, mental calm, stress relief, and sedation. This strain is commonly used for managing chronic pain, insomnia, anxiety, and tension. The high THC content delivers powerful effects that promote complete relaxation without overwhelming mental fog.</p>\n<h3>Is Permanent Marker suitable for daytime use?</h3>\n<p><strong>A:</strong> While the product description mentions daytime use for lazy afternoons, the high potency and indica dominance make Permanent Marker better suited for evening or weekend use when you can fully relax. It may cause drowsiness and reduced motivation, so avoid using before work or important tasks.</p>\n<h3>What does Permanent Marker taste and smell like?</h3>\n<p><strong>A:</strong> Permanent Marker features a complex flavour profile inherited from its Biscotti, Jealousy, and Sherbet BX lineage. Expect sweet, earthy, and slightly spicy notes with hints of citrus and cream. The aroma is pungent and distinctive with dessert-like undertones.</p>\n<h3>How should I store Permanent Marker?</h3>\n<p><strong>A:</strong> Store in an airtight container (glass mason jars work best) in a cool, dark place away from heat, light, and moisture. Proper storage preserves the potent THC content, terpene profile, and overall freshness for 6-12 months. Keep out of reach of children and pets.</p>\n<h3>Does Mohawk Medibles ship Permanent Marker across Canada?</h3>\n<p><strong>A:</strong> Yes! We offer fast, discreet Canada-wide shipping with same-day processing on orders placed before 2 PM EST. All packages arrive in plain, unmarked packaging to ensure privacy. Track your order from our dispensary in Tyendinaga Mohawk Territory directly to your door.</p>\n</div>\n</div>\n</div>",
