        "descriptionHTML": "<div class=\"tab-pane active\" id=\"tab-description\">\n<div class=\"detail-tab-desc detail-content-wrap\">\n<p>**Buy Tequila Sunrise Hash online in Canada at Mohawk Medibles**, your trusted Indigenous-owned cannabis dispensary. Shop this premium imported Mexican hash and enjoy fast Canada-wide shipping with same-day processing. Order now for discreet delivery of this rare, exotic concentrate straight from Tyendinaga Mohawk Territory. Experience authentic craftsmanship with the convenience of secure online ordering.</p>\n<p>–</p>\n<h2>💡 Usage Guide</h2>\n<h3>Recommended Dosage</h3>\n<ul>\n<li><strong>Beginners:</strong> Start with a rice grain-sized amount (approximately 0.025g). Hash is significantly more potent than flower.</li>\n<li><strong>Experienced Users:</strong> 0.05-0.1g per session, adjusting based on tolerance and desired effects.</li>\n<li><strong>High Tolerance:</strong> Up to 0.15g per session for seasoned concentrate consumers.</li>\n</ul>\n<h3>Consumption Methods</h3>\n<ul>\n<li><strong>Traditional Smoking:</strong> Crumble small pieces into joints, blunts, or mix with flower in pipes and bongs for enhanced potency.</li>\n<li><strong>Hot Knives:</strong> Classic method using heated knives to vaporize hash for immediate effects.</li>\n<li><strong>Vaporizing:</strong> Use hash-compatible vaporizer at 180-210°C for smooth, flavourful vapour.</li>\n<li><strong>Dabbing:</strong> Can be dabbed at lower temperatures (315-370°C) for a traditional hash experience with modern equipment.</li>\n<li><strong>Hash Edibles (Advanced):</strong> To make edibles, decarboxylate hash at 110-120°C (230-250°F) for 30-40 minutes to activate THC. Mix into butter or oil-based recipes. Effects take 30-120 minutes and last 6-12 hours. Hash edibles are significantly more potent than flower edibles—start with 1/4 of your normal flower edible dose.</li>\n</ul>\n<h3>Onset &amp; Duration</h3>\n<ul>\n<li><strong>Onset:</strong> 2-5 minutes when smoked or vaporized</li>\n<li><strong>Peak Effects:</strong> 15-45 minutes after consumption</li>\n<li><strong>Duration:</strong> 2-4 hours depending on dosage and tolerance</li>\n</ul>\n<h3>Best Use Cases</h3>\n<p>Perfect for experienced cannabis enthusiasts seeking authentic imported hash with unique flavour profiles. The citrusy-sweet notes make this ideal for evening relaxation, social sessions, or enhancing creative activities. Best enjoyed when you have time to savour the smooth, exotic smoking experience that only traditional Mexican hash can deliver.</p>\n<p><strong>⚠️ Important:</strong> Hash is more concentrated than regular flower. Start with minimal amounts and wait 15-20 minutes before consuming more to gauge effects. beginners should start with smaller amounts and lower potency products first.</p>\n<h2>❓ Frequently Asked Questions</h2>\n<h3>What is Tequila Sunrise Hash and where does it come from?</h3>\n<p><strong>A:</strong> Tequila Sunrise Hash is an imported concentrate from Mexico, crafted using traditional hash-making techniques. This exotic hash features a distinctive citrusy-sweet profile with earthy undertones, inspired by the classic Tequila Sunrise cocktail. It represents authentic Mexican cannabis craftsmanship rarely found in the Canadian market.</p>\n<h3>How do I use Tequila Sunrise Hash?</h3>\n<p><strong>A:</strong> You can crumble small pieces into joints or bowls, use the traditional hot knife method, vaporize it in a hash-compatible device at 180-210°C, or dab it at lower temperatures. Start with a rice grain-sized amount if you’re new to hash, as it’s more potent than regular flower.</p>\n<h3>How potent is Tequila Sunrise Hash compared to regular cannabis flower?</h3>\n<p><strong>A:</strong> Hash is significantly more concentrated than flower, typically containing 30-60% THC compared to 15-25% in most flower strains. Tequila Sunrise Hash delivers smooth, potent effects that are best suited for experienced cannabis users. Always start with less than you think you need.</p>\n<h3>Is Tequila Sunrise Hash suitable for beginners?</h3>\n<p><strong>A:</strong> Due to its concentrated potency, this hash is recommended for experienced cannabis consumers. If you’re new to concentrates but have experience with flower, start with a very small amount (rice grain size) and wait at least 15-20 minutes to assess effects before consuming more.</p>\n<h3>How should I store Tequila Sunrise Hash?</h3>\n<p><strong>A:</strong> Store your hash in an airtight container in a cool, dark place away from heat and direct sunlight. Parchment paper or silicone containers work well to prevent sticking. Properly stored hash can maintain its potency and flavour for 6-12 months or longer. Keep refrigerated for extended freshness.</p>\n<h3>Does Mohawk Medibles ship Tequila Sunrise Hash across Canada?</h3>\n<p><strong>A:</strong> Yes! We offer fast, discreet Canada-wide shipping on all our products, including this rare imported hash. Orders placed before 2 PM EST are processed the same day. All packages arrive in plain, unmarked packaging to ensure your privacy.</p>\n<h3>What makes imported Mexican hash different from Canadian concentrates?</h3>\n<p><strong>A:</strong> Traditional Mexican hash offers a unique flavour profile and texture that differs from modern Canadian concentrates. The hand-pressed techniques and regional cannabis varieties create distinctive characteristics you won’t find in domestically produced extracts. Tequila Sunrise Hash brings authentic international cannabis culture to Canadian consumers.</p>\n</div>\n</div>",
