        "descriptionHTML": "<div class=\"tab-pane active\" id=\"tab-description\">\n<div class=\"detail-tab-desc detail-content-wrap\">\n<p>**Buy Adalya Hookah Tobacco online in Canada at Mohawk Medibles**, your trusted Indigenous-owned tobacco and cannabis dispensary. Shop this premium hookah tobacco blend and enjoy fast Canada-wide shipping with same-day processing on orders placed before 2 PM EST. Order Adalya Blue Dragon now for discreet delivery and experience authentic, high-quality hookah tobacco sourced from trusted suppliers. Perfect for social sessions and smooth, flavourful smoke.</p>\n<p>–</p>\n<h2>💡 Usage Guide</h2>\n<h3>Recommended Amount</h3>\n<ul>\n<li><strong>Standard Bowl:</strong> 15-20g of tobacco for a typical hookah session</li>\n<li><strong>Small Bowl:</strong> 10-15g for shorter, personal sessions</li>\n<li><strong>Large Bowl:</strong> 20-30g for extended group sessions</li>\n</ul>\n<h3>Preparation Methods</h3>\n<ul>\n<li><strong>Fluff Pack:</strong> Lightly sprinkle tobacco into bowl without pressing down, allowing airflow for smoother smoke</li>\n<li><strong>Dense Pack:</strong> Firmly pack tobacco for longer-lasting sessions and stronger flavour</li>\n<li><strong>Semi-Dense Pack:</strong> Moderate packing for balanced smoke duration and flavour intensity</li>\n</ul>\n<h3>Session Duration</h3>\n<ul>\n<li><strong>Heat-Up Time:</strong> 5-10 minutes with proper coal placement</li>\n<li><strong>Optimal Smoking:</strong> 45-90 minutes depending on bowl size and pack method</li>\n<li><strong>Flavour Peak:</strong> First 30-45 minutes provide the richest taste</li>\n</ul>\n<h3>Best Use Cases</h3>\n<p>Ideal for social gatherings, relaxing evenings, and creating memorable experiences with friends. The Blue Dragon blend’s smooth smoke and rich flavour profile makes it perfect for both experienced hookah enthusiasts and those new to shisha. Best enjoyed in comfortable settings where you can savour the tropical dragon fruit and blueberry notes.</p>\n<h2>❓ Frequently Asked Questions</h2>\n<h3>What flavours are in Adalya Blue Dragon hookah tobacco?</h3>\n<p><strong>A:</strong> Adalya Blue Dragon features a premium blend combining the tropical sweetness of dragon fruit with the rich, juicy notes of ripe blueberries. This creates a smooth, fruity smoking experience that’s both refreshing and satisfying for hookah enthusiasts.</p>\n<h3>How should I store Adalya hookah tobacco?</h3>\n<p><strong>A:</strong> Store your Adalya tobacco in its original sealed packaging or transfer to an airtight container. Keep it in a cool, dark place away from direct sunlight and heat sources. Properly stored hookah tobacco maintains its moisture and flavour for 6-12 months. If it becomes dry, you can revive it with a few drops of glycerin or molasses.</p>\n<h3>Is Adalya hookah tobacco suitable for beginners?</h3>\n<p><strong>A:</strong> Yes, Adalya is excellent for beginners due to its smooth smoke, easy-to-pack consistency, and forgiving nature. The Blue Dragon flavour is particularly approachable with its sweet, fruity profile that’s not overwhelming. Start with a fluff pack method and moderate heat for the best first-time experience.</p>\n<h3>Does Mohawk Medibles ship Adalya hookah tobacco across Canada?</h3>\n<p><strong>A:</strong> Absolutely! We offer fast, discreet Canada-wide shipping on all hookah tobacco products. Orders placed before 2 PM EST are processed the same day. All packages arrive in plain, unmarked packaging to ensure your privacy.</p>\n<h3>How much hookah tobacco do I need per session?</h3>\n<p><strong>A:</strong> For a standard session lasting 60-90 minutes, use 15-20g of Adalya tobacco. A typical 50g package provides 2-3 full sessions, while a 250g container offers 12-15 sessions. The amount varies based on your bowl size and packing method.</p>\n<h3>What makes Adalya hookah tobacco high quality?</h3>\n<p><strong>A:</strong> Adalya is crafted using premium Virginia tobacco leaves combined with high-quality flavourings, glycerin, and molasses. The brand is known for consistent moisture levels, rich flavour profiles, and smooth smoke production. Each batch undergoes quality control to ensure the authentic taste and performance hookah enthusiasts expect.</p>\n<h3>Can I mix Adalya Blue Dragon with other flavours?</h3>\n<p><strong>A:</strong> Yes, Adalya blends exceptionally well with other flavours. Blue Dragon pairs beautifully with mint, citrus, or other berry flavours. Try mixing 70% Blue Dragon with 30% mint for a refreshing twist, or combine with other tropical flavours for a custom fruit medley. Experiment to find your perfect blend.</p>\n</div>\n</div>",
