        "descriptionHTML": "<div class=\"tab-pane active\" id=\"tab-description\">\n<div class=\"detail-tab-desc detail-content-wrap\">\n<p>**Buy Nature’s Magic Earl Grey Psilocybin Tea online in Canada at Mohawk Medibles**, your trusted Indigenous-owned dispensary for premium psychedelic products. Shop this convenient and flavourful psilocybin tea available in three potency options (200mg, 500mg, and 1000mg per bag) and enjoy fast Canada-wide shipping with discreet delivery. Order now for same-day processing and experience the perfect blend of classic Earl Grey flavour with precisely dosed psilocybin mushrooms from Tyendinaga Mohawk Territory.</p>\n<p>–</p>\n<h2>💡 Usage Guide</h2>\n<h3>Recommended Dosage</h3>\n<ul>\n<li><strong>Beginners (200mg bags):</strong> Start with one full tea bag steeped for 10-15 minutes. This microdose level is ideal for subtle mood enhancement and creativity without overwhelming effects.</li>\n<li><strong>Intermediate Users (500mg bags):</strong> One tea bag provides a moderate psychedelic experience suitable for introspection, enhanced sensory perception, and emotional exploration.</li>\n<li><strong>Experienced Users (1000mg bags):</strong> One tea bag delivers a full psychedelic journey. Only recommended for those familiar with higher-dose psilocybin experiences.</li>\n</ul>\n<h3>Preparation Method</h3>\n<ul>\n<li><strong>Brewing:</strong> Steep one tea bag in 250-300ml of hot (not boiling) water for 10-15 minutes. Water temperature should be around 70-80°C to preserve psilocybin potency.</li>\n<li><strong>Enhancement:</strong> Add honey, lemon, or milk to taste. Lemon may slightly enhance absorption.</li>\n<li><strong>Consumption:</strong> Drink slowly over 15-20 minutes on an empty or light stomach for optimal absorption.</li>\n</ul>\n<h3>Onset &amp; Duration</h3>\n<ul>\n<li><strong>Onset:</strong> 20-45 minutes when consumed on an empty stomach</li>\n<li><strong>Peak Effects:</strong> 1-2 hours after consumption</li>\n<li><strong>Duration:</strong> 4-6 hours total experience, with after-effects lasting up to 8 hours</li>\n</ul>\n<h3>Best Use Cases</h3>\n<p>Ideal for therapeutic introspection, creative exploration, or spiritual experiences in a comfortable, safe setting. The tea format provides gentler onset than eating raw mushrooms and is easier on the stomach. Best consumed during daytime or early evening when you have no obligations. Always ensure you’re in a safe environment with trusted companions if desired.</p>\n<p><strong>⚠️ Important Safety Information:</strong> Psilocybin is a powerful psychedelic substance. Do not drive or operate machinery. Not recommended for individuals with personal or family history of psychosis or severe mental health conditions. Start with lower doses to assess your sensitivity. Set and setting are crucial for positive experiences.</p>\n<h2>❓ Frequently Asked Questions</h2>\n<h3>What’s the difference between the 200mg, 500mg, and 1000mg options?</h3>\n<p><strong>A:</strong> The 200mg bags (5 per pack) provide microdosing experiences with subtle effects ideal for beginners or functional use. The 500mg bags (2 per pack) offer moderate psychedelic experiences suitable for intermediate users seeking introspection and sensory enhancement. The 1000mg bags (2 per pack) deliver full psychedelic journeys recommended only for experienced users comfortable with higher-dose psilocybin.</p>\n<h3>How does psilocybin tea compare to eating mushrooms directly?</h3>\n<p><strong>A:</strong> Psilocybin tea offers several advantages: faster onset (20-45 minutes vs. 30-90 minutes), reduced nausea and digestive discomfort, more predictable dosing, and pleasant Earl Grey flavour that masks the earthy mushroom taste. The effects are similar in quality but tea may have a slightly shorter duration due to faster absorption.</p>\n<h3>Can I adjust the strength by steeping time or water amount?</h3>\n<p><strong>A:</strong> Steeping time affects flavour more than potency—10-15 minutes extracts most psilocybin effectively. Using more water dilutes the tea but doesn’t reduce total psilocybin content. For lower doses, consider splitting a tea bag between multiple cups or choosing the 200mg option. Never exceed one bag per session without prior experience at that dose level.</p>\n<h3>Is Nature’s Magic Earl Grey Psilocybin Tea legal in Canada?</h3>\n<p><strong>A:</strong> Psilocybin remains a controlled substance in Canada, though enforcement and regulations are evolving. Mohawk Medibles operates from Tyendinaga Mohawk Territory with Indigenous sovereignty considerations. We ship discreetly across Canada. Customers are responsible for understanding their local regulations regarding psilocybin products.</p>\n<h3>How should I store my psilocybin tea bags?</h3>\n<p><strong>A:</strong> Store tea bags in their original packaging in a cool, dark, and dry place away from direct sunlight and heat. Properly stored, psilocybin tea maintains potency for 6-12 months. Keep in an airtight container if packaging is opened. Always store securely out of reach of children and pets.</p>\n<h3>Does Mohawk Medibles ship Nature’s Magic tea across Canada?</h3>\n<p><strong>A:</strong> Yes! We offer fast, discreet Canada-wide shipping with same-day processing on orders placed before 2 PM EST. All packages arrive in plain, unmarked packaging with no indication of contents. Track your order from Tyendinaga Mohawk Territory to your door with confidence.</p>\n<h3>What if I’m new to psilocybin—which option should I choose?</h3>\n<p><strong>A:</strong> First-time users should start with the 200mg bags. This microdose level allows you to experience subtle effects and gauge your sensitivity without overwhelming experiences. You can always increase dosage in future sessions once you understand how psilocybin affects you personally. Remember: you can always take more next time, but you can’t take less once consumed.</p>\n</div>\n</div>",
