        "descriptionHTML": "<div class=\"tab-pane active\" id=\"tab-description\">\n<div class=\"detail-tab-desc detail-content-wrap\">\n<h2 data-end=\"228\" data-start=\"189\">🖤 <strong data-end=\"226\" data-start=\"194\">Kabul Hash – $6/Gram Special</strong></h2>\n<p data-end=\"288\" data-start=\"229\"><strong data-end=\"288\" data-start=\"229\">Premium Afghanistan-Style Hash • Deep • Potent • Earthy</strong></p>\n<hr/>\n<p data-end=\"844\" data-start=\"719\">Kabul Hash is crafted for smokers who want <strong data-end=\"797\" data-start=\"762\">strong, traditional Afghan hash</strong> with a rich flavour and a heavy, calming high.</p>\n<p data-end=\"1119\" data-start=\"846\"><strong data-end=\"870\" data-start=\"846\">From the first look,</strong> you’ll notice its signature style—dark brown to almost black on the outside, with a lighter golden-brown centre when broken open.<br data-end=\"1003\" data-start=\"1000\"/><strong data-end=\"1020\" data-start=\"1003\">When touched,</strong> the texture becomes even more telling: soft, warm, and easy to mold, just like true Kabul imports.</p>\n<p data-end=\"1336\" data-start=\"1121\"><strong data-end=\"1154\" data-start=\"1121\">As you take your first smell,</strong> waves of deep earth, spice, and wood rise up.<br data-end=\"1203\" data-start=\"1200\"/><strong data-end=\"1222\" data-start=\"1203\">Then, once lit,</strong> the flavour becomes full and smooth, offering a rich, creamy smoke with natural Afghani spice and a clean finish.</p>\n<p data-end=\"1676\" data-start=\"1338\"><strong data-end=\"1371\" data-start=\"1338\">Soon after your first inhale,</strong> the high settles in. With THC levels ranging from <strong data-end=\"1432\" data-start=\"1422\">25–40%</strong>, Kabul Hash brings a strong body melt paired with a warm, hazy calm in the mind.<br data-end=\"1516\" data-start=\"1513\"/><strong data-end=\"1541\" data-start=\"1516\">As the effects build,</strong> tension releases, stress fades, and your whole body enters a deep, peaceful state—ideal for evenings, pain relief, or quiet nights in.</p>\n<p data-end=\"1799\" data-start=\"1678\">This hash is perfect for anyone who wants <strong data-end=\"1785\" data-start=\"1720\">potent strength, classic flavour, and old-world craftsmanship</strong> in every hit.</p>\n<hr data-end=\"1804\" data-start=\"1801\"/>\n<h3 data-end=\"1824\" data-start=\"1806\">🔥 <strong data-end=\"1822\" data-start=\"1811\">EFFECTS</strong></h3>\n<ul data-end=\"1936\" data-start=\"1825\">\n<li data-end=\"1849\" data-start=\"1825\">\n<p data-end=\"1849\" data-start=\"1827\">Deep body relaxation</p>\n</li>\n<li data-end=\"1864\" data-start=\"1850\">\n<p data-end=\"1864\" data-start=\"1852\">Heavy calm</p>\n</li>\n<li data-end=\"1888\" data-start=\"1865\">\n<p data-end=\"1888\" data-start=\"1867\">Warm, hazy euphoria</p>\n</li>\n<li data-end=\"1906\" data-start=\"1889\">\n<p data-end=\"1906\" data-start=\"1891\">Stress relief</p>\n</li>\n<li data-end=\"1936\" data-start=\"1907\">\n<p data-end=\"1936\" data-start=\"1909\">Peaceful nighttime unwind</p>\n</li>\n</ul>\n<hr data-end=\"1941\" data-start=\"1938\"/>\n<h3 data-end=\"1967\" data-start=\"1943\">🌿 <strong data-end=\"1965\" data-start=\"1948\">MAY HELP WITH</strong></h3>\n<ul data-end=\"2056\" data-start=\"1968\">\n<li data-end=\"1984\" data-start=\"1968\">\n<p data-end=\"1984\" data-start=\"1970\">Chronic pain</p>\n</li>\n<li data-end=\"1995\" data-start=\"1985\">\n<p data-end=\"1995\" data-start=\"1987\">Stress</p>\n</li>\n<li data-end=\"2007\" data-start=\"1996\">\n<p data-end=\"2007\" data-start=\"1998\">Anxiety</p>\n</li>\n<li data-end=\"2020\" data-start=\"2008\">\n<p data-end=\"2020\" data-start=\"2010\">Insomnia</p>\n</li>\n<li data-end=\"2039\" data-start=\"2021\">\n<p data-end=\"2039\" data-start=\"2023\">Muscle tension</p>\n</li>\n<li data-end=\"2056\" data-start=\"2040\">\n<p data-end=\"2056\" data-start=\"2042\">Restlessness</p>\n</li>\n</ul>\n<hr data-end=\"2061\" data-start=\"2058\"/>\n<h3 data-end=\"2081\" data-start=\"2063\">🖤 <strong data-end=\"2079\" data-start=\"2068\">FLAVORS</strong></h3>\n<ul data-end=\"2162\" data-start=\"2082\">\n<li data-end=\"2092\" data-start=\"2082\">\n<p data-end=\"2092\" data-start=\"2084\">Earthy</p>\n</li>\n<li data-end=\"2102\" data-start=\"2093\">\n<p data-end=\"2102\" data-start=\"2095\">Spicy</p>\n</li>\n<li data-end=\"2112\" data-start=\"2103\">\n<p data-end=\"2112\" data-start=\"2105\">Woody</p>\n</li>\n<li data-end=\"2135\" data-start=\"2113\">\n<p data-end=\"2135\" data-start=\"2115\">Rich + smooth hash</p>\n</li>\n<li data-end=\"2162\" data-start=\"2136\">\n<p data-end=\"2162\" data-start=\"2138\">Classic Afghan profile</p>\n</li>\n</ul>\n<hr data-end=\"2167\" data-start=\"2164\"/>\n<h3 data-end=\"2187\" data-start=\"2169\">🌬️ <strong data-end=\"2185\" data-start=\"2175\">AROMAS</strong></h3>\n<ul data-end=\"2266\" data-start=\"2188\">\n<li data-end=\"2202\" data-start=\"2188\">\n<p data-end=\"2202\" data-start=\"2190\">Deep earth</p>\n</li>\n<li data-end=\"2217\" data-start=\"2203\">\n<p data-end=\"2217\" data-start=\"2205\">Warm spice</p>\n</li>\n<li data-end=\"2236\" data-start=\"2218\">\n<p data-end=\"2236\" data-start=\"2220\">Wood and herbs</p>\n</li>\n<li data-end=\"2266\" data-start=\"2237\">\n<p data-end=\"2266\" data-start=\"2239\">Traditional Afghani scent</p>\n</li>\n</ul>\n<hr/>\n<h2>💡 Usage Guide</h2>\n<h3>Recommended Dosage</h3>\n<ul>\n<li><strong>Beginners:</strong> Start with a rice grain-sized piece (approximately 0.025-0.05g). Hash is significantly more potent than flower.</li>\n<li><strong>Experienced Users:</strong> 0.1-0.2g per session, adjusting based on tolerance and desired effects.</li>\n<li><strong>High Tolerance:</strong> Up to 0.3g per session for seasoned concentrate consumers.</li>\n</ul>\n<h3>Consumption Methods</h3>\n<ul>\n<li><strong>Smoking:</strong> Crumble and mix with flower in joints, pipes, or bongs for enhanced potency and traditional experience.</li>\n<li><strong>Vaporizing:</strong> Use hash-compatible vaporizer at 180-210°C for smooth, flavourful vapour with maximum terpene preservation.</li>\n<li><strong>Hot Knives:</strong> Traditional method heating two knives and pressing hash between them for immediate effects.</li>\n<li><strong>Topping Bowls:</strong> Add small pieces atop flower bowls for elevated potency without altering your regular routine.</li>\n<li><strong>Hash Edibles (Advanced):</strong> To make edibles, decarboxylate hash at 110-120°C (230-250°F) for 30-40 minutes to activate THC. Mix into butter or oil-based recipes. Effects take 30-120 minutes and last 6-12 hours. Hash edibles are significantly more potent than flower edibles—start with 1/4 of your normal flower edible dose.</li>\n</ul>\n<h3>Onset &amp; Duration</h3>\n<ul>\n<li><strong>Onset (Smoking/Vaping):</strong> 2-10 minutes</li>\n<li><strong>Onset (Edibles):</strong> 30-120 minutes</li>\n<li><strong>Peak Effects:</strong> 15-45 minutes (inhaled) or 2-4 hours (edibles)</li>\n<li><strong>Duration:</strong> 2-4 hours (inhaled) or 6-12 hours (edibles)</li>\n</ul>\n<p><strong>⚠️ Important:</strong> Hash is significantly more potent than regular flower. Start with minimal amounts and wait to assess effects before consuming more. for experienced users – beginners should start with lower doses or those new to concentrates.</p>\n</div>\n</div>",
