        "shortDescription": "Larry Burger LA Mousse Hash brings bold flavour and powerful relaxation together in a premium, solventless concentrate. To begin with, this indica-dominant hybrid (70% indica / 30% sativa) comes fro...",
        "descriptionHTML": "<div class=\"tab-pane active\" id=\"tab-description\">\n<div class=\"detail-tab-desc detail-content-wrap\">\n<p data-end=\"841\" data-start=\"519\"><strong data-end=\"550\" data-start=\"519\">Larry Burger LA Mousse Hash</strong> brings bold flavour and powerful relaxation together in a premium, solventless concentrate. To begin with, this <strong data-end=\"715\" data-start=\"663\">indica-dominant hybrid (70% indica / 30% sativa)</strong> comes from the legendary pairing of <strong data-end=\"778\" data-start=\"752\">GMO Cookies × Larry OG</strong>, a lineage known for potency, depth, and unmistakable flavour.</p>\n<p data-end=\"1235\" data-start=\"843\">Right away, the effects begin to settle in 🧠➡️🛋️. First, the mind lifts into a calm, happy state, easing stress and quieting racing thoughts. Shortly after, a heavy body relaxation follows, spreading through the limbs and encouraging you to slow down and get comfortable. Because of this progression, Larry Burger is ideal for evening sessions, movie nights, or curling up with a good book.</p>\n<p data-end=\"1489\" data-start=\"1237\">As the experience deepens, the high becomes soothing and immersive 🌙. The body feels loose and relaxed, while the mind stays pleasantly euphoric. At higher doses, sleep often comes easily, making this hash a favourite for winding down after long days.</p>\n<p data-end=\"1752\" data-start=\"1491\">Meanwhile, the flavour profile keeps things rich and memorable 🍪🥩. Sweet cookie notes hit first, followed by a savory, slightly funky finish true to its GMO roots. Earthy kush undertones round out the smoke, delivering a smooth, full-bodied pull that lingers.</p>\n<p data-end=\"1954\" data-start=\"1754\">Because this is <strong data-end=\"1788\" data-start=\"1770\">LA Mousse Hash</strong>, the texture stays <strong data-end=\"1838\" data-start=\"1808\">light, fluffy, and aerated</strong>. As a result, it’s easy to handle, melts cleanly, and burns evenly whether mixed with flower or enjoyed on its own.</p>\n<hr data-end=\"1959\" data-start=\"1956\"/>\n<h3 data-end=\"1986\" data-start=\"1961\">✨ Effects You’ll Feel</h3>\n<ul data-end=\"2121\" data-start=\"1987\">\n<li data-end=\"2014\" data-start=\"1987\">\n<p data-end=\"2014\" data-start=\"1989\">😌 Deep body relaxation</p>\n</li>\n<li data-end=\"2042\" data-start=\"2015\">\n<p data-end=\"2042\" data-start=\"2017\">😊 Euphoric, happy mood</p>\n</li>\n<li data-end=\"2069\" data-start=\"2043\">\n<p data-end=\"2069\" data-start=\"2045\">🛋️ Couch-locking calm</p>\n</li>\n<li data-end=\"2100\" data-start=\"2070\">\n<p data-end=\"2100\" data-start=\"2072\">🌙 Sleep-friendly sedation</p>\n</li>\n<li data-end=\"2121\" data-start=\"2101\">\n<p data-end=\"2121\" data-start=\"2103\">🧘 Stress relief</p>\n</li>\n</ul>\n<hr data-end=\"2126\" data-start=\"2123\"/>\n<h3 data-end=\"2154\" data-start=\"2128\">🩺 Commonly Chosen For</h3>\n<ul data-end=\"2244\" data-start=\"2155\">\n<li data-end=\"2175\" data-start=\"2155\">\n<p data-end=\"2175\" data-start=\"2157\">Stress &amp; anxiety</p>\n</li>\n<li data-end=\"2192\" data-start=\"2176\">\n<p data-end=\"2192\" data-start=\"2178\">Chronic pain</p>\n</li>\n<li data-end=\"2208\" data-start=\"2193\">\n<p data-end=\"2208\" data-start=\"2195\">Mood swings</p>\n</li>\n<li data-end=\"2221\" data-start=\"2209\">\n<p data-end=\"2221\" data-start=\"2211\">Insomnia</p>\n</li>\n<li data-end=\"2244\" data-start=\"2222\">\n<p data-end=\"2244\" data-start=\"2224\">Evening relaxation</p>\n</li>\n</ul>\n<hr data-end=\"2249\" data-start=\"2246\"/>\n<h3 data-end=\"2271\" data-start=\"2251\">🍪 Flavour Notes</h3>\n<ul data-end=\"2337\" data-start=\"2272\">\n<li data-end=\"2288\" data-start=\"2272\">\n<p data-end=\"2288\" data-start=\"2274\">Sweet cookie</p>\n</li>\n<li data-end=\"2304\" data-start=\"2289\">\n<p data-end=\"2304\" data-start=\"2291\">Savory funk</p>\n</li>\n<li data-end=\"2320\" data-start=\"2305\">\n<p data-end=\"2320\" data-start=\"2307\">Earthy kush</p>\n</li>\n<li data-end=\"2337\" data-start=\"2321\">\n<p data-end=\"2337\" data-start=\"2323\">Subtle spice</p>\n</li>\n</ul>\n<hr data-end=\"2342\" data-start=\"2339\"/>\n<h3 data-end=\"2365\" data-start=\"2344\">🌬️ Aroma Profile</h3>\n<ul data-end=\"2425\" data-start=\"2366\">\n<li data-end=\"2376\" data-start=\"2366\">\n<p data-end=\"2376\" data-start=\"2368\">Earthy</p>\n</li>\n<li data-end=\"2387\" data-start=\"2377\">\n<p data-end=\"2387\" data-start=\"2379\">Herbal</p>\n</li>\n<li data-end=\"2406\" data-start=\"2388\">\n<p data-end=\"2406\" data-start=\"2390\">Sweet &amp; savory</p>\n</li>\n<li data-end=\"2425\" data-start=\"2407\">\n<p data-end=\"2425\" data-start=\"2409\">Light pungency</p>\n</li>\n</ul>\n<hr data-end=\"2430\" data-start=\"2427\"/>\n<h3 data-end=\"2481\" data-start=\"2432\">💎 Why Larry Burger LA Mousse Hash Stands Out</h3>\n<ul data-end=\"2661\" data-start=\"2482\">\n<li data-end=\"2513\" data-start=\"2482\">\n<p data-end=\"2513\" data-start=\"2484\">Strong <strong data-end=\"2513\" data-start=\"2491\">20–33% THC potency</strong></p>\n</li>\n<li data-end=\"2548\" data-start=\"2514\">\n<p data-end=\"2548\" data-start=\"2516\">Premium <strong data-end=\"2548\" data-start=\"2524\">solventless dry sift</strong></p>\n</li>\n<li data-end=\"2590\" data-start=\"2549\">\n<p data-end=\"2590\" data-start=\"2551\">Light, aerated <strong data-end=\"2590\" data-start=\"2566\">French Touch texture</strong></p>\n</li>\n<li data-end=\"2620\" data-start=\"2591\">\n<p data-end=\"2620\" data-start=\"2593\">Rich dessert-savory flavour</p>\n</li>\n<li data-end=\"2661\" data-start=\"2621\">\n<p data-end=\"2661\" data-start=\"2623\">Perfect for evenings and sleep support</p>\n</li>\n</ul>\n<hr/>\n<h2>💡 Usage Guide</h2>\n<h3>Recommended Dosage</h3>\n<ul>\n<li><strong>Beginners:</strong> Start with a rice grain-sized piece (approximately 0.025-0.05g). Hash is significantly more potent than flower.</li>\n<li><strong>Experienced Users:</strong> 0.1-0.2g per session, adjusting based on tolerance and desired effects.</li>\n<li><strong>High Tolerance:</strong> Up to 0.3g per session for seasoned concentrate consumers.</li>\n</ul>\n<h3>Consumption Methods</h3>\n<ul>\n<li><strong>Smoking:</strong> Crumble and mix with flower in joints, pipes, or bongs for enhanced potency and traditional experience.</li>\n<li><strong>Vaporizing:</strong> Use hash-compatible vaporizer at 180-210°C for smooth, flavourful vapour with maximum terpene preservation.</li>\n<li><strong>Hot Knives:</strong> Traditional method heating two knives and pressing hash between them for immediate effects.</li>\n<li><strong>Topping Bowls:</strong> Add small pieces atop flower bowls for elevated potency without altering your regular routine.</li>\n<li><strong>Hash Edibles (Advanced):</strong> To make edibles, decarboxylate hash at 110-120°C (230-250°F) for 30-40 minutes to activate THC. Mix into butter or oil-based recipes. Effects take 30-120 minutes and last 6-12 hours. Hash edibles are significantly more potent than flower edibles—start with 1/4 of your normal flower edible dose.</li>\n</ul>\n<h3>Onset &amp; Duration</h3>\n<ul>\n<li><strong>Onset (Smoking/Vaping):</strong> 2-10 minutes</li>\n<li><strong>Onset (Edibles):</strong> 30-120 minutes</li>\n<li><strong>Peak Effects:</strong> 15-45 minutes (inhaled) or 2-4 hours (edibles)</li>\n<li><strong>Duration:</strong> 2-4 hours (inhaled) or 6-12 hours (edibles)</li>\n</ul>\n<p><strong>⚠️ Important:</strong> Hash is significantly more potent than regular flower. Start with minimal amounts and wait to assess effects before consuming more. for experienced users – beginners should start with lower doses or those new to concentrates.</p>\n</div>\n</div>",
