        "descriptionHTML": "<div class=\"tab-pane active\" id=\"tab-description\">\n<div class=\"detail-tab-desc detail-content-wrap\">\n<p>**Buy Beast Duo 20mg Nicotine Pouches online in Canada at Mohawk Medibles**, your trusted Indigenous-owned retailer for premium nicotine alternatives. Shop this innovative dual-flavor nicotine pouch and enjoy fast Canada-wide shipping with same-day processing. Order now for discreet delivery and experience the convenience of tobacco-free nicotine satisfaction from a dispensary you can trust.</p>\n<p>–</p>\n<h2>💡 Usage Guide</h2>\n<h3>Recommended Dosage</h3>\n<ul>\n<li><strong>New Users:</strong> Start with one pouch for 15-20 minutes to assess tolerance. 20mg is a strong dose.</li>\n<li><strong>Experienced Users:</strong> Use 1-2 pouches per session, spacing usage by at least 30-60 minutes.</li>\n<li><strong>Daily Limit:</strong> Do not exceed 15 pouches per day. Monitor your nicotine intake carefully.</li>\n</ul>\n<h3>How to Use</h3>\n<ul>\n<li><strong>Placement:</strong> Place one pouch between your upper lip and gum, positioning it comfortably to one side.</li>\n<li><strong>Duration:</strong> Keep the pouch in place for 20-40 minutes for optimal nicotine absorption.</li>\n<li><strong>Do Not Chew or Swallow:</strong> The pouch is designed to release nicotine gradually through the gum. Dispose of used pouches responsibly.</li>\n<li><strong>Rotate Placement:</strong> Alternate sides of your mouth to prevent gum irritation with regular use.</li>\n</ul>\n<h3>Onset &amp; Duration</h3>\n<ul>\n<li><strong>Onset:</strong> 3-5 minutes for initial effects</li>\n<li><strong>Peak Effects:</strong> 10-15 minutes after placement</li>\n<li><strong>Duration:</strong> Effects last 30-60 minutes depending on usage time</li>\n</ul>\n<h3>Best Use Cases</h3>\n<p>Perfect for discreet nicotine satisfaction throughout the day when smoking or vaping isn’t convenient. Ideal for work environments, travel, social settings, or anywhere tobacco use is restricted. The dual-flavor experience makes this an excellent choice for users seeking variety and stronger nicotine delivery.</p>\n<p><strong>⚠️ Important:</strong> This product contains nicotine, which is highly addictive. Not recommended for non-smokers, pregnant or nursing women, or individuals with heart conditions. Keep out of reach of children and pets. For adult use only (19+).</p>\n<h2>❓ Frequently Asked Questions</h2>\n<h3>What is the nicotine strength of Beast Duo pouches?</h3>\n<p><strong>A:</strong> Beast Duo contains 20mg of nicotine per pouch, which is considered a strong dose. This strength is best suited for experienced nicotine users or those transitioning from heavy cigarette use. If you’re new to nicotine pouches, consider starting with a lower strength product.</p>\n<h3>Are Beast Duo nicotine pouches tobacco-free?</h3>\n<p><strong>A:</strong> Yes, Beast Duo pouches are completely tobacco-free and made with synthetic nicotine. They contain no tobacco leaf, which means no tobacco-specific impurities, cleaner nicotine delivery, and no staining of teeth. You get pure nicotine satisfaction without the tobacco.</p>\n<h3>What does “dual flavor” mean?</h3>\n<p><strong>A:</strong> Beast Duo features two distinct flavors in one can, giving you variety and choice with every use. This innovative approach lets you switch between flavors based on your mood or preference, providing a more dynamic nicotine pouch experience compared to single-flavor options.</p>\n<h3>How long does a can of Beast Duo last?</h3>\n<p><strong>A:</strong> Each can contains multiple pouches (quantity varies by package). For moderate users consuming 5-8 pouches daily, one can typically lasts 2-4 days. Store in a cool, dry place and reseal the can after each use to maintain freshness and moisture content.</p>\n<h3>Can I use Beast Duo pouches on airplanes or in public places?</h3>\n<p><strong>A:</strong> Yes, nicotine pouches are discreet and produce no smoke, vapor, or odor, making them suitable for use in most environments where smoking and vaping are prohibited. However, always check local regulations and venue policies regarding nicotine product use.</p>\n<h3>Does Mohawk Medibles ship Beast Duo across Canada?</h3>\n<p><strong>A:</strong> Yes! We offer fast, discreet Canada-wide shipping on all nicotine pouch products with same-day processing on orders placed before 2 PM EST. All packages arrive in plain, unmarked packaging. You must be 19+ with valid ID to purchase and receive nicotine products.</p>\n<h3>Are there any side effects from using nicotine pouches?</h3>\n<p><strong>A:</strong> Some users may experience hiccups, nausea, mouth irritation, or increased heart rate, especially when first starting or using high-strength pouches like the 20mg Beast Duo. If you experience discomfort, remove the pouch immediately. Start with shorter usage times and gradually increase as your tolerance develops. Consult a healthcare provider if you have concerns about nicotine use.</p>\n</div>\n</div>",
