        "descriptionHTML": "<div class=\"tab-pane active\" id=\"tab-description\">\n<div class=\"detail-tab-desc detail-content-wrap\">\n<p>**Buy Metal Pipe with Screens online in Canada at Mohawk Medibles**, your trusted Indigenous-owned cannabis accessory supplier. Shop this durable, high-grade metal pipe set and enjoy fast Canada-wide shipping with same-day processing. Order now for discreet delivery from Tyendinaga Mohawk Territory. Perfect for on-the-go cannabis enthusiasts who value reliability and portability, this complete pipe set includes 5 premium screens for immediate use.</p>\n<p>–</p>\n<h2>💡 Usage Guide</h2>\n<h3>How to Use Your Metal Pipe</h3>\n<ul>\n<li><strong>Insert Screen:</strong> Place one of the included pipe screens into the bowl to prevent debris from being inhaled and ensure smooth airflow</li>\n<li><strong>Pack the Bowl:</strong> Grind your cannabis flower and gently pack into the bowl without over-compressing</li>\n<li><strong>Light and Inhale:</strong> Apply flame to the bowl while inhaling slowly through the mouthpiece</li>\n<li><strong>Clear the Chamber:</strong> Remove flame and continue inhaling to clear remaining smoke</li>\n</ul>\n<h3>Cleaning &amp; Maintenance</h3>\n<ul>\n<li><strong>Regular Cleaning:</strong> Clean after every 5-10 uses with isopropyl alcohol and pipe cleaners</li>\n<li><strong>Screen Replacement:</strong> Replace screens when clogged or after 10-15 uses for optimal performance</li>\n<li><strong>Deep Clean:</strong> Soak in isopropyl alcohol for 30 minutes, scrub with pipe cleaners, rinse thoroughly with warm water</li>\n</ul>\n<h3>Best Use Cases</h3>\n<p>Ideal for travel, hiking, camping, festivals, and everyday portable use. The durable metal construction withstands outdoor conditions and frequent transport. Perfect for quick sessions when you need a reliable, no-fuss smoking method. Compact size fits easily in pockets, bags, or backpacks without risk of breakage.</p>\n<p><strong>⚠️ Safety Note:</strong> Metal pipes can become hot during use. Allow to cool between sessions and handle with care. Always use in well-ventilated areas and never leave unattended while hot.</p>\n<h2>❓ Frequently Asked Questions</h2>\n<h3>What material is this metal pipe made from?</h3>\n<p><strong>A:</strong> This pipe is crafted from high-grade metal designed for durability and heat resistance. The quality construction ensures long-lasting performance even with regular use and travel.</p>\n<h3>How many screens are included with the metal pipe?</h3>\n<p><strong>A:</strong> Each metal pipe set includes 5 premium pipe screens, giving you multiple replacements for extended use. Additional screens can be purchased separately when needed.</p>\n<h3>Is this pipe suitable for beginners?</h3>\n<p><strong>A:</strong> Yes! Metal pipes are one of the most straightforward consumption methods, making them perfect for beginners. They’re easy to use, require no special equipment, and provide immediate effects with simple maintenance.</p>\n<h3>How do I clean my metal pipe?</h3>\n<p><strong>A:</strong> Soak the pipe in isopropyl alcohol (90%+ recommended) for 30 minutes, use pipe cleaners or cotton swabs to scrub interior surfaces, then rinse thoroughly with warm water and allow to dry completely before next use.</p>\n<h3>Can I travel with this metal pipe in Canada?</h3>\n<p><strong>A:</strong> Yes, cannabis accessories are legal across Canada. However, ensure the pipe is clean and free of residue when traveling, especially across provincial borders or through airports. Store in your checked luggage when flying.</p>\n<h3>Does Mohawk Medibles ship this pipe across Canada?</h3>\n<p><strong>A:</strong> Absolutely! We offer fast, discreet Canada-wide shipping with same-day processing on orders placed before 2 PM EST. Your metal pipe will arrive in plain, unmarked packaging to ensure privacy.</p>\n<h3>How long will this metal pipe last?</h3>\n<p><strong>A:</strong> With proper care and regular cleaning, a high-grade metal pipe can last for years. The durable construction resists damage from drops and outdoor conditions, making it significantly more long-lasting than glass alternatives.</p>\n</div>\n</div>",
