        "descriptionHTML": "<div class=\"tab-pane active\" id=\"tab-description\">\n<div class=\"detail-tab-desc detail-content-wrap\">\n<h2 data-end=\"232\" data-start=\"186\">🍊 <strong data-end=\"230\" data-start=\"191\">Sour Pink Grapefruit – $100/OZ Deal</strong></h2>\n<p data-end=\"288\" data-start=\"233\"><strong data-end=\"269\" data-start=\"233\">Hybrid • 50% Indica / 50% Sativa</strong><br data-end=\"272\" data-start=\"269\"/><strong data-end=\"288\" data-start=\"272\">THC: 15%–23%</strong></p>\n<hr/>\n<p data-end=\"852\" data-start=\"627\">Sour Pink Grapefruit is a balanced hybrid made from <strong data-end=\"714\" data-start=\"679\">Sweet Pink Grapefruit × ECSD V3</strong>. It’s a top pick for anyone who loves bold citrus flavour and a high that shifts smoothly from bright and energetic to calm and sedating.</p>\n<p data-end=\"1143\" data-start=\"854\"><strong data-end=\"886\" data-start=\"854\">Right after your first toke,</strong> a light and happy cerebral lift starts to rise. Your mind feels brighter, more elevated, and wrapped in a warm wave of easygoing bliss.<br data-end=\"1025\" data-start=\"1022\"/><strong data-end=\"1056\" data-start=\"1025\">As this mental high builds,</strong> your thoughts drift into a carefree, unfocused happiness that feels airy and euphoric.</p>\n<p data-end=\"1403\" data-start=\"1145\"><strong data-end=\"1170\" data-start=\"1145\">Then comes the shift.</strong> Your body begins to settle, muscles loosen, and the relaxing heaviness spreads through your entire frame.<br data-end=\"1279\" data-start=\"1276\"/><strong data-end=\"1295\" data-start=\"1279\">Soon enough,</strong> you’re locked into the couch, completely mellow, and ready to drift into deep rest or a long movie session.</p>\n<p data-end=\"1577\" data-start=\"1405\">With its balanced but powerful high, Sour Pink Grapefruit is a great choice for anyone looking to unwind after a long day while still enjoying a delicious, vibrant flavour.</p>\n<p data-end=\"1818\" data-start=\"1579\"><strong data-end=\"1615\" data-start=\"1579\">The flavour itself is a standout</strong>—bright sour citrus, sugary grapefruit, and a hint of earthy diesel on the finish.<br data-end=\"1700\" data-start=\"1697\"/><strong data-end=\"1728\" data-start=\"1700\">As the buds break apart,</strong> the aroma becomes even stronger, filling the room with a pungent grapefruit-diesel punch.</p>\n<p data-end=\"1931\" data-start=\"1820\">This strain is often used by people who want support with fatigue, insomnia, stress, and mood-related concerns.</p>\n<hr data-end=\"1936\" data-start=\"1933\"/>\n<h3 data-end=\"1956\" data-start=\"1938\">🌟 <strong data-end=\"1954\" data-start=\"1943\">EFFECTS</strong></h3>\n<ul data-end=\"2016\" data-start=\"1957\">\n<li data-end=\"1970\" data-start=\"1957\">\n<p data-end=\"1970\" data-start=\"1959\">Uplifting</p>\n</li>\n<li data-end=\"1983\" data-start=\"1971\">\n<p data-end=\"1983\" data-start=\"1973\">Relaxing</p>\n</li>\n<li data-end=\"1994\" data-start=\"1984\">\n<p data-end=\"1994\" data-start=\"1986\">Sleepy</p>\n</li>\n<li data-end=\"2007\" data-start=\"1995\">\n<p data-end=\"2007\" data-start=\"1997\">Euphoric</p>\n</li>\n<li data-end=\"2016\" data-start=\"2008\">\n<p data-end=\"2016\" data-start=\"2010\">Calm</p>\n</li>\n</ul>\n<hr data-end=\"2021\" data-start=\"2018\"/>\n<h3 data-end=\"2047\" data-start=\"2023\">🌿 <strong data-end=\"2045\" data-start=\"2028\">MAY HELP WITH</strong></h3>\n<ul data-end=\"2110\" data-start=\"2048\">\n<li data-end=\"2059\" data-start=\"2048\">\n<p data-end=\"2059\" data-start=\"2050\">Anxiety</p>\n</li>\n<li data-end=\"2074\" data-start=\"2060\">\n<p data-end=\"2074\" data-start=\"2062\">Depression</p>\n</li>\n<li data-end=\"2086\" data-start=\"2075\">\n<p data-end=\"2086\" data-start=\"2077\">Fatigue</p>\n</li>\n<li data-end=\"2099\" data-start=\"2087\">\n<p data-end=\"2099\" data-start=\"2089\">Insomnia</p>\n</li>\n<li data-end=\"2110\" data-start=\"2100\">\n<p data-end=\"2110\" data-start=\"2102\">Stress</p>\n</li>\n</ul>\n<hr data-end=\"2115\" data-start=\"2112\"/>\n<h3 data-end=\"2136\" data-start=\"2117\">🍬 <strong data-end=\"2134\" data-start=\"2122\">FLAVOURS</strong></h3>\n<ul data-end=\"2199\" data-start=\"2137\">\n<li data-end=\"2147\" data-start=\"2137\">\n<p data-end=\"2147\" data-start=\"2139\">Citrus</p>\n</li>\n<li data-end=\"2167\" data-start=\"2148\">\n<p data-end=\"2167\" data-start=\"2150\">Sour grapefruit</p>\n</li>\n<li data-end=\"2177\" data-start=\"2168\">\n<p data-end=\"2177\" data-start=\"2170\">Sweet</p>\n</li>\n<li data-end=\"2188\" data-start=\"2178\">\n<p data-end=\"2188\" data-start=\"2180\">Sugary</p>\n</li>\n<li data-end=\"2199\" data-start=\"2189\">\n<p data-end=\"2199\" data-start=\"2191\">Diesel</p>\n</li>\n</ul>\n<hr data-end=\"2204\" data-start=\"2201\"/>\n<h3 data-end=\"2224\" data-start=\"2206\">🌬️ <strong data-end=\"2222\" data-start=\"2212\">AROMAS</strong></h3>\n<ul data-end=\"2283\" data-start=\"2225\">\n<li data-end=\"2235\" data-start=\"2225\">\n<p data-end=\"2235\" data-start=\"2227\">Citrus</p>\n</li>\n<li data-end=\"2250\" data-start=\"2236\">\n<p data-end=\"2250\" data-start=\"2238\">Grapefruit</p>\n</li>\n<li data-end=\"2261\" data-start=\"2251\">\n<p data-end=\"2261\" data-start=\"2253\">Diesel</p>\n</li>\n<li data-end=\"2273\" data-start=\"2262\">\n<p data-end=\"2273\" data-start=\"2264\">Pungent</p>\n</li>\n<li data-end=\"2283\" data-start=\"2274\">\n<p data-end=\"2283\" data-start=\"2276\">Sweet</p>\n</li>\n</ul>\n</div>\n</div>",
