        "descriptionHTML": "<div class=\"tab-pane active\" id=\"tab-description\">\n<div class=\"detail-tab-desc detail-content-wrap\">\n<p>**Buy Hustler MEGA 25k Nicotine Vape online in Canada at Mohawk Medibles**, your trusted Indigenous-owned dispensary. Shop this premium high-capacity vape device and enjoy fast Canada-wide shipping with same-day processing. Order now for discreet delivery and experience cutting-edge vaping technology with adjustable power settings, dual mesh coil performance, and an impressive 25,000 puff capacity. Get yours delivered straight to your door from Tyendinaga Mohawk Territory.</p>\n<p>–</p>\n<h2>💡 Usage Guide</h2>\n<h3>Getting Started</h3>\n<ul>\n<li><strong>First Use:</strong> Remove device from packaging and remove any protective seals. The device is pre-filled and pre-charged, ready to use immediately</li>\n<li><strong>Activation:</strong> Simply inhale from the mouthpiece to activate – no buttons required</li>\n<li><strong>Power Adjustment:</strong> Use the device controls to switch between 16W (smooth, flavour-focused) and 25W (intense, cloud-heavy) modes</li>\n<li><strong>Screen Display:</strong> The full HD screen shows battery life, puff count, and power mode for complete control</li>\n</ul>\n<h3>Recommended Usage</h3>\n<ul>\n<li><strong>New Vapers:</strong> Start with 16W power mode and take 1-2 second draws. Wait 5-10 minutes between sessions</li>\n<li><strong>Experienced Users:</strong> Adjust to 25W for more intense satisfaction. 2-3 second draws as needed</li>\n<li><strong>Daily Consumption:</strong> 50mg nicotine strength is designed for regular users transitioning from cigarettes</li>\n</ul>\n<h3>Maintenance &amp; Care</h3>\n<ul>\n<li><strong>Storage:</strong> Keep device upright in a cool, dry place away from direct sunlight</li>\n<li><strong>Temperature:</strong> Avoid extreme heat or cold which can affect performance</li>\n<li><strong>Lifespan:</strong> Device lasts for approximately 25,000 puffs or until e-liquid is depleted</li>\n</ul>\n<h3>Best Use Cases</h3>\n<p>Ideal for adult smokers seeking a convenient, long-lasting alternative to traditional cigarettes. The high-capacity design makes it perfect for extended use without replacement, while dual power modes let you customize your experience. The 50mg nicotine strength provides satisfying throat hit for those transitioning from regular cigarettes.</p>\n<p><strong>⚠️ Important Safety Information:</strong> This product contains nicotine, a highly addictive substance. Not intended for non-smokers, pregnant or breastfeeding women, or individuals with heart conditions. Keep out of reach of children and pets. For adult use only (19+).</p>\n<h2>❓ Frequently Asked Questions</h2>\n<h3>How long does the Hustler MEGA 25k vape last?</h3>\n<p><strong>A:</strong> The Hustler MEGA 25k provides approximately 25,000 puffs, which typically lasts 3-6 weeks depending on your usage frequency. The full HD screen displays your remaining puff count so you always know when replacement is needed. This exceptional capacity makes it one of the longest-lasting disposable vapes available in Canada.</p>\n<h3>What nicotine strength is the Hustler MEGA 25k?</h3>\n<p><strong>A:</strong> This device contains 25mL of e-liquid at 50mg (5%) nicotine strength per mL, designed for adult smokers seeking a satisfying alternative to cigarettes. The higher nicotine concentration provides effective craving relief and throat hit comparable to traditional smoking.</p>\n<h3>What’s the difference between 16W and 25W power modes?</h3>\n<p><strong>A:</strong> The 16W mode delivers smoother, more flavourful draws with moderate vapour production – ideal for all-day use and flavour enthusiasts. The 25W mode provides more intense satisfaction with larger clouds and stronger throat hit – perfect for experienced vapers. You can easily switch between modes using the device controls.</p>\n<h3>Does the Hustler MEGA 25k need to be charged?</h3>\n<p><strong>A:</strong> Yes, this device features a rechargeable battery to ensure you can use all 25,000 puffs. It comes pre-charged but can be recharged via USB-C connection (cable not included) when battery runs low. The HD screen displays battery level so you know when to recharge.</p>\n<h3>Can I buy the Hustler MEGA 25k vape online in Canada?</h3>\n<p><strong>A:</strong> Yes! Mohawk Medibles ships the Hustler MEGA 25k across Canada with fast, discreet delivery. Orders placed before 2 PM EST are processed the same day. All packages arrive in plain, unmarked packaging. You must be 19+ with valid ID to purchase nicotine vaping products.</p>\n<h3>Is the Hustler MEGA 25k safe to use?</h3>\n<p><strong>A:</strong> When used as intended by adults 19+, this device meets Canadian vaping product standards. The dual mesh coil technology provides consistent, safe heating. However, vaping products contain nicotine which is addictive. Not recommended for non-smokers, pregnant individuals, or those with heart conditions. Always follow usage guidelines and safety warnings.</p>\n<h3>How should I dispose of the Hustler MEGA 25k when empty?</h3>\n<p><strong>A:</strong> This device contains a lithium battery and should be disposed of responsibly. Take empty devices to designated e-waste or battery recycling facilities in your area. Do not throw in regular garbage or attempt to disassemble. Contact your local municipality for electronic waste disposal locations.</p>\n</div>\n</div>",
