        "descriptionHTML": "<div class=\"tab-pane active\" id=\"tab-description\">\n<div class=\"detail-tab-desc detail-content-wrap\">\n<p>**Buy Adjust MyFlavor Nicotine Vape online in Canada at Mohawk Medibles**, your trusted Indigenous-owned dispensary offering premium vaping products. Shop this revolutionary 40K puff disposable vape with dual flavour control technology and enjoy fast Canada-wide shipping with same-day processing. Order now for discreet delivery and experience the most advanced disposable vape on the market, available exclusively at Mohawk Medibles.</p>\n<p>–</p>\n<h2>💡 Usage Guide</h2>\n<h3>Getting Started</h3>\n<ul>\n<li><strong>Unboxing:</strong> Remove device from packaging and remove any protective stickers or silicone plugs</li>\n<li><strong>First Use:</strong> No charging or filling required – simply inhale from the mouthpiece to activate</li>\n<li><strong>Flavour Adjustment:</strong> Use the MyFlavor dial to customize your flavour intensity between the two available flavours</li>\n<li><strong>Burst Mode:</strong> Activate burst mode for enhanced vapour production and intensified flavour</li>\n</ul>\n<h3>Recommended Usage</h3>\n<ul>\n<li><strong>New Vapers:</strong> Start with standard mode and lower flavour intensity; take 1-2 second draws</li>\n<li><strong>Experienced Vapers:</strong> Customize flavour blend to preference; use burst mode for fuller experience</li>\n<li><strong>Daily Use:</strong> Monitor puff counter display to track usage and plan for replacement</li>\n</ul>\n<h3>Device Lifespan</h3>\n<ul>\n<li><strong>Puff Capacity:</strong> Up to 40,000 puffs per device</li>\n<li><strong>Battery Life:</strong> Integrated rechargeable battery lasts entire device lifespan</li>\n<li><strong>Charging:</strong> USB-C charging port for quick recharging when battery indicator shows low</li>\n</ul>\n<h3>Best Use Cases</h3>\n<p>Ideal for vapers seeking customizable flavour experiences and extended device longevity. Perfect for daily use, travel, or as a long-lasting alternative to traditional cigarettes. The dual flavour system allows you to switch between flavours or blend them according to your mood and preference throughout the day.</p>\n<p><strong>⚠️ Important:</strong> This product contains nicotine. Nicotine is an addictive substance. Not for use by non-smokers, minors, pregnant or breastfeeding women, or individuals with heart conditions. Keep out of reach of children and pets.</p>\n<h2>❓ Frequently Asked Questions</h2>\n<h3>What makes the Adjust MyFlavor 40K different from other disposable vapes?</h3>\n<p><strong>A:</strong> The Adjust MyFlavor 40K features revolutionary dual flavour control technology, allowing you to adjust between two distinct flavours or blend them to create your perfect taste. With 40,000 puffs, burst mode capability, and a rechargeable battery, it offers significantly more value and customization than standard disposable vapes.</p>\n<h3>How do I adjust the flavours on my device?</h3>\n<p><strong>A:</strong> Simply rotate the MyFlavor dial located on the device to switch between flavour profiles or find your ideal blend. You can adjust the flavour intensity in real-time while vaping, giving you complete control over your vaping experience without needing to switch devices.</p>\n<h3>How long will the Adjust MyFlavor 40K last?</h3>\n<p><strong>A:</strong> With up to 40,000 puffs, the device can last several weeks to months depending on your usage frequency. For reference, if you take approximately 200 puffs per day (average user), the device will last approximately 200 days. The integrated rechargeable battery ensures the device lasts for its entire puff capacity.</p>\n<h3>Is the battery rechargeable, and how do I charge it?</h3>\n<p><strong>A:</strong> Yes, the Adjust MyFlavor 40K features a rechargeable battery with a USB-C charging port. Simply connect a USB-C cable (not included) to any standard USB power source. The device includes a battery indicator to show when charging is needed, ensuring you never run out of power before using all 40,000 puffs.</p>\n<h3>What nicotine strength does this vape contain?</h3>\n<p><strong>A:</strong> Please refer to the product specifications or packaging for exact nicotine strength information. The Adjust MyFlavor is designed to deliver consistent nicotine satisfaction throughout its 40,000 puff lifespan. If you have questions about nicotine levels, contact our customer service team before ordering.</p>\n<h3>Does Mohawk Medibles ship vape products across Canada?</h3>\n<p><strong>A:</strong> Yes! We offer fast, discreet Canada-wide shipping on all vape products with same-day processing on orders placed before 2 PM EST. All packages arrive in plain, unmarked packaging. Please note: You must be of legal age in your province to purchase nicotine vaping products.</p>\n<h3>How should I dispose of my Adjust MyFlavor vape when it’s finished?</h3>\n<p><strong>A:</strong> Disposable vapes contain lithium batteries and should be disposed of responsibly. Take your used device to an electronics recycling facility or battery recycling depot. Never throw vaping devices in regular garbage or recycling bins. Check your local municipality’s website for e-waste disposal locations near you.</p>\n</div>\n</div>",
