        "shortDescription": "🍬 Candy Cane — $6/Gram Special\nIndica Dominant Hybrid | 70% Indica / 30% SativaTHC: 15% – 20%\n\nCandy Cane is a smooth, feel-good indica-dominant hybrid that blends uplifting vibes with soothing rela...",
        "descriptionHTML": "<div class=\"tab-pane active\" id=\"tab-description\">\n<div class=\"detail-tab-desc detail-content-wrap\">\n<h2 data-end=\"126\" data-start=\"90\">🍬 Candy Cane — $6/Gram Special</h2>\n<p data-end=\"200\" data-start=\"127\"><strong data-end=\"179\" data-start=\"127\">Indica Dominant Hybrid | 70% Indica / 30% Sativa</strong><br data-end=\"182\" data-start=\"179\"/><strong data-end=\"200\" data-start=\"182\">THC: 15% – 20%</strong></p>\n<hr/>\n<p data-end=\"680\" data-start=\"427\">Candy Cane is a smooth, feel-good <strong data-end=\"487\" data-start=\"461\">indica-dominant hybrid</strong> that blends uplifting vibes with soothing relaxation 🌿🍬. Right from the first hit, a wave of <strong data-end=\"602\" data-start=\"583\">euphoric energy</strong> rolls in, boosting your mood and keeping things light, upbeat, and enjoyable.</p>\n<p data-end=\"928\" data-start=\"682\">Soon after, a <strong data-end=\"714\" data-start=\"696\">warm body buzz</strong> follows. Muscles loosen. Tension fades. Pain melts away — all without knocking you out right away. Because of this balance, Candy Cane works great for both <strong data-end=\"892\" data-start=\"871\">daytime enjoyment</strong> and <strong data-end=\"927\" data-start=\"897\">evening wind-down sessions</strong>.</p>\n<p data-end=\"1173\" data-start=\"930\">Meanwhile, the flavour steals the show. Sweet mint leads the way, followed by <strong data-end=\"1034\" data-start=\"1008\">berry and citrus notes</strong>, finishing with a smooth, slightly pungent exhale ❄️🍓. The aroma mirrors the taste, filling the air with fresh mint and sugary sweetness.</p>\n<p data-end=\"1313\" data-start=\"1175\">With moderate THC levels, Candy Cane is <strong data-end=\"1236\" data-start=\"1215\">beginner-friendly</strong>, yet still satisfying for seasoned smokers looking for a mellow, happy high.</p>\n<hr/>\n<h3 data-end=\"1337\" data-start=\"1315\">✨ What You’ll Feel</h3>\n<ul data-end=\"1482\" data-start=\"1338\">\n<li data-end=\"1363\" data-start=\"1338\">\n<p data-end=\"1363\" data-start=\"1340\">😄 Euphoric and happy</p>\n</li>\n<li data-end=\"1388\" data-start=\"1364\">\n<p data-end=\"1388\" data-start=\"1366\">⚡ Light energy boost</p>\n</li>\n<li data-end=\"1413\" data-start=\"1389\">\n<p data-end=\"1413\" data-start=\"1391\">😌 Relaxed body calm</p>\n</li>\n<li data-end=\"1441\" data-start=\"1414\">\n<p data-end=\"1441\" data-start=\"1416\">🍔 Appetite stimulation</p>\n</li>\n<li data-end=\"1482\" data-start=\"1442\">\n<p data-end=\"1482\" data-start=\"1444\">😴 Gentle sleepiness at higher doses</p>\n</li>\n</ul>\n<hr/>\n<h3 data-end=\"1504\" data-start=\"1484\">🩺 May Help With</h3>\n<ul data-end=\"1586\" data-start=\"1505\">\n<li data-end=\"1516\" data-start=\"1505\">\n<p data-end=\"1516\" data-start=\"1507\">Fatigue</p>\n</li>\n<li data-end=\"1531\" data-start=\"1517\">\n<p data-end=\"1531\" data-start=\"1519\">Depression</p>\n</li>\n<li data-end=\"1544\" data-start=\"1532\">\n<p data-end=\"1544\" data-start=\"1534\">Insomnia</p>\n</li>\n<li data-end=\"1558\" data-start=\"1545\">\n<p data-end=\"1558\" data-start=\"1547\">Migraines</p>\n</li>\n<li data-end=\"1575\" data-start=\"1559\">\n<p data-end=\"1575\" data-start=\"1561\">Chronic pain</p>\n</li>\n<li data-end=\"1586\" data-start=\"1576\">\n<p data-end=\"1586\" data-start=\"1578\">Nausea</p>\n</li>\n</ul>\n<hr/>\n<h3 data-end=\"1610\" data-start=\"1588\">🍭 Flavour Profile</h3>\n<ul data-end=\"1667\" data-start=\"1611\">\n<li data-end=\"1625\" data-start=\"1611\">\n<p data-end=\"1625\" data-start=\"1613\">Sweet mint</p>\n</li>\n<li data-end=\"1635\" data-start=\"1626\">\n<p data-end=\"1635\" data-start=\"1628\">Berry</p>\n</li>\n<li data-end=\"1646\" data-start=\"1636\">\n<p data-end=\"1646\" data-start=\"1638\">Citrus</p>\n</li>\n<li data-end=\"1667\" data-start=\"1647\">\n<p data-end=\"1667\" data-start=\"1649\">Fruity freshness</p>\n</li>\n</ul>\n<hr/>\n<h3 data-end=\"1690\" data-start=\"1669\">🌬️ Aroma Profile</h3>\n<ul data-end=\"1730\" data-start=\"1691\">\n<li data-end=\"1700\" data-start=\"1691\">\n<p data-end=\"1700\" data-start=\"1693\">Minty</p>\n</li>\n<li data-end=\"1710\" data-start=\"1701\">\n<p data-end=\"1710\" data-start=\"1703\">Sweet</p>\n</li>\n<li data-end=\"1730\" data-start=\"1711\">\n<p data-end=\"1730\" data-start=\"1713\">Lightly pungent</p>\n</li>\n</ul>\n<p data-end=\"1832\" data-start=\"1732\">Candy Cane is the kind of strain that <strong data-end=\"1791\" data-start=\"1770\">keeps you smiling</strong>, relaxed, and coming back for more 🎄🍃.</p>\n<hr/>\n<p><strong>How to Use Marijuana (Responsibly)</strong></p>\n<p><strong>Start Low, Go Slow</strong> – If you’re new to cannabis or trying a strong strain like Blue Comatose, begin with a <strong>small dose</strong> (1–2 puffs or a low-dose edible) and wait 30–60 minutes to gauge the effects.</p>\n<p><strong>Choose the Right Method:</strong></p>\n<ul>\n<li><strong>Smoking or Vaping:</strong> Fast-acting and ideal for experienced users. Use a joint, pipe, or dry herb vape.</li>\n<li><strong>Edibles or Capsules:</strong> Longer-lasting effects but slower onset (30–90 mins). Start with a low dose (5–10mg THC).</li>\n<li><strong>Tinctures or Oils:</strong> Absorbed under the tongue for quicker onset (15–30 mins). Great for controlled dosing.</li>\n<li><strong>Topicals:</strong> Not psychoactive—best for localized relief from aches or inflammation.</li>\n</ul>\n<p><strong>Stay Hydrated &amp; Have Snacks</strong> – Dry mouth and the munchies are common. Keep water and snacks handy.</p>\n<p><strong>Don’t Mix With Alcohol or Other Substances</strong> – Mixing can intensify effects unpredictably.</p>\n<p><strong>Don’t Drive or Operate Machinery</strong> – Wait several hours after using THC-rich products before engaging in any activity that requires focus or coordination.</p>\n<p><strong>Store Safely</strong> – Keep all cannabis products out of reach of children and pets.</p>\n</div>\n</div>",
