        "descriptionHTML": "<div class=\"tab-pane active\" id=\"tab-description\">\n<div class=\"detail-tab-desc detail-content-wrap\">\n<p>**Buy BACKWOODS Select Cigars online in Canada at Mohawk Medibles**, your trusted Indigenous-owned cannabis dispensary. Shop these premium vape products in convenient 3-packs and enjoy fast Canada-wide shipping with same-day processing. Order now for discreet delivery and experience the smooth, bold satisfaction of authentic BACKWOODS quality. Choose between Pennsylvania Primo or Connecticut Broadleaf varieties to match your flavour preference.</p>\n<p>–</p>\n<h2>💡 Usage Guide</h2>\n<h3>How to Use Your BACKWOODS Select Cigars</h3>\n<ul>\n<li><strong>Preparation:</strong> Remove cigar from packaging and inspect for quality. Allow to reach room temperature if stored in cool conditions.</li>\n<li><strong>Lighting:</strong> Toast the foot of the cigar evenly before drawing, rotating for an even burn.</li>\n<li><strong>Enjoying:</strong> Draw slowly and steadily, allowing smoke to fill your mouth before exhaling. Avoid inhaling deeply into lungs.</li>\n<li><strong>Pacing:</strong> Take your time between draws to prevent overheating and maintain optimal flavour profile.</li>\n</ul>\n<h3>Session Duration &amp; Experience</h3>\n<ul>\n<li><strong>Average Session:</strong> 20-40 minutes per cigar depending on size and pace</li>\n<li><strong>Flavour Profile:</strong> Rich, natural tobacco notes with rustic, authentic character</li>\n<li><strong>Best Enjoyed:</strong> During relaxation time, social gatherings, or as a satisfying end to your day</li>\n</ul>\n<h3>Storage Recommendations</h3>\n<p>Store your BACKWOODS Select Cigars in a cool, dry place away from direct sunlight. Keep in original packaging or a humidor at 65-72% humidity to maintain freshness and prevent drying. Properly stored cigars maintain quality for several months.</p>\n<p><strong>⚠️ Important:</strong> This product contains tobacco and nicotine. Not suitable for minors. Use responsibly and in accordance with local regulations.</p>\n<h2>❓ Frequently Asked Questions</h2>\n<h3>What varieties are available in the BACKWOODS Select Cigars 3-pack?</h3>\n<p><strong>A:</strong> You can choose between Pennsylvania Primo, known for its robust and earthy flavour profile, or Connecticut Broadleaf, which offers a smoother, more mellow smoking experience. Both varieties deliver the authentic BACKWOODS quality and rustic charm that enthusiasts love.</p>\n<h3>How many cigars come in each pack?</h3>\n<p><strong>A:</strong> Each BACKWOODS Select Cigars package contains 3 premium cigars, providing you with multiple satisfying sessions. This convenient pack size is perfect for personal enjoyment or sharing with friends during social occasions.</p>\n<h3>Are BACKWOODS Select Cigars suitable for beginners?</h3>\n<p><strong>A:</strong> BACKWOODS cigars are known for their bold, authentic tobacco flavour and rustic character. While they can be enjoyed by newcomers, they’re particularly appreciated by those with some cigar experience. If you’re new to cigars, start with slower, smaller draws to gauge your comfort level.</p>\n<h3>How should I store my BACKWOODS Select Cigars?</h3>\n<p><strong>A:</strong> Keep your cigars in their original packaging in a cool, dry location away from direct sunlight and heat sources. For optimal freshness, store at room temperature with moderate humidity (65-72%). Avoid refrigeration, as this can dry out the tobacco and affect flavour quality.</p>\n<h3>Does Mohawk Medibles ship BACKWOODS Select Cigars across Canada?</h3>\n<p><strong>A:</strong> Yes! We offer fast, discreet Canada-wide shipping on all BACKWOODS products. Orders placed before 2 PM EST are processed the same day. All packages arrive in plain, unmarked packaging to ensure your privacy. Delivery times vary by location but typically range from 2-5 business days.</p>\n<h3>What makes BACKWOODS Select Cigars different from regular cigars?</h3>\n<p><strong>A:</strong> BACKWOODS cigars feature a distinctive rustic appearance with natural tobacco leaf wrappers that provide authentic, unprocessed flavour. Their unique construction and curing process delivers a bold, satisfying smoke that stands apart from machine-made cigars, offering a more traditional and genuine tobacco experience.</p>\n<h3>Can I return or exchange my BACKWOODS Select Cigars?</h3>\n<p><strong>A:</strong> Due to health and safety regulations, we cannot accept returns on tobacco products once shipped. However, if your order arrives damaged or defective, please contact our customer service team within 48 hours of delivery, and we’ll work with you to resolve the issue promptly.</p>\n</div>\n</div>",
