        "descriptionHTML": "<div class=\"tab-pane active\" id=\"tab-description\">\n<div class=\"detail-tab-desc detail-content-wrap\">\n<h2 data-end=\"188\" data-start=\"133\">👽🍪 Miracle Alien Cookies (MAC) — $6/Gram Special</h2>\n<p data-end=\"246\" data-start=\"189\"><strong data-end=\"225\" data-start=\"189\">Hybrid | 50% Sativa / 50% Indica</strong><br data-end=\"228\" data-start=\"225\"/><strong data-end=\"246\" data-start=\"228\">THC: 14% – 20%</strong></p>\n<hr/>\n<p data-end=\"770\" data-start=\"490\">Miracle Alien Cookies, better known as <strong data-end=\"536\" data-start=\"529\">MAC</strong>, is a perfectly balanced hybrid that blends <strong data-end=\"623\" data-start=\"581\">powerful effects with standout flavour</strong> 🌿✨. From the very first hit, the high rushes in fast, lifting your mood and sparking <strong data-end=\"736\" data-start=\"710\">happy, creative energy</strong> that feels smooth and effortless.</p>\n<p data-end=\"1124\" data-start=\"772\">As the head high settles in, a deep sense of <strong data-end=\"848\" data-start=\"817\">mental clarity and euphoria</strong> takes over. Shortly after, a soothing body relaxation follows, melting away tension and discomfort without dragging you down or making you sleepy. Because of this even balance, MAC works beautifully <strong data-end=\"1064\" data-start=\"1048\">day or night</strong>, whether you’re creating, socializing, or simply unwinding.</p>\n<p data-end=\"1425\" data-start=\"1126\">The flavour is loud and unmistakable 🍋⛽. Expect <strong data-end=\"1206\" data-start=\"1175\">sour citrus and sweet notes</strong> up front, followed by spicy, earthy undertones and a gassy diesel finish that lingers on the exhale. The aroma fills the room with <strong data-end=\"1377\" data-start=\"1338\">dank, pungent fuel and earthy herbs</strong>, making MAC a favourite among seasoned smokers.</p>\n<p data-end=\"1594\" data-start=\"1427\">With moderate-to-high THC levels, Miracle Alien Cookies delivers a <strong data-end=\"1532\" data-start=\"1494\">strong but approachable experience</strong> that keeps both mind and body feeling good without overwhelm.</p>\n<hr/>\n<h3 data-end=\"1618\" data-start=\"1596\">✨ What You’ll Feel</h3>\n<ul data-end=\"1732\" data-start=\"1619\">\n<li data-end=\"1644\" data-start=\"1619\">\n<p data-end=\"1644\" data-start=\"1621\">😄 Happy and euphoric</p>\n</li>\n<li data-end=\"1673\" data-start=\"1645\">\n<p data-end=\"1673\" data-start=\"1647\">🎨 Creative and uplifted</p>\n</li>\n<li data-end=\"1704\" data-start=\"1674\">\n<p data-end=\"1704\" data-start=\"1676\">😌 Calm, relaxed body buzz</p>\n</li>\n<li data-end=\"1732\" data-start=\"1705\">\n<p data-end=\"1732\" data-start=\"1707\">🧠 Clear-headed balance</p>\n</li>\n</ul>\n<hr/>\n<h3 data-end=\"1754\" data-start=\"1734\">🩺 May Help With</h3>\n<ul data-end=\"1836\" data-start=\"1755\">\n<li data-end=\"1771\" data-start=\"1755\">\n<p data-end=\"1771\" data-start=\"1757\">Chronic pain</p>\n</li>\n<li data-end=\"1792\" data-start=\"1772\">\n<p data-end=\"1792\" data-start=\"1774\">Stress &amp; anxiety</p>\n</li>\n<li data-end=\"1807\" data-start=\"1793\">\n<p data-end=\"1807\" data-start=\"1795\">Depression</p>\n</li>\n<li data-end=\"1820\" data-start=\"1808\">\n<p data-end=\"1820\" data-start=\"1810\">Insomnia</p>\n</li>\n<li data-end=\"1836\" data-start=\"1821\">\n<p data-end=\"1836\" data-start=\"1823\">Mood swings</p>\n</li>\n</ul>\n<hr/>\n<h3 data-end=\"1860\" data-start=\"1838\">🍋 Flavour Profile</h3>\n<ul data-end=\"1913\" data-start=\"1861\">\n<li data-end=\"1876\" data-start=\"1861\">\n<p data-end=\"1876\" data-start=\"1863\">Sour citrus</p>\n</li>\n<li data-end=\"1892\" data-start=\"1877\">\n<p data-end=\"1892\" data-start=\"1879\">Sweet notes</p>\n</li>\n<li data-end=\"1902\" data-start=\"1893\">\n<p data-end=\"1902\" data-start=\"1895\">Spicy</p>\n</li>\n<li data-end=\"1913\" data-start=\"1903\">\n<p data-end=\"1913\" data-start=\"1905\">Diesel</p>\n</li>\n</ul>\n<hr/>\n<h3 data-end=\"1936\" data-start=\"1915\">🌬️ Aroma Profile</h3>\n<ul data-end=\"1998\" data-start=\"1937\">\n<li data-end=\"1945\" data-start=\"1937\">\n<p data-end=\"1945\" data-start=\"1939\">Dank</p>\n</li>\n<li data-end=\"1962\" data-start=\"1946\">\n<p data-end=\"1962\" data-start=\"1948\">Earthy herbs</p>\n</li>\n<li data-end=\"1981\" data-start=\"1963\">\n<p data-end=\"1981\" data-start=\"1965\">Pungent diesel</p>\n</li>\n<li data-end=\"1998\" data-start=\"1982\">\n<p data-end=\"1998\" data-start=\"1984\">Spicy floral</p>\n</li>\n</ul>\n<p data-end=\"2108\" data-start=\"2000\">Miracle Alien Cookies is a <strong data-end=\"2050\" data-start=\"2027\">true modern classic</strong> — balanced, flavour-packed, and endlessly enjoyable 👽🔥.</p>\n<hr/>\n<p><strong>How to Use Marijuana (Responsibly)</strong></p>\n<p><strong>Start Low, Go Slow</strong> – If you’re new to cannabis or trying a strong strain like Blue Comatose, begin with a <strong>small dose</strong> (1–2 puffs or a low-dose edible) and wait 30–60 minutes to gauge the effects.</p>\n<p><strong>Choose the Right Method:</strong></p>\n<ul>\n<li><strong>Smoking or Vaping:</strong> Fast-acting and ideal for experienced users. Use a joint, pipe, or dry herb vape.</li>\n<li><strong>Edibles or Capsules:</strong> Longer-lasting effects but slower onset (30–90 mins). Start with a low dose (5–10mg THC).</li>\n<li><strong>Tinctures or Oils:</strong> Absorbed under the tongue for quicker onset (15–30 mins). Great for controlled dosing.</li>\n<li><strong>Topicals:</strong> Not psychoactive—best for localized relief from aches or inflammation.</li>\n</ul>\n<p><strong>Stay Hydrated &amp; Have Snacks</strong> – Dry mouth and the munchies are common. Keep water and snacks handy.</p>\n<p><strong>Don’t Mix With Alcohol or Other Substances</strong> – Mixing can intensify effects unpredictably.</p>\n<p><strong>Don’t Drive or Operate Machinery</strong> – Wait several hours after using THC-rich products before engaging in any activity that requires focus or coordination.</p>\n<p><strong>Store Safely</strong> – Keep all cannabis products out of reach of children and pets.</p>\n</div>\n</div>",
