        "descriptionHTML": "<div class=\"tab-pane active\" id=\"tab-description\">\n<div class=\"detail-tab-desc detail-content-wrap\">\n<p>**Buy Wesley Tea Company 1:1 Tea online in Canada at Mohawk Medibles**, your trusted Indigenous-owned cannabis dispensary. Shop this perfectly balanced 40mg THC:CBD herbal tea blend and enjoy fast Canada-wide shipping with same-day processing. Order now for discreet delivery of premium cannabis-infused wellness beverages that combine therapeutic benefits with exceptional taste. Experience the harmony of equal-ratio cannabinoids in every soothing cup.</p>\n<p>–</p>\n<h2>💡 Usage Guide</h2>\n<h3>Recommended Dosage</h3>\n<ul>\n<li><strong>Beginners:</strong> Start with half a serving (10mg THC + 10mg CBD) and wait 60-90 minutes before consuming more</li>\n<li><strong>Experienced Users:</strong> One full serving (20mg THC + 20mg CBD) provides balanced, therapeutic effects</li>\n<li><strong>Medical Patients:</strong> Consult with your healthcare provider; the 1:1 ratio is ideal for symptom management without overwhelming psychoactivity</li>\n</ul>\n<h3>Preparation Instructions</h3>\n<ul>\n<li><strong>Hot Tea:</strong> Steep tea bag in 250ml of hot water (90-95°C) for 5-7 minutes. Add honey or lemon to taste</li>\n<li><strong>Iced Tea:</strong> Steep in hot water, then pour over ice for a refreshing cold beverage</li>\n<li><strong>Enhanced Absorption:</strong> Add a small amount of milk, cream, or coconut oil to help cannabinoid absorption</li>\n<li><strong>Important:</strong> Stir well before drinking as cannabinoids may settle. Consume entire cup for full dosage</li>\n</ul>\n<h3>Onset &amp; Duration</h3>\n<ul>\n<li><strong>Onset:</strong> 30-90 minutes (faster on empty stomach, slower with food)</li>\n<li><strong>Peak Effects:</strong> 2-3 hours after consumption</li>\n<li><strong>Duration:</strong> 4-6 hours of balanced effects</li>\n<li><strong>Note:</strong> The 1:1 ratio means CBD moderates THC effects for a smoother, more manageable experience</li>\n</ul>\n<h3>Best Use Cases</h3>\n<p>This balanced 1:1 tea is perfect for daytime or evening wellness rituals. The equal ratio of THC and CBD provides gentle relaxation without sedation, making it ideal for stress relief, discomfort management, and promoting calm focus. Enjoy during afternoon breaks, evening wind-down routines, or anytime you need balanced therapeutic support. The CBD content helps minimize anxiety while the THC provides gentle euphoria and physical comfort.</p>\n<h2>❓ Frequently Asked Questions</h2>\n<h3>What does 1:1 ratio mean in Wesley Tea Company tea?</h3>\n<p><strong>A:</strong> The 1:1 ratio means this tea contains equal amounts of THC and CBD – specifically 20mg of each per serving, for 40mg total cannabinoids. This balanced ratio provides therapeutic benefits with moderated psychoactive effects, as CBD naturally counterbalances THC’s intensity.</p>\n<h3>How long does Wesley Tea Company 1:1 Tea take to work?</h3>\n<p><strong>A:</strong> As a cannabis-infused beverage, this tea typically takes 30-90 minutes to take effect, similar to edibles. Effects peak around 2-3 hours and can last 4-6 hours total. Always start with a half serving if you’re new to cannabis beverages and wait at least 90 minutes before consuming more.</p>\n<h3>Will this tea make me feel high?</h3>\n<p><strong>A:</strong> The 1:1 THC:CBD ratio provides gentle, balanced effects rather than an intense high. The CBD moderates the THC, resulting in mild euphoria, relaxation, and therapeutic benefits without overwhelming psychoactivity. Most users report feeling calm, comfortable, and clear-headed rather than heavily intoxicated.</p>\n<h3>Can I drink Wesley Tea before work or driving?</h3>\n<p><strong>A:</strong> No. This product contains 20mg of THC per serving, which will impair your ability to drive or operate machinery. Only consume when you have no obligations for at least 6 hours. Never drive or operate heavy equipment after consuming cannabis products.</p>\n<h3>Is Wesley Tea Company 1:1 Tea suitable for beginners?</h3>\n<p><strong>A:</strong> Yes, the 1:1 ratio makes this an excellent choice for beginners seeking therapeutic benefits. Start with half a serving (10mg THC + 10mg CBD) to assess your tolerance. The CBD content provides a safety buffer that makes the experience more predictable and comfortable than THC-only products.</p>\n<h3>How should I store Wesley Tea Company tea?</h3>\n<p><strong>A:</strong> Store tea bags in their original packaging in a cool, dry place away from direct sunlight, heat, and moisture. Keep sealed until ready to use. Properly stored, cannabis tea maintains potency for 6-12 months. Always keep out of reach of children and pets.</p>\n<h3>Does Mohawk Medibles ship Wesley Tea across Canada?</h3>\n<p><strong>A:</strong> Yes! We offer fast, discreet Canada-wide shipping on all Wesley Tea Company products with same-day processing on orders placed before 2 PM EST. All packages arrive in plain, unmarked packaging with no indication of contents for complete privacy.</p>\n</div>\n</div>",
