        "descriptionHTML": "<div class=\"tab-pane active\" id=\"tab-description\">\n<div class=\"detail-tab-desc detail-content-wrap\">\n<p><strong>Buy Plant of Life Full Spectrum Organic Pet CBD Oil online in Canada at Mohawk Medibles</strong>, your trusted Indigenous-owned cannabis dispensary. Shop this premium, veterinarian-approved pet wellness formula and enjoy fast Canada-wide shipping with same-day processing. Order now for discreet delivery and give your furry companion the natural, organic hemp-derived support they deserve. Perfect for pet owners seeking high-quality, GMO-free CBD solutions sourced from trusted suppliers.</p>\n<p>–</p>\n<h2>💡 Usage Guide</h2>\n<h3>Recommended Dosage for Pets</h3>\n<ul>\n<li><strong>Small Pets (under 10 kg):</strong> Start with 1-2 drops twice daily</li>\n<li><strong>Medium Pets (10-25 kg):</strong> 2-4 drops twice daily</li>\n<li><strong>Large Pets (over 25 kg):</strong> 4-6 drops twice daily</li>\n<li><strong>Important:</strong> Always start with the lowest dose and gradually increase over 5-7 days while monitoring your pet’s response</li>\n</ul>\n<h3>How to Administer</h3>\n<ul>\n<li><strong>Direct Method:</strong> Place drops directly into your pet’s mouth using the dropper, aiming for under the tongue for optimal absorption</li>\n<li><strong>Food Mixing:</strong> Mix drops into your pet’s favourite food or treats for easy consumption</li>\n<li><strong>Treat Application:</strong> Apply drops onto a pet treat and allow them to absorb before feeding</li>\n</ul>\n<h3>Onset &amp; Duration</h3>\n<ul>\n<li><strong>Onset:</strong> 15-45 minutes when administered directly; 30-60 minutes when mixed with food</li>\n<li><strong>Peak Effects:</strong> 1-2 hours after administration</li>\n<li><strong>Duration:</strong> 4-6 hours of support</li>\n</ul>\n<h3>Best Use Cases</h3>\n<p>Ideal for daily wellness support, helping pets maintain calm during stressful situations, supporting joint comfort in aging pets, and promoting overall well-being. This human-grade, full-spectrum formula is perfect for pet owners seeking natural, organic solutions. Administer consistently at the same times each day for best results.</p>\n<p><strong>⚠️ Safety Note:</strong> This product contains 0% THC and is non-psychoactive, making it safe for pets. However, always consult with your veterinarian before starting any new supplement regimen, especially if your pet is on medication or has existing health conditions.</p>\n<h2>❓ Frequently Asked Questions</h2>\n<h3>Is Plant of Life Pet CBD Oil safe for my pet?</h3>\n<p><strong>A:</strong> Yes, this veterinarian-approved formula is crafted from 100% GMO-free organic hemp and contains 0% THC, making it completely non-psychoactive and safe for pets. It’s formulated with human-grade ingredients and infused with premium hemp extract. However, we always recommend consulting your veterinarian before introducing any new supplement to your pet’s routine.</p>\n<h3>Will this CBD oil make my pet high?</h3>\n<p><strong>A:</strong> No, absolutely not. Plant of Life Pet CBD Oil contains no THC, the psychoactive compound found in cannabis. Your pet will experience only the potential wellness benefits of CBD without any intoxicating effects. This product is specifically formulated for safe pet consumption.</p>\n<h3>What size pet is this CBD oil suitable for?</h3>\n<p><strong>A:</strong> This CBD oil is suitable for pets of all sizes, from small cats and toy breeds to large dogs. The dropper allows for precise dosing, so you can easily adjust the amount based on your pet’s weight. Start with the recommended dose for your pet’s size and adjust as needed under veterinary guidance.</p>\n<h3>How long does one bottle of Plant of Life Pet CBD Oil last?</h3>\n<p><strong>A:</strong> The duration depends on your pet’s size and dosage. For small pets using 1-2 drops twice daily, one bottle can last 4-6 weeks. For larger pets requiring higher doses, expect 2-4 weeks per bottle. Consistent daily use provides the best results for your pet’s wellness.</p>\n<h3>Can I give this to both my cat and dog?</h3>\n<p><strong>A:</strong> Yes, Plant of Life Pet CBD Oil is safe for both cats and dogs, as well as other pets. Simply adjust the dosage according to each pet’s weight and needs. The organic, full-spectrum formula is gentle enough for felines while effective for canines of all sizes.</p>\n<h3>Does Mohawk Medibles ship Pet CBD Oil across Canada?</h3>\n<p><strong>A:</strong> Yes! We offer fast, discreet Canada-wide shipping with same-day processing on orders placed before 2 PM EST. Your Plant of Life Pet CBD Oil will arrive in plain, unmarked packaging to ensure privacy and product integrity.</p>\n<h3>How should I store Plant of Life Pet CBD Oil?</h3>\n<p><strong>A:</strong> Store the bottle in a cool, dark place away from direct sunlight and heat. Keep the cap tightly sealed when not in use to preserve freshness and potency. Store out of reach of children and pets. Properly stored, CBD oil maintains its quality for 12-18 months. Refrigeration can extend shelf life but may cause the oil to thicken temporarily.</p>\n\n</div>\n</div>",
