        "descriptionHTML": "<div class=\"tab-pane active\" id=\"tab-description\">\n<div class=\"detail-tab-desc detail-content-wrap\">\n<h2 data-end=\"299\" data-start=\"247\">🌍🔥 <strong data-end=\"292\" data-start=\"255\">Moroccan Hash – Classic Rif Style</strong> 🔥🌍</h2>\n<p data-end=\"321\" data-start=\"300\"><strong data-end=\"321\" data-start=\"300\">$5 / Gram Special</strong></p>\n<hr/>\n<p data-end=\"926\" data-start=\"649\">Moroccan Hash is a <strong data-end=\"706\" data-start=\"668\">time-honoured cannabis concentrate</strong> with deep cultural roots in the Rif Mountains of Morocco. To begin with, it’s traditionally crafted from resin-heavy cannabis plants, including classic Rif and Ketama genetics, prized for their rich trichome production.</p>\n<p data-end=\"1127\" data-start=\"928\">In appearance, this hash is instantly recognizable. Typically, it shows a <strong data-end=\"1048\" data-start=\"1002\">darker outer layer with a lighter interior</strong>, along with a firm yet workable texture that breaks down smoothly when warmed.</p>\n<p data-end=\"1431\" data-start=\"1129\">When it comes to flavour, Moroccan Hash delivers a <strong data-end=\"1216\" data-start=\"1180\">classic earthy and spicy profile</strong>. Right away, warm soil and herbal notes come forward. Shortly after, subtle floral tones appear, finishing with a light <strong data-end=\"1358\" data-start=\"1337\">black pepper kick</strong> on the exhale. The smoke stays smooth, aromatic, and never overpowering.</p>\n<p data-end=\"1756\" data-start=\"1433\">As for the effects, Moroccan Hash provides a <strong data-end=\"1509\" data-start=\"1478\">quick-onset, buzzy euphoria</strong> that lifts the mood and clears the mind. At the same time, a gentle body relaxation settles in, keeping things calm without heavy sedation. Because of this balance, it works well for <strong data-end=\"1755\" data-start=\"1693\">social settings, creative activities, or light daytime use</strong>.</p>\n<p data-end=\"1944\" data-start=\"1758\">Thanks to its moderate THC levels and traditional preparation, Moroccan Hash remains a go-to choice for those seeking <strong data-end=\"1943\" data-start=\"1876\">authentic flavour, reliable effects, and classic hash character</strong>.</p>\n<hr data-end=\"1949\" data-start=\"1946\"/>\n<h3 data-end=\"1972\" data-start=\"1951\">💥 Key Highlights</h3>\n<ul data-end=\"2178\" data-start=\"1973\">\n<li data-end=\"2008\" data-start=\"1973\">\n<p data-end=\"2008\" data-start=\"1975\">Traditional Moroccan-style hash</p>\n</li>\n<li data-end=\"2052\" data-start=\"2009\">\n<p data-end=\"2052\" data-start=\"2011\">Made from Rif Mountain cannabis strains</p>\n</li>\n<li data-end=\"2098\" data-start=\"2053\">\n<p data-end=\"2098\" data-start=\"2055\">Earthy, spicy, and floral flavour profile</p>\n</li>\n<li data-end=\"2135\" data-start=\"2099\">\n<p data-end=\"2135\" data-start=\"2101\">Smooth smoke with peppery finish</p>\n</li>\n<li data-end=\"2178\" data-start=\"2136\">\n<p data-end=\"2178\" data-start=\"2138\">Balanced effects: uplifting &amp; relaxing</p>\n</li>\n</ul>\n<hr data-end=\"2183\" data-start=\"2180\"/>\n<h3 data-end=\"2203\" data-start=\"2185\">📊 THC Content</h3>\n<ul data-end=\"2224\" data-start=\"2204\">\n<li data-end=\"2224\" data-start=\"2204\">\n<p data-end=\"2224\" data-start=\"2206\"><strong data-end=\"2224\" data-start=\"2206\">~14% – 16% THC</strong></p>\n</li>\n</ul>\n</div>\n</div>",
