        "descriptionHTML": "<div class=\"tab-pane active\" id=\"tab-description\">\n<div class=\"detail-tab-desc detail-content-wrap\">\n<p>**Buy Medibles Hash Oil online in Canada at Mohawk Medibles**, your trusted Indigenous-owned cannabis dispensary. Shop this premium concentrated cannabis extract with exceptional potency (70-86% THC) and enjoy fast Canada-wide shipping with same-day processing. Order now for discreet delivery from Tyendinaga Mohawk Territory. Available in multiple varieties including Regular, Premium, Cherry, and Honey flavours in convenient 5ml and 2g bottles.</p>\n<p>–</p>\n<h2>💡 Usage Guide</h2>\n<h3>Recommended Dosage</h3>\n<ul>\n<li><strong>Beginners:</strong> Start with a rice grain-sized amount (approximately 0.025g). Hash oil is extremely potent and should be approached with caution by new users.</li>\n<li><strong>Experienced Users:</strong> 0.05-0.1g per session, adjusting based on tolerance and desired effects.</li>\n<li><strong>Medical Patients:</strong> Consult with your healthcare provider for personalized dosing. Typically 0.05-0.15g daily for symptom management.</li>\n</ul>\n<h3>Consumption Methods</h3>\n<ul>\n<li><strong>Dabbing:</strong> Use a dab rig or e-nail at 315-400°C for optimal flavour and immediate effects. This is the most popular method for hash oil.</li>\n<li><strong>Vaporizing:</strong> Load into a concentrate-compatible vaporizer for portable, discreet consumption with smooth vapour production.</li>\n<li><strong>Topping Flower:</strong> Add a small amount to bowls, joints, or blunts to significantly enhance potency and effects.</li>\n<li><strong>Edible Infusion:</strong> Incorporate into oils or butter for homemade edibles. Already activated, so no decarboxylation needed.</li>\n<li><strong>Topical Application:</strong> Apply directly to skin for localized relief of pain and inflammation without psychoactive effects.</li>\n</ul>\n<h3>Onset &amp; Duration</h3>\n<ul>\n<li><strong>Onset (Inhalation):</strong> Immediate to 5 minutes for dabbing and vaporizing</li>\n<li><strong>Onset (Oral):</strong> 30-90 minutes when consumed as an edible</li>\n<li><strong>Onset (Topical):</strong> 15-45 minutes for localized effects</li>\n<li><strong>Peak Effects:</strong> 15-45 minutes for inhalation; 2-3 hours for oral consumption</li>\n<li><strong>Duration:</strong> 2-4 hours for inhalation; 4-8 hours for oral consumption; 2-4 hours for topical application</li>\n</ul>\n<h3>Best Use Cases</h3>\n<p>Mohawk Medibles Hash Oil is ideal for experienced consumers seeking fast-acting, potent relief. The versatile formulation works excellently for managing chronic pain, severe nausea, and inflammation. Perfect for evening use when you need powerful relaxation and symptom relief. The variety of consumption methods makes it adaptable to your lifestyle—dab for immediate effects, infuse for long-lasting edibles, or apply topically for targeted relief without intoxication.</p>\n<p><strong>⚠️ Important Safety Information:</strong> Hash oil contains very high THC levels (70-86%). This product is for experienced users – beginners should start with lower doses or those with low tolerance. Start with minimal amounts and wait 15-20 minutes before consuming more when inhaling, or 2+ hours when consuming orally. Do not operate vehicles or machinery after use. Store securely away from children and pets.</p>\n<h2>❓ Frequently Asked Questions</h2>\n<h3>What is Medibles Hash Oil and how is it made?</h3>\n<p><strong>A:</strong> Medibles Hash Oil is a concentrated cannabis extract produced by Mohawk Medibles using premium cannabis flower. This home-made concentrate preserves the plant’s beneficial compounds while removing plant material, resulting in a potent oil with 70-86% THC content. Available in Regular, Premium, Cherry, and Honey varieties in both 5ml and 2g bottles.</p>\n<h3>How potent is Medibles Hash Oil compared to regular cannabis?</h3>\n<p><strong>A:</strong> With 70-86% THC, Medibles Hash Oil is approximately 3-4 times more potent than premium cannabis flower (typically 20-25% THC). This extreme potency means you need significantly less product to achieve desired effects. We strongly recommend this product for experienced consumers only, and advise starting with rice grain-sized amounts.</p>\n<h3>Can I use Medibles Hash Oil in multiple ways?</h3>\n<p><strong>A:</strong> Yes! Medibles Hash Oil is incredibly versatile. You can dab it using a rig, vaporize it in a concentrate pen, add it to joints or bowls, infuse it into edibles (no decarboxylation required), or apply it topically to skin for localized pain relief. This versatility makes it an excellent value for consumers who want multiple consumption options from one product.</p>\n<h3>What’s the difference between Regular, Premium, Cherry, and Honey varieties?</h3>\n<p><strong>A:</strong> Regular offers classic cannabis flavour and effects at an excellent value point. Premium is crafted from top-shelf flower for enhanced potency and terpene profiles. Cherry and Honey varieties feature natural flavouring for those who prefer a more palatable taste, especially when consuming orally or adding to edibles. All varieties maintain the 70-86% THC potency range.</p>\n<h3>How should I store Medibles Hash Oil?</h3>\n<p><strong>A:</strong> Store your hash oil in its original container in a cool, dark place away from direct sunlight and heat sources. A drawer or cupboard works well. Avoid storing in the refrigerator as this can change the consistency. Properly stored, hash oil maintains its potency for 6-12 months. Always keep securely sealed and out of reach of children and pets.</p>\n<h3>Is Medibles Hash Oil safe for beginners?</h3>\n<p><strong>A:</strong> No, we do not recommend hash oil for cannabis beginners. With 70-86% THC, this is an extremely potent concentrate best suited for experienced consumers with established tolerance. If you’re new to cannabis, we recommend starting with flower or low-dose edibles. If you’re experienced with flower but new to concentrates, start with the smallest possible amount and wait to assess effects.</p>\n<h3>Does Mohawk Medibles ship hash oil across Canada?</h3>\n<p><strong>A:</strong> Yes! We offer fast, discreet Canada-wide shipping on all Medibles Hash Oil products. Orders placed before 2 PM EST are processed the same day. All packages arrive in plain, unmarked packaging with no indication of contents. We ship from Tyendinaga Mohawk Territory and deliver to all Canadian provinces and territories.</p>\n</div>\n</div>",
