        "descriptionHTML": "<div class=\"tab-pane active\" id=\"tab-description\">\n<div class=\"detail-tab-desc detail-content-wrap\">\n<h2 data-end=\"227\" data-start=\"176\">🐎 <strong data-end=\"225\" data-start=\"181\">AFG Horseman </strong><strong data-end=\"225\" data-start=\"181\">Hash – Premium Afghan Resin</strong></h2>\n<h2 data-end=\"227\" data-start=\"176\"><strong data-end=\"289\" data-start=\"228\" style=\"font-size: 16px;\">Indica • Up to 60% THC • Deep Calm + Classic Afghan Spice</strong></h2>\n<hr/>\n<p data-end=\"988\" data-start=\"702\">AFG Horseman Hash offers a <strong data-end=\"766\" data-start=\"729\">true Afghan-style hash experience</strong>, crafted using classic hand-pressed techniques that preserve the resin’s natural oils and potency.<br data-end=\"868\" data-start=\"865\"/><strong data-end=\"883\" data-start=\"868\">Right away,</strong> you’ll notice its soft, pliable texture—easy to break, easy to roll, and ideal for mixing or vaporizing.</p>\n<p data-end=\"1207\" data-start=\"990\"><strong data-end=\"1017\" data-start=\"990\">As you bring it closer,</strong> a bold aroma rises: earthy, spicy, and slightly sweet.<br data-end=\"1075\" data-start=\"1072\"/><strong data-end=\"1091\" data-start=\"1075\">Once heated,</strong> the flavour becomes richer, offering a warm, smooth smoke with classic Afghan spice layered over deep earthy notes.</p>\n<p data-end=\"1534\" data-start=\"1209\"><strong data-end=\"1237\" data-start=\"1209\">After your first inhale,</strong> the Indica effects begin to settle in. A warm wave spreads through your entire body, easing tension and quieting the mind.<br data-end=\"1363\" data-start=\"1360\"/><strong data-end=\"1387\" data-start=\"1363\">As the high deepens,</strong> expect a soothing calm that slowly transforms into a heavy, sleepy melt—perfect for stress relief, pain management, and deep nighttime relaxation.</p>\n<p data-end=\"1715\" data-start=\"1536\">With <strong data-end=\"1567\" data-start=\"1541\">THC reaching up to 60%</strong>, AFG Horseman Hash is strong enough for seasoned hash lovers, but smooth enough for anyone who appreciates <strong data-end=\"1714\" data-start=\"1675\">classic, premium, old-world hashish</strong>.</p>\n<hr data-end=\"1720\" data-start=\"1717\"/>\n<h3 data-end=\"1740\" data-start=\"1722\">🔥 <strong data-end=\"1738\" data-start=\"1727\">EFFECTS</strong></h3>\n<ul data-end=\"1876\" data-start=\"1741\">\n<li data-end=\"1765\" data-start=\"1741\">\n<p data-end=\"1765\" data-start=\"1743\">Deep body relaxation</p>\n</li>\n<li data-end=\"1789\" data-start=\"1766\">\n<p data-end=\"1789\" data-start=\"1768\">Calm, peaceful mind</p>\n</li>\n<li data-end=\"1818\" data-start=\"1790\">\n<p data-end=\"1818\" data-start=\"1792\">Sedative, sleepy comfort</p>\n</li>\n<li data-end=\"1844\" data-start=\"1819\">\n<p data-end=\"1844\" data-start=\"1821\">Long-lasting euphoria</p>\n</li>\n<li data-end=\"1876\" data-start=\"1845\">\n<p data-end=\"1876\" data-start=\"1847\">Stress relief + muscle ease</p>\n</li>\n</ul>\n<hr data-end=\"1881\" data-start=\"1878\"/>\n<h3 data-end=\"1907\" data-start=\"1883\">🌿 <strong data-end=\"1905\" data-start=\"1888\">MAY HELP WITH</strong></h3>\n<ul data-end=\"1996\" data-start=\"1908\">\n<li data-end=\"1924\" data-start=\"1908\">\n<p data-end=\"1924\" data-start=\"1910\">Chronic pain</p>\n</li>\n<li data-end=\"1937\" data-start=\"1925\">\n<p data-end=\"1937\" data-start=\"1927\">Insomnia</p>\n</li>\n<li data-end=\"1948\" data-start=\"1938\">\n<p data-end=\"1948\" data-start=\"1940\">Stress</p>\n</li>\n<li data-end=\"1960\" data-start=\"1949\">\n<p data-end=\"1960\" data-start=\"1951\">Anxiety</p>\n</li>\n<li data-end=\"1979\" data-start=\"1961\">\n<p data-end=\"1979\" data-start=\"1963\">Muscle tension</p>\n</li>\n<li data-end=\"1996\" data-start=\"1980\">\n<p data-end=\"1996\" data-start=\"1982\">Restlessness</p>\n</li>\n</ul>\n<hr data-end=\"2001\" data-start=\"1998\"/>\n<h3 data-end=\"2021\" data-start=\"2003\">🍃 <strong data-end=\"2019\" data-start=\"2008\">FLAVORS</strong></h3>\n<ul data-end=\"2070\" data-start=\"2022\">\n<li data-end=\"2031\" data-start=\"2022\">\n<p data-end=\"2031\" data-start=\"2024\">Spicy</p>\n</li>\n<li data-end=\"2042\" data-start=\"2032\">\n<p data-end=\"2042\" data-start=\"2034\">Earthy</p>\n</li>\n<li data-end=\"2052\" data-start=\"2043\">\n<p data-end=\"2052\" data-start=\"2045\">Sweet</p>\n</li>\n<li data-end=\"2070\" data-start=\"2053\">\n<p data-end=\"2070\" data-start=\"2055\">Classic resin</p>\n</li>\n</ul>\n<hr data-end=\"2075\" data-start=\"2072\"/>\n<h3 data-end=\"2095\" data-start=\"2077\">🌬️ <strong data-end=\"2093\" data-start=\"2083\">AROMAS</strong></h3>\n<ul data-end=\"2167\" data-start=\"2096\">\n<li data-end=\"2110\" data-start=\"2096\">\n<p data-end=\"2110\" data-start=\"2098\">Deep earth</p>\n</li>\n<li data-end=\"2125\" data-start=\"2111\">\n<p data-end=\"2125\" data-start=\"2113\">Warm spice</p>\n</li>\n<li data-end=\"2144\" data-start=\"2126\">\n<p data-end=\"2144\" data-start=\"2128\">Hash sweetness</p>\n</li>\n<li data-end=\"2167\" data-start=\"2145\">\n<p data-end=\"2167\" data-start=\"2147\">Afghan-style scent</p>\n</li>\n</ul>\n<hr/>\n<h2>💡 Usage Guide</h2>\n<h3>Recommended Dosage</h3>\n<ul>\n<li><strong>Beginners:</strong> Start with a rice grain-sized piece (approximately 0.025-0.05g). Hash is significantly more potent than flower.</li>\n<li><strong>Experienced Users:</strong> 0.1-0.2g per session, adjusting based on tolerance and desired effects.</li>\n<li><strong>High Tolerance:</strong> Up to 0.3g per session for seasoned concentrate consumers.</li>\n</ul>\n<h3>Consumption Methods</h3>\n<ul>\n<li><strong>Smoking:</strong> Crumble and mix with flower in joints, pipes, or bongs for enhanced potency and traditional experience.</li>\n<li><strong>Vaporizing:</strong> Use hash-compatible vaporizer at 180-210°C for smooth, flavourful vapour with maximum terpene preservation.</li>\n<li><strong>Hot Knives:</strong> Traditional method heating two knives and pressing hash between them for immediate effects.</li>\n<li><strong>Topping Bowls:</strong> Add small pieces atop flower bowls for elevated potency without altering your regular routine.</li>\n<li><strong>Hash Edibles (Advanced):</strong> To make edibles, decarboxylate hash at 110-120°C (230-250°F) for 30-40 minutes to activate THC. Mix into butter or oil-based recipes. Effects take 30-120 minutes and last 6-12 hours. Hash edibles are significantly more potent than flower edibles—start with 1/4 of your normal flower edible dose.</li>\n</ul>\n<h3>Onset &amp; Duration</h3>\n<ul>\n<li><strong>Onset (Smoking/Vaping):</strong> 2-10 minutes</li>\n<li><strong>Onset (Edibles):</strong> 30-120 minutes</li>\n<li><strong>Peak Effects:</strong> 15-45 minutes (inhaled) or 2-4 hours (edibles)</li>\n<li><strong>Duration:</strong> 2-4 hours (inhaled) or 6-12 hours (edibles)</li>\n</ul>\n<p><strong>⚠️ Important:</strong> Hash is significantly more potent than regular flower. Start with minimal amounts and wait to assess effects before consuming more. for experienced users – beginners should start with lower doses or those new to concentrates.</p>\n</div>\n</div>",
