        "descriptionHTML": "<div class=\"tab-pane active\" id=\"tab-description\">\n<div class=\"detail-tab-desc detail-content-wrap\">\n<p>**Buy Entourage Cigars online in Canada at Mohawk Medibles**, your trusted Indigenous-owned cannabis dispensary. Shop these premium machine-rolled cigars crafted with quality tobacco and natural leaf wrapping, and enjoy fast Canada-wide shipping with same-day processing. Order now for discreet delivery straight from Tyendinaga Mohawk Territory. Whether you’re a seasoned cigar enthusiast or exploring smooth, affordable options for everyday enjoyment, Entourage Cigars deliver consistent quality and mellow satisfaction in every draw.</p>\n<p>–</p>\n<h2>💡 Usage Guide</h2>\n<h3>Recommended Smoking Experience</h3>\n<ul>\n<li><strong>Beginners:</strong> Take your time with slow, even draws to appreciate the smooth, mellow flavor profile</li>\n<li><strong>Regular Smokers:</strong> Enjoy at your preferred pace; the natural leaf wrap provides a consistent burn throughout</li>\n<li><strong>Pairing Suggestions:</strong> Pairs well with coffee, whiskey, or enjoyed solo during relaxation time</li>\n</ul>\n<h3>How to Enjoy</h3>\n<ul>\n<li><strong>Lighting:</strong> Toast the foot evenly with a quality lighter or cedar spill, rotating for an even burn</li>\n<li><strong>Draw Technique:</strong> Take slow, gentle draws to prevent overheating and maintain smooth flavor</li>\n<li><strong>Ash Management:</strong> Allow ash to build naturally; tap gently when needed to maintain airflow</li>\n</ul>\n<h3>Burn Time &amp; Experience</h3>\n<ul>\n<li><strong>Average Burn Time:</strong> 15-25 minutes depending on draw frequency</li>\n<li><strong>Flavor Profile:</strong> Mellow and smooth throughout, with natural tobacco notes</li>\n<li><strong>Best Enjoyed:</strong> During breaks, after meals, or as part of your evening wind-down routine</li>\n</ul>\n<h3>Storage &amp; Freshness</h3>\n<p>Store your Entourage Cigars in a cool, dry place away from direct sunlight. For optimal freshness, keep them in their original packaging or a humidor at 65-70% humidity. Properly stored cigars maintain their quality and flavor for extended periods.</p>\n<h2>❓ Frequently Asked Questions</h2>\n<h3>What makes Entourage Cigars different from premium hand-rolled cigars?</h3>\n<p><strong>A:</strong> Entourage Cigars are machine-rolled for consistency and affordability while still using quality tobacco and natural leaf wrapping. They offer a smooth, mellow smoking experience at an accessible price point, making them perfect for everyday enjoyment without compromising on quality.</p>\n<h3>Are Entourage Cigars suitable for beginners?</h3>\n<p><strong>A:</strong> Yes! Entourage Cigars feature a mellow flavor profile and smooth draw that’s ideal for those new to cigar smoking. The consistent construction ensures an easy, forgiving smoke that won’t overwhelm beginners while still satisfying experienced smokers.</p>\n<h3>How should I store my Entourage Cigars?</h3>\n<p><strong>A:</strong> Keep your cigars in a cool, dry place away from direct sunlight and heat sources. While they don’t require a premium humidor, storing them in their original packaging or a basic humidor at 65-70% humidity will maintain optimal freshness and prevent them from drying out.</p>\n<h3>What’s the burn time for an Entourage Cigar?</h3>\n<p><strong>A:</strong> You can expect approximately 15-25 minutes of smoking time per cigar, depending on your draw frequency and smoking pace. The natural leaf wrap and quality construction ensure an even, consistent burn from start to finish.</p>\n<h3>Does Mohawk Medibles ship Entourage Cigars across Canada?</h3>\n<p><strong>A:</strong> Absolutely! We offer fast, discreet Canada-wide shipping with same-day processing on orders placed before 2 PM EST. All packages arrive in plain, unmarked packaging to ensure your privacy and product freshness.</p>\n<h3>Can I buy Entourage Cigars individually or in bulk?</h3>\n<p><strong>A:</strong> Entourage Cigars are available as singles, perfect for trying the variety or enjoying occasional smokes. For regular smokers, consider stocking up to ensure you always have quality cigars on hand. Check our product options for current availability and bundle deals.</p>\n<h3>What flavor profile can I expect from Entourage Cigars?</h3>\n<p><strong>A:</strong> Entourage Cigars deliver a smooth, mellow smoking experience with natural tobacco notes. The flavor is approachable and balanced—not too strong or harsh—making them versatile for any time of day and suitable for both new and experienced cigar enthusiasts.</p>\n</div>\n</div>",
