        "descriptionHTML": "<div class=\"tab-pane active\" id=\"tab-description\">\n<div class=\"detail-tab-desc detail-content-wrap\">\n<p>**Buy WALT HERB CO. Infused Druley Kaboodle Pre Roll online in Canada at Mohawk Medibles**, your trusted Indigenous-owned cannabis dispensary. Shop this premium 1.1g infused pre-roll featuring Godfather OG and enjoy fast Canada-wide shipping with same-day processing. Order now for discreet delivery of this potent combination of high-grade flower, hashish, diamonds, and terp sauce from Tyendinaga Mohawk Territory.</p>\n<h2>🧬 Strain Profile</h2>\n<h3>Genetics &amp; Lineage</h3>\n<p>Godfather OG is a legendary indica-dominant hybrid born from the powerful cross of XXX OG and Alpha OG. Known as “The Don of All OGs,” this strain has earned its reputation as one of the most potent OG varieties available, with genetics deeply rooted in the celebrated OG Kush lineage. The strain’s prestigious parentage delivers the classic OG experience amplified to premium levels.</p>\n<h3>Dominant Terpenes</h3>\n<ul>\n<li><strong>Myrcene:</strong> Provides earthy, musky notes and enhances the sedative qualities</li>\n<li><strong>Limonene:</strong> Contributes citrus undertones and mood-elevating properties</li>\n<li><strong>Caryophyllene:</strong> Adds spicy, peppery notes with potential therapeutic benefits</li>\n</ul>\n<h3>Cannabinoid Profile</h3>\n<p>This infused pre-roll features significantly elevated potency due to the addition of hashish, diamonds, and terp sauce. The base Godfather OG flower typically contains 22-28% THC, but the infusion process amplifies total cannabinoid content substantially, making this suitable for experienced consumers seeking maximum potency.</p>\n<h3>Appearance &amp; Structure</h3>\n<p>The Druley Kaboodle pre-roll showcases Walt Herb Co.’s commitment to quality craftsmanship. Inside, you’ll find dense, resinous Godfather OG flower enhanced with visible concentrates. The infusion creates a rich, glistening appearance with amber-hued diamonds and golden terp sauce coating the premium flower and hashish blend.</p>\n<h3>Similar Strains</h3>\n<p>If you enjoy Godfather OG infused pre-rolls, you might also appreciate: <strong>Death Bubba</strong> (similar heavy indica effects), <strong>Pink Kush</strong> (comparable body relaxation), <strong>Tom Ford Pink Kush</strong> (premium potency), and <strong>Black Diamond OG</strong> (intense sedative properties).</p>\n<p>–</p>\n<h2>💡 Usage Guide</h2>\n<h3>Recommended Dosage</h3>\n<ul>\n<li><strong>Beginners:</strong> Take 1-2 small puffs and wait 10-15 minutes before consuming more. Consider starting with lower THC flower first</li>\n<li><strong>Experienced Users:</strong> Start with 2-3 small puffs and wait 10-15 minutes to assess effects</li>\n<li><strong>High Tolerance Consumers:</strong> Smoke half to the full 1.1g pre-roll per session, depending on desired intensity</li>\n</ul>\n<h3>Consumption Methods</h3>\n<ul>\n<li><strong>Direct Smoking:</strong> Light and smoke like a regular pre-roll; expect slower, more even burn due to concentrate infusion</li>\n<li><strong>Shared Sessions:</strong> Perfect for passing among 2-3 experienced users due to high potency</li>\n<li><strong>Pacing:</strong> Take breaks between puffs to fully appreciate the layered effects of flower, hash, diamonds, and terp sauce</li>\n</ul>\n<h3>Onset &amp; Duration</h3>\n<ul>\n<li><strong>Onset:</strong> 2-5 minutes (concentrates provide rapid effects)</li>\n<li><strong>Peak Effects:</strong> 15-45 minutes (extended peak due to concentrate combination)</li>\n<li><strong>Duration:</strong> 3-5 hours (longer-lasting than standard flower due to infusion)</li>\n</ul>\n<h3>Best Use Cases</h3>\n<p>Ideal for evening and nighttime use when you have no obligations. The Godfather OG infusion delivers profound body relaxation and sedative effects perfect for unwinding after a long day, managing discomfort, or preparing for deep, restful sleep. Best enjoyed in a comfortable setting where you can fully relax. Not recommended before work, driving, or activities requiring alertness.</p>\n<p><strong>⚠️ Important:</strong> This is a premium infused product with significantly elevated potency. The combination of flower, hashish, diamonds, and terp sauce creates extremely strong effects. Start with minimal consumption and wait before consuming more. For experienced consumers only.</p>\n<h2>❓ Frequently Asked Questions</h2>\n<h3>What makes the WALT HERB CO. Druley Kaboodle Pre Roll different from regular pre-rolls?</h3>\n<p><strong>A:</strong> This infused pre-roll combines high-grade Godfather OG flower with hashish, THCA diamonds, and terp sauce, creating a significantly more potent experience than standard pre-rolls. The multi-layer infusion delivers enhanced flavour, aroma, and substantially stronger effects suitable for experienced consumers seeking premium potency.</p>\n<h3>How strong is the WALT HERB CO. Infused Druley Kaboodle Pre Roll?</h3>\n<p><strong>A:</strong> This is an extremely potent product due to the concentrate infusion. While the base Godfather OG flower contains 22-28% THC, the addition of hashish, diamonds, and terp sauce significantly increases total cannabinoid content. This pre-roll is recommended for experienced consumers with established tolerance only.</p>\n<h3>Is the Druley Kaboodle Pre Roll suitable for beginners?</h3>\n<p><strong>A:</strong> No, this infused pre-roll is for experienced users – beginners should start with lower doses or those with low tolerance. The combination of concentrates creates very strong effects that may be overwhelming for inexperienced users. We suggest starting with regular flower or low-potency pre-rolls before trying infused products.</p>\n<h3>What effects can I expect from Godfather OG infusion?</h3>\n<p><strong>A:</strong> Expect powerful indica-dominant effects including deep body relaxation, sedation, euphoria, and stress relief. Users report feeling heavily relaxed with strong couch-lock effects. The infusion amplifies these characteristics, making it ideal for evening use, pain management, insomnia relief, and deep relaxation.</p>\n<h3>How should I store my WALT HERB CO. Pre Roll?</h3>\n<p><strong>A:</strong> Store in a cool, dark place in its original packaging or an airtight container. Keep away from heat, direct sunlight, and moisture to preserve the concentrates and maintain freshness. Properly stored infused pre-rolls maintain quality for several months. Always keep out of reach of children and pets.</p>\n<h3>Does Mohawk Medibles ship WALT HERB CO. products across Canada?</h3>\n<p><strong>A:</strong> Yes! We offer fast, discreet Canada-wide shipping for all Walt Herb Co. products with same-day processing on orders placed before 2 PM EST. All packages arrive in plain, unmarked packaging to ensure privacy and discretion.</p>\n<h3>Can I smoke this pre-roll throughout the day?</h3>\n<p><strong>A:</strong> Due to the high potency and sedative effects of Godfather OG infusion, this pre-roll is best reserved for evening or nighttime use when you have no responsibilities. The strong indica effects can cause drowsiness and impairment, making it unsuitable for daytime activities, work, or driving.</p>\n</div>\n</div>",
