        "descriptionHTML": "<div class=\"tab-pane active\" id=\"tab-description\">\n<div class=\"detail-tab-desc detail-content-wrap\">\n<p>**Buy Mohawk Medibles Caramels 200mg online in Canada at Mohawk Medibles**, your trusted Indigenous-owned cannabis dispensary. Shop this delicious THC edible 5-pack and enjoy fast Canada-wide shipping with same-day processing. Order now for discreet delivery and experience premium cannabis caramels crafted for consistent dosing and exceptional flavour. With 40mg per caramel, these yummy treats are perfect for experienced users seeking reliable, long-lasting effects.</p>\n<p>–</p>\n<h2>💡 Usage Guide</h2>\n<h3>Recommended Dosage</h3>\n<ul>\n<li><strong>Beginners:</strong> Start with half a caramel (20mg THC) and wait at least 2 hours before consuming more</li>\n<li><strong>Experienced Users:</strong> One full caramel (40mg THC) provides moderate to strong effects</li>\n<li><strong>High Tolerance:</strong> 1-2 caramels (40-80mg THC) for desired effects</li>\n</ul>\n<h3>Consumption Tips</h3>\n<ul>\n<li><strong>Start Low, Go Slow:</strong> Edibles can take 30-120 minutes to take effect depending on metabolism and stomach contents</li>\n<li><strong>Storage:</strong> Keep refrigerated to maintain freshness and prevent melting, especially in warm weather</li>\n<li><strong>Take with Food:</strong> Consuming with a light snack can improve absorption and reduce potential nausea</li>\n<li><strong>Stay Hydrated:</strong> Drink plenty of water throughout your experience</li>\n<li><strong>Plan Ahead:</strong> Effects can last 4-8 hours, so ensure you have no obligations or responsibilities</li>\n</ul>\n<h3>Onset &amp; Duration</h3>\n<ul>\n<li><strong>Onset:</strong> 30-120 minutes (varies by metabolism, body weight, and whether consumed on empty stomach)</li>\n<li><strong>Peak Effects:</strong> 2-3 hours after onset</li>\n<li><strong>Duration:</strong> 4-8 hours total, with gradual comedown</li>\n</ul>\n<h3>Best Use Cases</h3>\n<p>Perfect for evening relaxation, movie nights, creative projects, or deep rest. The long-lasting effects make these caramels ideal for experienced users seeking sustained relief or recreational enjoyment. Best consumed during days off or when you have several hours free. Not recommended before work, driving, or operating machinery.</p>\n<p><strong>⚠️ Important:</strong> At 40mg per caramel, these are potent edibles intended for experienced cannabis users. Never exceed your personal tolerance level. Keep refrigerated and store out of reach of children and pets.</p>\n<h2>❓ Frequently Asked Questions</h2>\n<h3>How long do Mohawk Medibles Caramels take to work?</h3>\n<p><strong>A:</strong> These THC caramels typically take 30-120 minutes to take effect, depending on your metabolism, body weight, and whether you’ve eaten recently. Effects can last 4-8 hours, so plan accordingly and avoid consuming more until you’ve waited at least 2 hours to feel the full effects.</p>\n<h3>How many mg of THC are in each caramel?</h3>\n<p><strong>A:</strong> Each caramel contains 40mg of THC, with 5 caramels per package for a total of 200mg THC. This makes them suitable for experienced users who understand their tolerance levels.</p>\n<h3>Can I eat a whole caramel at once?</h3>\n<p><strong>A:</strong> If you’re new to edibles or have low tolerance, start with half a caramel (20mg) and wait at least 2 hours before consuming more. Experienced users familiar with 40mg+ doses can consume a full caramel, but we always recommend starting low and going slow with edibles.</p>\n<h3>Are these caramels safe for beginners?</h3>\n<p><strong>A:</strong> At 40mg per caramel, these are potent edibles best suited for experienced cannabis consumers. Beginners should start with lower-dose edibles (2.5-10mg) to understand their tolerance before trying higher-potency products like these caramels.</p>\n<h3>Why do I need to refrigerate these caramels?</h3>\n<p><strong>A:</strong> Refrigeration keeps your caramels fresh, maintains their texture, and prevents melting, especially during warmer months. Store them in their original packaging in the refrigerator to preserve quality and potency. Properly stored, they’ll maintain freshness for several months.</p>\n<h3>Does Mohawk Medibles ship these caramels across Canada?</h3>\n<p><strong>A:</strong> Yes! We offer fast, discreet Canada-wide shipping with same-day processing on orders placed before 2 PM EST. All packages are shipped in plain, unmarked packaging with no indication of contents. Your caramels will arrive safely packaged to prevent damage during transit.</p>\n<h3>What’s the 3 for $25 deal?</h3>\n<p><strong>A:</strong> This special offer lets you purchase three 5-packs of Mohawk Medibles Caramels for just $25, giving you 15 caramels total (600mg THC) at an exceptional value. It’s our way of rewarding loyal customers who love these delicious, potent treats.</p>\n</div>\n</div>",
