        "descriptionHTML": "<div class=\"tab-pane active\" id=\"tab-description\">\n<div class=\"detail-tab-desc detail-content-wrap\">\n<h2 data-end=\"201\" data-start=\"162\">🍯 <strong data-end=\"199\" data-start=\"167\">Honey Hash – $5/Gram Special</strong></h2>\n<p data-end=\"247\" data-start=\"202\"><strong data-end=\"247\" data-start=\"202\">Indica-Dominant • Smooth • Sweet + Earthy • THC: 18%–22%</strong></p>\n<hr/>\n<p data-end=\"865\" data-start=\"611\">Honey Hash delivers a <strong data-end=\"665\" data-start=\"633\">rich, rustic hash experience</strong> with a sweet twist.<br data-end=\"688\" data-start=\"685\"/><strong data-end=\"719\" data-start=\"688\">Right from the first whiff,</strong> you’ll notice warm, earthy tones blending with a mellow honey sweetness that makes this hash stand out from regular Backwoods-style concentrates.</p>\n<p data-end=\"1118\" data-start=\"867\"><strong data-end=\"893\" data-start=\"867\">As you break it apart,</strong> the deep woody scent grows stronger, mixing smoothly with the natural sweetness.<br data-end=\"977\" data-start=\"974\"/><strong data-end=\"993\" data-start=\"977\">When smoked,</strong> Honey Hash gives you a full-bodied flavour—earthy, warm, and slightly sweet—creating a smooth and comforting hit every time.</p>\n<p data-end=\"1387\" data-start=\"1120\"><strong data-end=\"1147\" data-start=\"1120\">Soon after your inhale,</strong> the Indica-heavy relaxation begins to settle in. A calm wave eases into your body, softening tension and slowing racing thoughts.<br data-end=\"1280\" data-start=\"1277\"/><strong data-end=\"1304\" data-start=\"1280\">As the high deepens,</strong> a mental clarity remains, letting you unwind without feeling foggy or overwhelmed.</p>\n<p data-end=\"1559\" data-start=\"1389\">Honey Hash is ideal for evening sessions, stress relief after a long day, or any moment when you want a <strong data-end=\"1532\" data-start=\"1493\">simple, strong, slow-melting unwind</strong> with a smooth, sweet edge.</p>\n<hr data-end=\"1564\" data-start=\"1561\"/>\n<h3 data-end=\"1584\" data-start=\"1566\">🔥 <strong data-end=\"1582\" data-start=\"1571\">EFFECTS</strong></h3>\n<ul data-end=\"1685\" data-start=\"1585\">\n<li data-end=\"1604\" data-start=\"1585\">\n<p data-end=\"1604\" data-start=\"1587\">Deep relaxation</p>\n</li>\n<li data-end=\"1626\" data-start=\"1605\">\n<p data-end=\"1626\" data-start=\"1607\">Calming body melt</p>\n</li>\n<li data-end=\"1641\" data-start=\"1627\">\n<p data-end=\"1641\" data-start=\"1629\">Clear mind</p>\n</li>\n<li data-end=\"1659\" data-start=\"1642\">\n<p data-end=\"1659\" data-start=\"1644\">Stress relief</p>\n</li>\n<li data-end=\"1685\" data-start=\"1660\">\n<p data-end=\"1685\" data-start=\"1662\">Smooth evening unwind</p>\n</li>\n</ul>\n<hr data-end=\"1690\" data-start=\"1687\"/>\n<h3 data-end=\"1716\" data-start=\"1692\">🌿 <strong data-end=\"1714\" data-start=\"1697\">MAY HELP WITH</strong></h3>\n<ul data-end=\"1810\" data-start=\"1717\">\n<li data-end=\"1727\" data-start=\"1717\">\n<p data-end=\"1727\" data-start=\"1719\">Stress</p>\n</li>\n<li data-end=\"1739\" data-start=\"1728\">\n<p data-end=\"1739\" data-start=\"1730\">Anxiety</p>\n</li>\n<li data-end=\"1756\" data-start=\"1740\">\n<p data-end=\"1756\" data-start=\"1742\">Chronic pain</p>\n</li>\n<li data-end=\"1768\" data-start=\"1757\">\n<p data-end=\"1768\" data-start=\"1759\">Tension</p>\n</li>\n<li data-end=\"1785\" data-start=\"1769\">\n<p data-end=\"1785\" data-start=\"1771\">Restlessness</p>\n</li>\n<li data-end=\"1810\" data-start=\"1786\">\n<p data-end=\"1810\" data-start=\"1788\">Trouble winding down</p>\n</li>\n</ul>\n<hr data-end=\"1815\" data-start=\"1812\"/>\n<h3 data-end=\"1835\" data-start=\"1817\">🍯 <strong data-end=\"1833\" data-start=\"1822\">FLAVORS</strong></h3>\n<ul data-end=\"1899\" data-start=\"1836\">\n<li data-end=\"1855\" data-start=\"1836\">\n<p data-end=\"1855\" data-start=\"1838\">Honey sweetness</p>\n</li>\n<li data-end=\"1866\" data-start=\"1856\">\n<p data-end=\"1866\" data-start=\"1858\">Earthy</p>\n</li>\n<li data-end=\"1876\" data-start=\"1867\">\n<p data-end=\"1876\" data-start=\"1869\">Woody</p>\n</li>\n<li data-end=\"1899\" data-start=\"1877\">\n<p data-end=\"1899\" data-start=\"1879\">Natural hash tones</p>\n</li>\n</ul>\n<hr data-end=\"1904\" data-start=\"1901\"/>\n<h3 data-end=\"1924\" data-start=\"1906\">🌬️ <strong data-end=\"1922\" data-start=\"1912\">AROMAS</strong></h3>\n<ul data-end=\"1994\" data-start=\"1925\">\n<li data-end=\"1939\" data-start=\"1925\">\n<p data-end=\"1939\" data-start=\"1927\">Warm honey</p>\n</li>\n<li data-end=\"1956\" data-start=\"1940\">\n<p data-end=\"1956\" data-start=\"1942\">Earthy woods</p>\n</li>\n<li data-end=\"1972\" data-start=\"1957\">\n<p data-end=\"1972\" data-start=\"1959\">Light spice</p>\n</li>\n<li data-end=\"1994\" data-start=\"1973\">\n<p data-end=\"1994\" data-start=\"1975\">Smooth hash aroma</p>\n</li>\n</ul>\n<hr/>\n<h2>💡 Usage Guide</h2>\n<h3>Recommended Dosage</h3>\n<ul>\n<li><strong>Beginners:</strong> Start with a rice grain-sized piece (approximately 0.025-0.05g). Hash is significantly more potent than flower.</li>\n<li><strong>Experienced Users:</strong> 0.1-0.2g per session, adjusting based on tolerance and desired effects.</li>\n<li><strong>High Tolerance:</strong> Up to 0.3g per session for seasoned concentrate consumers.</li>\n</ul>\n<h3>Consumption Methods</h3>\n<ul>\n<li><strong>Smoking:</strong> Crumble and mix with flower in joints, pipes, or bongs for enhanced potency and traditional experience.</li>\n<li><strong>Vaporizing:</strong> Use hash-compatible vaporizer at 180-210°C for smooth, flavourful vapour with maximum terpene preservation.</li>\n<li><strong>Hot Knives:</strong> Traditional method heating two knives and pressing hash between them for immediate effects.</li>\n<li><strong>Topping Bowls:</strong> Add small pieces atop flower bowls for elevated potency without altering your regular routine.</li>\n<li><strong>Hash Edibles (Advanced):</strong> To make edibles, decarboxylate hash at 110-120°C (230-250°F) for 30-40 minutes to activate THC. Mix into butter or oil-based recipes. Effects take 30-120 minutes and last 6-12 hours. Hash edibles are significantly more potent than flower edibles—start with 1/4 of your normal flower edible dose.</li>\n</ul>\n<h3>Onset &amp; Duration</h3>\n<ul>\n<li><strong>Onset (Smoking/Vaping):</strong> 2-10 minutes</li>\n<li><strong>Onset (Edibles):</strong> 30-120 minutes</li>\n<li><strong>Peak Effects:</strong> 15-45 minutes (inhaled) or 2-4 hours (edibles)</li>\n<li><strong>Duration:</strong> 2-4 hours (inhaled) or 6-12 hours (edibles)</li>\n</ul>\n<p><strong>⚠️ Important:</strong> Hash is significantly more potent than regular flower. Start with minimal amounts and wait to assess effects before consuming more. for experienced users – beginners should start with lower doses or those new to concentrates.</p>\n</div>\n</div>",
