        "descriptionHTML": "<div class=\"tab-pane active\" id=\"tab-description\">\n<div class=\"detail-tab-desc detail-content-wrap\">\n<p>**Buy GAS GANG 2g Disposable online in Canada at Mohawk Medibles**, your trusted Indigenous-owned cannabis dispensary. Shop this premium concentrate disposable vape and enjoy fast Canada-wide shipping with same-day processing. Order now for discreet delivery of this high-potency, convenient vaping solution made with premium distillate. Experience quality craftsmanship from Tyendinaga Mohawk Territory with hassle-free, rechargeable technology designed for experienced consumers.</p>\n<p>–</p>\n<h2>💡 Usage Guide</h2>\n<h3>Recommended Dosage</h3>\n<ul>\n<li><strong>Beginners:</strong> Start with 1-2 short puffs (1-2 seconds each) and wait 10-15 minutes to assess effects. Disposables deliver concentrated vapour quickly.</li>\n<li><strong>Experienced Users:</strong> 2-4 puffs per session, adjusting based on desired intensity and tolerance level.</li>\n<li><strong>High Tolerance:</strong> 4-6 puffs as needed, but allow time between sessions to avoid overconsumption.</li>\n</ul>\n<h3>How to Use Your Disposable</h3>\n<ul>\n<li><strong>Activation:</strong> Press the button 5 times rapidly to turn the device on. The indicator light will confirm activation.</li>\n<li><strong>Inhaling:</strong> Press and hold the button while inhaling slowly and steadily for 2-3 seconds. Release before exhaling.</li>\n<li><strong>Recharging:</strong> Connect to USB charger when battery is low (indicator light will flash). Fully charge before first use for optimal performance.</li>\n<li><strong>Turning Off:</strong> Press button 5 times rapidly to power off when not in use to preserve battery and oil.</li>\n</ul>\n<h3>Onset &amp; Duration</h3>\n<ul>\n<li><strong>Onset:</strong> 2-5 minutes (effects felt almost immediately)</li>\n<li><strong>Peak Effects:</strong> 15-30 minutes after inhalation</li>\n<li><strong>Duration:</strong> 1-3 hours depending on dosage and individual metabolism</li>\n</ul>\n<h3>Best Use Cases</h3>\n<p>Ideal for on-the-go convenience and discreet consumption. Perfect for experienced users seeking fast-acting relief or recreational effects without the need for additional equipment. The 2g capacity provides extended use compared to standard 1g disposables. Best suited for evening relaxation, social situations, or whenever you need quick, potent effects. Not recommended before operating vehicles or machinery.</p>\n<p><strong>⚠️ Important:</strong> Distillate concentrates are highly potent. Start with minimal inhalation if you’re new to vaping concentrates. Store upright in a cool, dry place away from direct sunlight and extreme temperatures.</p>\n<h2>❓ Frequently Asked Questions</h2>\n<h3>How do I activate my GAS GANG 2g Disposable?</h3>\n<p><strong>A:</strong> Press the button 5 times rapidly to turn the device on. The indicator light will illuminate to confirm activation. To turn off, press the button 5 times again. Always charge fully before first use for best performance.</p>\n<h3>How potent is the GAS GANG disposable vape?</h3>\n<p><strong>A:</strong> This disposable is made with premium distillate, which typically contains 80-95% THC. It’s a highly concentrated product recommended for experienced cannabis consumers. Start with 1-2 small puffs and wait 10-15 minutes to gauge effects before consuming more.</p>\n<h3>How long will a 2g disposable last?</h3>\n<p><strong>A:</strong> Usage varies by individual consumption habits. For moderate users taking 3-5 puffs per session, a 2g disposable typically provides 200-400 puffs, lasting anywhere from 1-3 weeks. Heavy users may finish it more quickly, while occasional users can extend its lifespan to a month or more.</p>\n<h3>Can I recharge the GAS GANG disposable?</h3>\n<p><strong>A:</strong> Yes, this disposable vape is rechargeable via USB connection. If you notice decreased vapour production or the indicator light flashing, connect to a USB charger. A full charge typically takes 30-60 minutes. The device is designed to last through the entire 2g of oil with proper charging.</p>\n<h3>How should I store my disposable vape?</h3>\n<p><strong>A:</strong> Store upright in a cool, dry place away from direct sunlight and heat sources. Extreme temperatures can affect oil viscosity and battery performance. Keep in original packaging when not in use to protect from damage. Always store out of reach of children and pets.</p>\n<h3>Does Mohawk Medibles ship GAS GANG disposables across Canada?</h3>\n<p><strong>A:</strong> Yes! We offer fast, discreet Canada-wide shipping on all vape products with same-day processing on orders placed before 2 PM EST. All packages arrive in plain, unmarked packaging with no indication of contents, ensuring complete privacy and discretion.</p>\n<h3>What if my disposable isn’t producing vapour?</h3>\n<p><strong>A:</strong> First, ensure the device is turned on (press button 5 times) and fully charged. Check that you’re pressing the button while inhaling. If the oil appears too thick, gently warm the device in your hands for a minute. If issues persist, contact our customer service team for assistance or replacement options.</p>\n</div>\n</div>",
