        "descriptionHTML": "<div class=\"tab-pane active\" id=\"tab-description\">\n<div class=\"detail-tab-desc detail-content-wrap\">\n<p>**Buy ZOLT Nicotine Pouches online in Canada at Mohawk Medibles**, your trusted Indigenous-owned dispensary. Shop these premium tobacco-free nicotine pouches in 8mg and 15mg strengths and enjoy fast Canada-wide shipping with same-day processing. Order now for discreet delivery of these convenient, smoke-free nicotine pouches available in four delicious flavours. Perfect for on-the-go satisfaction without the smoke or vapour.</p>\n<p>–</p>\n<h2>💡 Usage Guide</h2>\n<h3>Recommended Usage</h3>\n<ul>\n<li><strong>New Users:</strong> Start with 8mg strength pouches, use 1-2 pouches per day to assess tolerance</li>\n<li><strong>Regular Users:</strong> 8mg strength, use as needed throughout the day (maximum 20 pouches per day)</li>\n<li><strong>Experienced Users:</strong> 15mg strength for stronger satisfaction, use as needed (maximum 15 pouches per day)</li>\n</ul>\n<h3>How to Use</h3>\n<ul>\n<li><strong>Placement:</strong> Place one pouch between your upper lip and gum</li>\n<li><strong>Duration:</strong> Leave in place for 20-30 minutes for optimal nicotine release</li>\n<li><strong>Disposal:</strong> Remove pouch and dispose in waste bin (do not swallow)</li>\n<li><strong>Frequency:</strong> Wait at least 30 minutes between pouches</li>\n</ul>\n<h3>Onset &amp; Duration</h3>\n<ul>\n<li><strong>Onset:</strong> 2-5 minutes after placement</li>\n<li><strong>Peak Effects:</strong> 10-15 minutes</li>\n<li><strong>Duration:</strong> Effects last 20-30 minutes per pouch</li>\n</ul>\n<h3>Best Use Cases</h3>\n<p>Ideal for smoke-free nicotine satisfaction anywhere – at work, while travelling, indoors, or in social settings where smoking isn’t permitted. Perfect for those seeking a discreet, convenient alternative to cigarettes or vaping. No smoke, no vapour, no spitting required.</p>\n<p><strong>⚠️ Important:</strong> This product contains nicotine, which is highly addictive. Not intended for non-smokers or individuals under 19 years of age. Keep out of reach of children and pets.</p>\n<h2>❓ Frequently Asked Questions</h2>\n<h3>What’s the difference between 8mg and 15mg ZOLT nicotine pouches?</h3>\n<p><strong>A:</strong> The 8mg pouches contain 8 milligrams of nicotine per pouch and are ideal for light to moderate users or those new to nicotine pouches. The 15mg pouches contain 15 milligrams per pouch, providing stronger satisfaction for experienced users or those transitioning from heavy cigarette use. We recommend starting with 8mg if you’re unsure.</p>\n<h3>How do I use ZOLT nicotine pouches?</h3>\n<p><strong>A:</strong> Simply place one pouch between your upper lip and gum. Leave it in place for 20-30 minutes while the nicotine is absorbed through your gum tissue. You’ll feel a tingling sensation initially, which is normal. After use, remove the pouch and dispose of it properly. No spitting required, unlike traditional tobacco pouches.</p>\n<h3>Are ZOLT nicotine pouches tobacco-free?</h3>\n<p><strong>A:</strong> Yes, ZOLT pouches are completely tobacco-free. They contain pharmaceutical-grade nicotine, plant-based fibres, flavourings, and food-grade ingredients. This means no tobacco leaf, no smoke, and no tobacco-related staining or odour.</p>\n<h3>What flavours are available for ZOLT pouches?</h3>\n<p><strong>A:</strong> ZOLT offers four delicious flavours: Pink Lemonade (15mg), Orange (15mg), Spearmint (8mg), and Vanilla (15mg). Each flavour provides a refreshing taste experience while delivering consistent nicotine satisfaction. The Spearmint option is only available in 8mg strength.</p>\n<h3>How long does a canister of ZOLT pouches last?</h3>\n<p><strong>A:</strong> Each canister contains 20 pouches. Depending on your usage, one canister typically lasts 1-3 days for regular users. Light users may find a canister lasts 5-7 days. Store unused pouches in the canister in a cool, dry place to maintain freshness.</p>\n<h3>Does Mohawk Medibles ship ZOLT nicotine pouches across Canada?</h3>\n<p><strong>A:</strong> Yes! We offer fast, discreet Canada-wide shipping with same-day processing on orders placed before 2 PM EST. All packages arrive in plain, unmarked packaging. You must be 19+ to purchase nicotine products in Canada.</p>\n<h3>Can ZOLT pouches help me quit smoking?</h3>\n<p><strong>A:</strong> While ZOLT pouches are not marketed as smoking cessation products, many users find them helpful as a smoke-free alternative to cigarettes. They provide nicotine satisfaction without the harmful effects of tobacco smoke. Consult with a healthcare provider about smoking cessation strategies that may work for you.</p>\n</div>\n</div>",
