        "descriptionHTML": "<div class=\"tab-pane active\" id=\"tab-description\">\n<div class=\"detail-tab-desc detail-content-wrap\">\n<p>**Buy TRIPNOTIK Psilocybin Dark Chocolate Bar 5000MG online in Canada at Mohawk Medibles**, your trusted Indigenous-owned dispensary. Shop this premium psilocybin-infused dark chocolate and enjoy fast Canada-wide shipping with same-day processing. Order now for discreet delivery and experience the perfect blend of rich espresso trance dark milk chocolate with precisely dosed psilocybin for controlled, transformative experiences. Each 5000mg bar is expertly crafted for both microdosing and full psychedelic journeys.</p>\n<p>–</p>\n<h2>💡 Usage Guide</h2>\n<h3>Recommended Dosage</h3>\n<ul>\n<li><strong>Microdose (Beginners):</strong> Start with 1 square (80mg) to assess tolerance. Wait 60-90 minutes before considering additional consumption.</li>\n<li><strong>Low Dose (Mild Experience):</strong> 2-3 squares (160-240mg) for enhanced creativity, mood elevation, and gentle visual effects.</li>\n<li><strong>Moderate Dose (Experienced Users):</strong> 4-6 squares (320-480mg) for deeper introspective experiences and pronounced psychedelic effects.</li>\n<li><strong>High Dose (Advanced Users Only):</strong> 7+ squares (560mg+) for full psychedelic journeys. Only for those with significant experience.</li>\n</ul>\n<h3>Consumption Tips</h3>\n<ul>\n<li><strong>Set &amp; Setting:</strong> Ensure you’re in a comfortable, safe environment with trusted companions if desired.</li>\n<li><strong>Empty Stomach:</strong> Consume on an empty or light stomach for optimal absorption and effect.</li>\n<li><strong>Stay Hydrated:</strong> Keep water nearby and sip throughout your experience.</li>\n<li><strong>Time Commitment:</strong> Clear your schedule for 4-8 hours with no obligations or responsibilities.</li>\n<li><strong>Do Not Mix:</strong> Avoid combining with alcohol or other substances.</li>\n</ul>\n<h3>Onset &amp; Duration</h3>\n<ul>\n<li><strong>Onset:</strong> 20-60 minutes (varies by metabolism and stomach content)</li>\n<li><strong>Peak Effects:</strong> 2-3 hours after onset</li>\n<li><strong>Duration:</strong> 4-6 hours total experience, with afterglow effects lasting several hours</li>\n<li><strong>Full Integration:</strong> Allow 24 hours for complete return to baseline</li>\n</ul>\n<h3>Best Use Cases</h3>\n<p>Ideal for therapeutic introspection, creative exploration, spiritual experiences, or recreational psychedelic journeys. Best consumed during daytime or early evening in a safe, comfortable setting. The espresso-infused dark chocolate provides a rich, enjoyable flavour that masks any earthy psilocybin taste. Perfect for experienced psychonauts and curious beginners alike when dosed appropriately.</p>\n<p><strong>⚠️ Important Safety Information:</strong> Psilocybin is a powerful psychedelic substance. Do not drive or operate machinery. Not recommended for individuals with personal or family history of psychosis or severe mental health conditions. Consult with a healthcare provider if you have any medical concerns. Keep out of reach of children and pets. Must be 19+ years of age.</p>\n<h2>❓ Frequently Asked Questions</h2>\n<h3>How many mg of psilocybin are in each square of TRIPNOTIK chocolate?</h3>\n<p><strong>A:</strong> Each square contains precisely 80mg of psilocybin, allowing for controlled, customizable dosing. The entire bar contains 5000mg total, giving you complete control over your experience intensity.</p>\n<h3>How long does TRIPNOTIK Psilocybin Dark Chocolate take to work?</h3>\n<p><strong>A:</strong> Effects typically begin within 20-60 minutes of consumption, depending on your metabolism and whether you’ve eaten recently. Peak effects occur 2-3 hours after onset, with the full experience lasting 4-6 hours. Always start with a low dose and wait at least 90 minutes before considering additional consumption.</p>\n<h3>Is TRIPNOTIK suitable for first-time psilocybin users?</h3>\n<p><strong>A:</strong> Yes, when consumed responsibly. First-time users should start with just 1 square (80mg) to assess individual tolerance and sensitivity. The precisely dosed squares make it easy to control your experience. We recommend having an experienced friend present and ensuring you’re in a safe, comfortable environment.</p>\n<h3>What does TRIPNOTIK Psilocybin Dark Chocolate taste like?</h3>\n<p><strong>A:</strong> TRIPNOTIK features rich espresso trance dark milk chocolate that provides a delicious, gourmet flavour experience. The high-quality chocolate effectively masks any earthy psilocybin taste, making consumption enjoyable and pleasant.</p>\n<h3>How should I store my TRIPNOTIK chocolate bar?</h3>\n<p><strong>A:</strong> Store in a cool, dry place away from direct sunlight and heat. Keep sealed in original packaging to maintain freshness and potency. Refrigeration is recommended in warm climates but avoid freezing. Properly stored, your chocolate bar will maintain potency for 6-12 months. Always keep out of reach of children and pets.</p>\n<h3>Does Mohawk Medibles ship TRIPNOTIK Psilocybin chocolate across Canada?</h3>\n<p><strong>A:</strong> Yes! We offer fast, discreet Canada-wide shipping with same-day processing on orders placed before 2 PM EST. All packages arrive in plain, unmarked packaging with no indication of contents, ensuring complete privacy and discretion.</p>\n<h3>Can I microdose with TRIPNOTIK chocolate?</h3>\n<p><strong>A:</strong> Absolutely. Each 80mg square can be further divided for microdosing purposes. A typical microdose is 10-25mg (approximately 1/8 to 1/4 of a square). Microdosing protocols typically involve consuming small amounts every 3-4 days for enhanced creativity, focus, and mood without noticeable psychedelic effects.</p>\n</div>\n</div>",
