        "descriptionHTML": "<div class=\"tab-pane active\" id=\"tab-description\">\n<div class=\"detail-tab-desc detail-content-wrap\">\n<p>**Buy Bubble Gum Hash online in Canada at Mohawk Medibles**, your trusted Indigenous-owned cannabis dispensary. Shop this premium hash at an unbeatable $140/oz deal and enjoy fast Canada-wide shipping with same-day processing. Order now for discreet delivery of authentic, high-quality hash sourced from Tyendinaga Mohawk Territory. Perfect for experienced consumers seeking potent, traditional cannabis concentrates at exceptional value.</p>\n<h2>🧬 Strain Profile</h2>\n<h3>Genetics &amp; Lineage</h3>\n<p>Bubble Gum Hash is crafted from premium Bubble Gum cannabis flower, an iconic indica-dominant hybrid strain originally developed by Indiana Bubble Gum and later perfected by Dutch breeders. This hash preserves the legendary sweet, bubblegum flavour profile that made the original strain famous worldwide, while concentrating its therapeutic effects through traditional hash-making techniques.</p>\n<h3>Dominant Terpenes</h3>\n<ul>\n<li><strong>Caryophyllene:</strong> Provides spicy, peppery notes and potential anti-inflammatory benefits</li>\n<li><strong>Limonene:</strong> Contributes citrus undertones and mood-elevating properties</li>\n<li><strong>Myrcene:</strong> Delivers earthy, herbal aromas with relaxing, sedative effects</li>\n</ul>\n<h3>Cannabinoid Profile</h3>\n<p>As a concentrated hash product, Bubble Gum Hash contains significantly elevated THC levels compared to traditional flower, typically ranging from 40-60% THC. This potent concentration delivers powerful, long-lasting effects ideal for experienced consumers seeking maximum therapeutic or recreational impact.</p>\n<h3>Appearance &amp; Structure</h3>\n<p>This hash displays a classic pressed texture with a dark brown to black exterior and a lighter, more pliable interior. The consistency is malleable when warmed, making it easy to break apart and portion. Quality indicators include a sticky, resinous feel and aromatic fragrance that intensifies when handled.</p>\n<h3>Similar Strains</h3>\n<p>If you enjoy Bubble Gum Hash, consider trying: <strong>Afghan Hash</strong> for traditional earthy profiles, <strong>Lebanese Hash</strong> for smooth, balanced effects, or <strong>Moroccan Hash</strong> for lighter, more cerebral experiences. For flower alternatives, explore <strong>Northern Lights Hash</strong> or <strong>Blueberry Hash</strong> for similar sweet, relaxing characteristics.</p>\n<p>–</p>\n<h2>💡 Usage Guide</h2>\n<h3>Recommended Dosage</h3>\n<ul>\n<li><strong>Beginners:</strong> Hash is highly concentrated – start with a grain-of-rice sized amount (approximately 0.05g) if new to concentrates</li>\n<li><strong>Experienced Users:</strong> 0.1-0.2g per session for balanced effects</li>\n<li><strong>High Tolerance:</strong> 0.3-0.5g per session; adjust based on personal experience</li>\n</ul>\n<h3>Consumption Methods</h3>\n<ul>\n<li><strong>Hot Knifing:</strong> Traditional method using heated knives to vaporize small amounts for immediate effects</li>\n<li><strong>Pipe or Bong:</strong> Crumble hash over cannabis flower or use alone in a mesh screen</li>\n<li><strong>Joint/Spliff:</strong> Roll thin strips inside joints or create hash “snakes” for enhanced potency</li>\n<li><strong>Vaporizing:</strong> Use concentrate-compatible vaporizer at 180-200°C for smooth, flavourful vapour</li>\n</ul>\n<h3>Onset &amp; Duration</h3>\n<ul>\n<li><strong>Onset:</strong> 2-5 minutes when smoked or vaporized</li>\n<li><strong>Peak Effects:</strong> 20-45 minutes after consumption</li>\n<li><strong>Duration:</strong> 3-5 hours, longer than traditional flower due to concentrated cannabinoids</li>\n</ul>\n<h3>Best Use Cases</h3>\n<p>Bubble Gum Hash is ideal for evening relaxation, pain management, and deep stress relief. The potent indica-dominant effects make this perfect for unwinding after long days, promoting restful sleep, or managing chronic discomfort. Best consumed when you have no obligations and can fully enjoy the profound body relaxation and mental calm.</p>\n<p><strong>⚠️ Important:</strong> Hash contains significantly higher THC concentrations than flower (40-60%+). for experienced users – beginners should start with lower doses or those sensitive to THC. Start with minimal amounts and wait 15-20 minutes before consuming more. Do not drive or operate machinery after use.</p>\n<h2>❓ Frequently Asked Questions</h2>\n<h3>What is Bubble Gum Hash and how is it different from regular cannabis flower?</h3>\n<p><strong>A:</strong> Bubble Gum Hash is a concentrated cannabis product made by separating trichomes from Bubble Gum strain flower using ice water extraction or traditional pressing methods. It contains 40-60% THC compared to flower’s 15-25%, delivering significantly more potent effects in smaller amounts. Hash offers longer-lasting effects and requires less product per session.</p>\n<h3>How do I use Bubble Gum Hash?</h3>\n<p><strong>A:</strong> Break off a small piece and add it to your pipe, bong, or vaporizer. You can also crumble it over flower in joints, use the hot knife method, or vaporize it in concentrate-compatible devices. Start with a rice grain-sized amount if you’re new to hash. Always use lower amounts than you would with flower due to increased potency.</p>\n<h3>Is this $140/oz deal good value for hash?</h3>\n<p><strong>A:</strong> Yes! At $140/oz ($5/gram), this represents exceptional value for quality hash. Hash typically costs $8-15/gram at retail, making this deal nearly 50% off regular pricing. Because hash is concentrated, an ounce lasts significantly longer than an ounce of flower, providing even greater value for experienced consumers.</p>\n<h3>What effects can I expect from Bubble Gum Hash?</h3>\n<p><strong>A:</strong> Expect powerful indica-dominant effects including deep body relaxation, mental calm, stress relief, and sedation. Users report feeling euphoric initially, followed by profound physical relaxation. Common uses include pain management, insomnia relief, anxiety reduction, and evening relaxation. Effects are more intense and longer-lasting than flower.</p>\n<h3>How should I store Bubble Gum Hash?</h3>\n<p><strong>A:</strong> Store hash in an airtight container in a cool, dark place away from heat, light, and moisture. Parchment paper or silicone containers work best to prevent sticking. Properly stored hash maintains potency and quality for 1-2 years. Avoid refrigeration as temperature changes can create condensation and degrade quality.</p>\n<h3>Is Bubble Gum Hash suitable for beginners?</h3>\n<p><strong>A:</strong> Hash is generally not recommended for cannabis beginners due to its high THC concentration (40-60%+). If you’re new to cannabis, start with lower-potency flower (15-20% THC) to understand your tolerance. Experienced flower users can try hash by starting with very small amounts and gradually increasing as tolerance develops.</p>\n<h3>Does Mohawk Medibles ship Bubble Gum Hash across Canada?</h3>\n<p><strong>A:</strong> Yes! We offer fast, discreet Canada-wide shipping on all hash products including Bubble Gum Hash. Orders placed before 2 PM EST receive same-day processing. All packages arrive in plain, unmarked packaging with no cannabis references, ensuring complete privacy and discretion for your delivery.</p>\n</div>\n</div>",
