        "descriptionHTML": "<div class=\"tab-pane active\" id=\"tab-description\">\n<div class=\"detail-tab-desc detail-content-wrap\">\n<h2 data-end=\"220\" data-start=\"177\">🍫 <strong data-end=\"218\" data-start=\"182\">Chocolate Hash – $5/Gram Special</strong></h2>\n<p data-end=\"255\" data-start=\"221\"><strong data-end=\"255\" data-start=\"221\">Indica-Dominant • THC: 18%–22%</strong></p>\n<hr/>\n<p data-end=\"910\" data-start=\"680\">Chocolate Hash is built for those who love <strong data-end=\"757\" data-start=\"723\">rich, natural, old-school hash</strong>.<br data-end=\"761\" data-start=\"758\"/><strong data-end=\"776\" data-start=\"761\">Right away,</strong> you’ll notice its deep aroma—earthy, woody, and touched with a sweet cocoa scent inspired by the popular Chocolate Backwoods flavour.</p>\n<p data-end=\"1200\" data-start=\"912\"><strong data-end=\"938\" data-start=\"912\">As you break it apart,</strong> the hash releases even stronger natural notes, giving it that rugged, forest-like Backwoods feel.<br data-end=\"1039\" data-start=\"1036\"/><strong data-end=\"1052\" data-start=\"1039\">Once lit,</strong> the flavour becomes fuller: warm chocolate tones blend with wood and earth, delivering a smooth, steady smoke that stays rich from start to finish.</p>\n<p data-end=\"1514\" data-start=\"1202\"><strong data-end=\"1235\" data-start=\"1202\">Soon after your first exhale,</strong> the Indica-heavy effects begin to settle in. A slow wave of relaxation spreads through the body, easing tension and calming your mind.<br data-end=\"1373\" data-start=\"1370\"/><strong data-end=\"1382\" data-start=\"1373\">Then,</strong> the high deepens into a heavier melt—perfect for users looking to kick back, quiet their thoughts, or settle into a peaceful night.</p>\n<p data-end=\"1636\" data-start=\"1516\"><strong data-end=\"1536\" data-start=\"1516\">With 18–22% THC,</strong> this hash is strong enough for experienced smokers while still offering a smooth and enjoyable hit.</p>\n<hr data-end=\"1641\" data-start=\"1638\"/>\n<h3 data-end=\"1661\" data-start=\"1643\">🔥 <strong data-end=\"1659\" data-start=\"1648\">EFFECTS</strong></h3>\n<ul data-end=\"1756\" data-start=\"1662\">\n<li data-end=\"1682\" data-start=\"1662\">\n<p data-end=\"1682\" data-start=\"1664\">Heavy relaxation</p>\n</li>\n<li data-end=\"1701\" data-start=\"1683\">\n<p data-end=\"1701\" data-start=\"1685\">Calm body melt</p>\n</li>\n<li data-end=\"1719\" data-start=\"1702\">\n<p data-end=\"1719\" data-start=\"1704\">Stress relief</p>\n</li>\n<li data-end=\"1737\" data-start=\"1720\">\n<p data-end=\"1737\" data-start=\"1722\">Mild euphoria</p>\n</li>\n<li data-end=\"1756\" data-start=\"1738\">\n<p data-end=\"1756\" data-start=\"1740\">Evening unwind</p>\n</li>\n</ul>\n<hr data-end=\"1761\" data-start=\"1758\"/>\n<h3 data-end=\"1787\" data-start=\"1763\">🌿 <strong data-end=\"1785\" data-start=\"1768\">MAY HELP WITH</strong></h3>\n<ul data-end=\"1863\" data-start=\"1788\">\n<li data-end=\"1798\" data-start=\"1788\">\n<p data-end=\"1798\" data-start=\"1790\">Stress</p>\n</li>\n<li data-end=\"1811\" data-start=\"1799\">\n<p data-end=\"1811\" data-start=\"1801\">Insomnia</p>\n</li>\n<li data-end=\"1823\" data-start=\"1812\">\n<p data-end=\"1823\" data-start=\"1814\">Anxiety</p>\n</li>\n<li data-end=\"1840\" data-start=\"1824\">\n<p data-end=\"1840\" data-start=\"1826\">Body tension</p>\n</li>\n<li data-end=\"1863\" data-start=\"1841\">\n<p data-end=\"1863\" data-start=\"1843\">Chronic discomfort</p>\n</li>\n</ul>\n<hr data-end=\"1868\" data-start=\"1865\"/>\n<h3 data-end=\"1888\" data-start=\"1870\">🍫 <strong data-end=\"1886\" data-start=\"1875\">FLAVORS</strong></h3>\n<ul data-end=\"1967\" data-start=\"1889\">\n<li data-end=\"1902\" data-start=\"1889\">\n<p data-end=\"1902\" data-start=\"1891\">Chocolate</p>\n</li>\n<li data-end=\"1913\" data-start=\"1903\">\n<p data-end=\"1913\" data-start=\"1905\">Earthy</p>\n</li>\n<li data-end=\"1923\" data-start=\"1914\">\n<p data-end=\"1923\" data-start=\"1916\">Woody</p>\n</li>\n<li data-end=\"1944\" data-start=\"1924\">\n<p data-end=\"1944\" data-start=\"1926\">Slight sweetness</p>\n</li>\n<li data-end=\"1967\" data-start=\"1945\">\n<p data-end=\"1967\" data-start=\"1947\">Natural hash tones</p>\n</li>\n</ul>\n<hr data-end=\"1972\" data-start=\"1969\"/>\n<h3 data-end=\"1992\" data-start=\"1974\">🌬️ <strong data-end=\"1990\" data-start=\"1980\">AROMAS</strong></h3>\n<ul data-end=\"2053\" data-start=\"1993\">\n<li data-end=\"2002\" data-start=\"1993\">\n<p data-end=\"2002\" data-start=\"1995\">Cocoa</p>\n</li>\n<li data-end=\"2019\" data-start=\"2003\">\n<p data-end=\"2019\" data-start=\"2005\">Earthy woods</p>\n</li>\n<li data-end=\"2034\" data-start=\"2020\">\n<p data-end=\"2034\" data-start=\"2022\">Deep spice</p>\n</li>\n<li data-end=\"2053\" data-start=\"2035\">\n<p data-end=\"2053\" data-start=\"2037\">Smoky richness</p>\n</li>\n</ul>\n<hr/>\n<h2>💡 Usage Guide</h2>\n<h3>Recommended Dosage</h3>\n<ul>\n<li><strong>Beginners:</strong> Start with a rice grain-sized piece (approximately 0.025-0.05g). Hash is significantly more potent than flower.</li>\n<li><strong>Experienced Users:</strong> 0.1-0.2g per session, adjusting based on tolerance and desired effects.</li>\n<li><strong>High Tolerance:</strong> Up to 0.3g per session for seasoned concentrate consumers.</li>\n</ul>\n<h3>Consumption Methods</h3>\n<ul>\n<li><strong>Smoking:</strong> Crumble and mix with flower in joints, pipes, or bongs for enhanced potency and traditional experience.</li>\n<li><strong>Vaporizing:</strong> Use hash-compatible vaporizer at 180-210°C for smooth, flavourful vapour with maximum terpene preservation.</li>\n<li><strong>Hot Knives:</strong> Traditional method heating two knives and pressing hash between them for immediate effects.</li>\n<li><strong>Topping Bowls:</strong> Add small pieces atop flower bowls for elevated potency without altering your regular routine.</li>\n<li><strong>Hash Edibles (Advanced):</strong> To make edibles, decarboxylate hash at 110-120°C (230-250°F) for 30-40 minutes to activate THC. Mix into butter or oil-based recipes. Effects take 30-120 minutes and last 6-12 hours. Hash edibles are significantly more potent than flower edibles—start with 1/4 of your normal flower edible dose.</li>\n</ul>\n<h3>Onset &amp; Duration</h3>\n<ul>\n<li><strong>Onset (Smoking/Vaping):</strong> 2-10 minutes</li>\n<li><strong>Onset (Edibles):</strong> 30-120 minutes</li>\n<li><strong>Peak Effects:</strong> 15-45 minutes (inhaled) or 2-4 hours (edibles)</li>\n<li><strong>Duration:</strong> 2-4 hours (inhaled) or 6-12 hours (edibles)</li>\n</ul>\n<p><strong>⚠️ Important:</strong> Hash is significantly more potent than regular flower. Start with minimal amounts and wait to assess effects before consuming more. for experienced users – beginners should start with lower doses or those new to concentrates.</p>\n</div>\n</div>",
