        "descriptionHTML": "<div class=\"tab-pane active\" id=\"tab-description\">\n<div class=\"detail-tab-desc detail-content-wrap\">\n<p>**Buy Nicozy Nicotine Pouches online in Canada at Mohawk Medibles**, your trusted Indigenous-owned dispensary offering smoke-free alternatives. Shop these discreet, tobacco-free nicotine pouches and enjoy fast Canada-wide shipping with same-day processing. Order now for convenient, vapour-free nicotine delivery from Tyendinaga Mohawk Territory—perfect for on-the-go use anywhere, anytime.</p>\n<p>–</p>\n<h2>💡 Usage Guide</h2>\n<h3>Recommended Usage</h3>\n<ul>\n<li><strong>New Users:</strong> Start with one pouch for 15-20 minutes to assess tolerance</li>\n<li><strong>Regular Users:</strong> Use 1-2 pouches per session as needed throughout the day</li>\n<li><strong>Maximum Daily Use:</strong> Follow product packaging guidelines; avoid exceeding recommended daily limits</li>\n</ul>\n<h3>How to Use Nicozy Pouches</h3>\n<ul>\n<li><strong>Step 1:</strong> Remove one pouch from the container</li>\n<li><strong>Step 2:</strong> Place the pouch between your upper lip and gum</li>\n<li><strong>Step 3:</strong> Leave in place for 15-30 minutes to allow nicotine absorption</li>\n<li><strong>Step 4:</strong> Dispose of used pouch responsibly in waste bin (do not swallow)</li>\n</ul>\n<h3>Onset &amp; Duration</h3>\n<ul>\n<li><strong>Onset:</strong> 3-5 minutes for initial nicotine delivery</li>\n<li><strong>Peak Effects:</strong> 10-15 minutes</li>\n<li><strong>Duration:</strong> 20-40 minutes per pouch</li>\n</ul>\n<h3>Best Use Cases</h3>\n<p>Ideal for situations where smoking or vaping isn’t permitted—offices, restaurants, flights, public transit, or indoor spaces. Perfect for users seeking a discreet, mess-free nicotine option without smoke, vapour, or odour. Use anytime you need convenient nicotine delivery without disrupting your surroundings.</p>\n<p><strong>⚠️ Important:</strong> This product contains nicotine, which is highly addictive. Not intended for non-smokers or individuals under 19 years of age. Keep out of reach of children and pets. If you experience nausea, dizziness, or discomfort, remove the pouch immediately.</p>\n<h2>❓ Frequently Asked Questions</h2>\n<h3>What are Nicozy Nicotine Pouches?</h3>\n<p><strong>A:</strong> Nicozy pouches are tobacco-free, smoke-free nicotine products designed for oral use. Each small, discreet pouch delivers nicotine through the gum without requiring smoking, vaping, or spitting. They’re perfect for convenient nicotine delivery anywhere.</p>\n<h3>How much nicotine is in each Nicozy pouch?</h3>\n<p><strong>A:</strong> Nicotine strength varies by product variant. Check the product packaging for specific mg content per pouch. We recommend starting with lower-strength options if you’re new to nicotine pouches or transitioning from cigarettes.</p>\n<h3>Are Nicozy pouches safe to use indoors?</h3>\n<p><strong>A:</strong> Yes! Nicozy pouches produce no smoke, vapour, or odour, making them suitable for use in offices, restaurants, flights, and other indoor environments where smoking and vaping are prohibited. They’re completely discreet and won’t disturb others.</p>\n<h3>Can I swallow the nicotine pouch or the saliva?</h3>\n<p><strong>A:</strong> You can safely swallow the saliva produced while using the pouch, but do not swallow the pouch itself. Always dispose of used pouches in the trash. Swallowing excessive saliva may cause mild stomach discomfort in some users.</p>\n<h3>How long can I keep a Nicozy pouch in my mouth?</h3>\n<p><strong>A:</strong> Most users keep pouches in place for 15-30 minutes. You can remove it earlier if you experience strong effects or discomfort, or keep it slightly longer if desired. Once the tingling sensation fades, the pouch has released most of its nicotine.</p>\n<h3>Does Mohawk Medibles ship Nicozy pouches across Canada?</h3>\n<p><strong>A:</strong> Yes! We offer fast, discreet Canada-wide shipping on all Nicozy products with same-day processing on orders placed before 2 PM EST. All packages arrive in plain, unmarked packaging. You must be 19+ to purchase nicotine products.</p>\n<h3>How should I store Nicozy Nicotine Pouches?</h3>\n<p><strong>A:</strong> Store Nicozy pouches in their original container in a cool, dry place away from direct sunlight and heat. Keep the container sealed to maintain freshness and potency. Always store out of reach of children and pets.</p>\n</div>\n</div>",
