        "shortDescription": "Biscotti LA Mousse Hash brings together dessert-level flavour and deep indica relaxation in one premium, solventless concentrate. To begin with, this indica-dominant hybrid (80% indica / 20% sativa)...",
        "descriptionHTML": "<div class=\"tab-pane active\" id=\"tab-description\">\n<div class=\"detail-tab-desc detail-content-wrap\">\n<p data-end=\"917\" data-start=\"522\"><strong data-end=\"549\" data-start=\"522\">Biscotti LA Mousse Hash</strong> brings together <strong data-end=\"591\" data-start=\"566\">dessert-level flavour</strong> and <strong data-end=\"622\" data-start=\"596\">deep indica relaxation</strong> in one premium, solventless concentrate. To begin with, this indica-dominant hybrid (80% indica / 20% sativa) is crafted from the legendary <strong data-end=\"817\" data-start=\"763\">Gelato #25 × Girl Scout Cookies × South Florida OG</strong> lineage. Because of this elite genetic mix, every session delivers both flavour and full-body calm.</p>\n<p data-end=\"1252\" data-start=\"919\">Right away, the experience starts in the mind 🧠✨. First, a gentle cerebral lift eases stress and quiets racing thoughts. Soon after, laughter comes easily and the mood turns light and upbeat. Then, as the high settles in, a soothing body wave rolls through the muscles, helping you fully relax without feeling overwhelming or heavy.</p>\n<p data-end=\"1507\" data-start=\"1254\">Meanwhile, the flavour steals the show 🍪🔥. Each hit opens with <strong data-end=\"1349\" data-start=\"1319\">sweet, sugary cookie notes</strong>, followed by <strong data-end=\"1381\" data-start=\"1363\">nutty richness</strong> and a <strong data-end=\"1410\" data-start=\"1388\">warm, spicy finish</strong>. Underneath it all, earthy herbal tones keep the smoke smooth and balanced from start to finish.</p>\n<p data-end=\"1788\" data-start=\"1509\">Because this is <strong data-end=\"1543\" data-start=\"1525\">LA Mousse Hash</strong>, the texture stays <strong data-end=\"1601\" data-start=\"1563\">light, airy, and easy to work with</strong>. As a result, it crumbles effortlessly, melts cleanly, and delivers consistent potency every time. Whether you sprinkle it, roll it, or press it, Biscotti LA Mousse performs beautifully.</p>\n<hr data-end=\"1793\" data-start=\"1790\"/>\n<h3 data-end=\"1822\" data-start=\"1795\">✨ Effects You’ll Notice</h3>\n<ul data-end=\"1937\" data-start=\"1823\">\n<li data-end=\"1850\" data-start=\"1823\">\n<p data-end=\"1850\" data-start=\"1825\">😌 Deep body relaxation</p>\n</li>\n<li data-end=\"1878\" data-start=\"1851\">\n<p data-end=\"1878\" data-start=\"1853\">😄 Giggly, happy uplift</p>\n</li>\n<li data-end=\"1907\" data-start=\"1879\">\n<p data-end=\"1907\" data-start=\"1881\">🛋️ Calm, stoney comfort</p>\n</li>\n<li data-end=\"1937\" data-start=\"1908\">\n<p data-end=\"1937\" data-start=\"1910\">🌙 Perfect evening unwind</p>\n</li>\n</ul>\n<hr data-end=\"1942\" data-start=\"1939\"/>\n<h3 data-end=\"1970\" data-start=\"1944\">🩺 Commonly Chosen For</h3>\n<ul data-end=\"2063\" data-start=\"1971\">\n<li data-end=\"1991\" data-start=\"1971\">\n<p data-end=\"1991\" data-start=\"1973\">Stress &amp; anxiety</p>\n</li>\n<li data-end=\"2008\" data-start=\"1992\">\n<p data-end=\"2008\" data-start=\"1994\">Chronic pain</p>\n</li>\n<li data-end=\"2037\" data-start=\"2009\">\n<p data-end=\"2037\" data-start=\"2011\">Depression &amp; mood swings</p>\n</li>\n<li data-end=\"2063\" data-start=\"2038\">\n<p data-end=\"2063\" data-start=\"2040\">End-of-day relaxation</p>\n</li>\n</ul>\n<hr data-end=\"2068\" data-start=\"2065\"/>\n<h3 data-end=\"2090\" data-start=\"2070\">🍬 Flavour Notes</h3>\n<ul data-end=\"2180\" data-start=\"2091\">\n<li data-end=\"2118\" data-start=\"2091\">\n<p data-end=\"2118\" data-start=\"2093\">Sugary cookie sweetness</p>\n</li>\n<li data-end=\"2142\" data-start=\"2119\">\n<p data-end=\"2142\" data-start=\"2121\">Nutty dessert tones</p>\n</li>\n<li data-end=\"2157\" data-start=\"2143\">\n<p data-end=\"2157\" data-start=\"2145\">Warm spice</p>\n</li>\n<li data-end=\"2180\" data-start=\"2158\">\n<p data-end=\"2180\" data-start=\"2160\">Light herbal earth</p>\n</li>\n</ul>\n<hr data-end=\"2185\" data-start=\"2182\"/>\n<h3 data-end=\"2208\" data-start=\"2187\">🌬️ Aroma Profile</h3>\n<ul data-end=\"2273\" data-start=\"2209\">\n<li data-end=\"2228\" data-start=\"2209\">\n<p data-end=\"2228\" data-start=\"2211\">Earthy &amp; herbal</p>\n</li>\n<li data-end=\"2251\" data-start=\"2229\">\n<p data-end=\"2251\" data-start=\"2231\">Sweet cookie dough</p>\n</li>\n<li data-end=\"2273\" data-start=\"2252\">\n<p data-end=\"2273\" data-start=\"2254\">Fruity undertones</p>\n</li>\n</ul>\n<hr data-end=\"2278\" data-start=\"2275\"/>\n<h3 data-end=\"2325\" data-start=\"2280\">💎 Why Biscotti LA Mousse Hash Stands Out</h3>\n<ul data-end=\"2523\" data-start=\"2326\">\n<li data-end=\"2367\" data-start=\"2326\">\n<p data-end=\"2367\" data-start=\"2328\">Solventless <strong data-end=\"2367\" data-start=\"2340\">dry sift LA Mousse hash</strong></p>\n</li>\n<li data-end=\"2409\" data-start=\"2368\">\n<p data-end=\"2409\" data-start=\"2370\">Light, aerated <strong data-end=\"2409\" data-start=\"2385\">French Touch texture</strong></p>\n</li>\n<li data-end=\"2441\" data-start=\"2410\">\n<p data-end=\"2441\" data-start=\"2412\">Dessert-grade flavour profile</p>\n</li>\n<li data-end=\"2481\" data-start=\"2442\">\n<p data-end=\"2481\" data-start=\"2444\">Strong yet smooth <strong data-end=\"2481\" data-start=\"2462\">25% THC potency</strong></p>\n</li>\n<li data-end=\"2523\" data-start=\"2482\">\n<p data-end=\"2523\" data-start=\"2484\">Ideal for relaxation without couch-lock</p>\n</li>\n</ul>\n<hr/>\n<h2>💡 Usage Guide</h2>\n<h3>Recommended Dosage</h3>\n<ul>\n<li><strong>Beginners:</strong> Start with a rice grain-sized piece (approximately 0.025-0.05g). Hash is significantly more potent than flower.</li>\n<li><strong>Experienced Users:</strong> 0.1-0.2g per session, adjusting based on tolerance and desired effects.</li>\n<li><strong>High Tolerance:</strong> Up to 0.3g per session for seasoned concentrate consumers.</li>\n</ul>\n<h3>Consumption Methods</h3>\n<ul>\n<li><strong>Smoking:</strong> Crumble and mix with flower in joints, pipes, or bongs for enhanced potency and traditional experience.</li>\n<li><strong>Vaporizing:</strong> Use hash-compatible vaporizer at 180-210°C for smooth, flavourful vapour with maximum terpene preservation.</li>\n<li><strong>Hot Knives:</strong> Traditional method heating two knives and pressing hash between them for immediate effects.</li>\n<li><strong>Topping Bowls:</strong> Add small pieces atop flower bowls for elevated potency without altering your regular routine.</li>\n<li><strong>Hash Edibles (Advanced):</strong> To make edibles, decarboxylate hash at 110-120°C (230-250°F) for 30-40 minutes to activate THC. Mix into butter or oil-based recipes. Effects take 30-120 minutes and last 6-12 hours. Hash edibles are significantly more potent than flower edibles—start with 1/4 of your normal flower edible dose.</li>\n</ul>\n<h3>Onset &amp; Duration</h3>\n<ul>\n<li><strong>Onset (Smoking/Vaping):</strong> 2-10 minutes</li>\n<li><strong>Onset (Edibles):</strong> 30-120 minutes</li>\n<li><strong>Peak Effects:</strong> 15-45 minutes (inhaled) or 2-4 hours (edibles)</li>\n<li><strong>Duration:</strong> 2-4 hours (inhaled) or 6-12 hours (edibles)</li>\n</ul>\n<p><strong>⚠️ Important:</strong> Hash is significantly more potent than regular flower. Start with minimal amounts and wait to assess effects before consuming more. for experienced users – beginners should start with lower doses or those new to concentrates.</p>\n</div>\n</div>",
