        "descriptionHTML": "<div class=\"tab-pane active\" id=\"tab-description\">\n<div class=\"detail-tab-desc detail-content-wrap\">\n<p>**Buy Euphoria Psychedelics Salted Caramel Hot Cocoa online in Canada at Mohawk Medibles**, your trusted Indigenous-owned cannabis dispensary. Shop this premium cannabis-infused hot chocolate and enjoy fast Canada-wide shipping with same-day processing. Order now for discreet delivery of this delicious, cozy treat that takes your hot cocoa experience to a whole new level. Perfect for relaxing evenings and cold Canadian nights.</p>\n<p>–</p>\n<h2>💡 Usage Guide</h2>\n<h3>Recommended Dosage</h3>\n<ul>\n<li><strong>Beginners:</strong> Start with half a packet (check THC content on package) and wait 60-90 minutes before consuming more</li>\n<li><strong>Experienced Users:</strong> One full packet per serving, adjusting based on your tolerance and desired effects</li>\n<li><strong>High Tolerance:</strong> One to two packets, but always start conservatively with edibles</li>\n</ul>\n<h3>Preparation Instructions</h3>\n<ul>\n<li><strong>Hot Preparation:</strong> Empty packet into your favourite mug, add 8-10 oz of hot water or milk, stir thoroughly until fully dissolved</li>\n<li><strong>Enhanced Experience:</strong> Top with whipped cream, extra marshmallows, or a cinnamon stick for added indulgence</li>\n<li><strong>Milk vs Water:</strong> Using whole milk or oat milk enhances creaminess and can improve cannabinoid absorption</li>\n</ul>\n<h3>Onset &amp; Duration</h3>\n<ul>\n<li><strong>Onset:</strong> 45-90 minutes (faster on empty stomach, slower after meals)</li>\n<li><strong>Peak Effects:</strong> 2-3 hours after consumption</li>\n<li><strong>Duration:</strong> 4-6 hours total experience</li>\n</ul>\n<h3>Best Use Cases</h3>\n<p>Perfect for cozy evenings at home, movie nights, or winding down after a long day. The warm, comforting nature of hot cocoa combined with cannabis creates an ideal relaxation experience. Best enjoyed 1-2 hours before your desired peak effects, making it perfect for evening use. Not recommended before work, driving, or operating machinery.</p>\n<p><strong>⚠️ Important:</strong> Edibles take longer to take effect than smoking or vaping. Start low and go slow—wait at least 2 hours before consuming more. Effects are stronger and longer-lasting than inhaled cannabis.</p>\n<h2>❓ Frequently Asked Questions</h2>\n<h3>How much THC is in Euphoria Salted Caramel Hot Cocoa?</h3>\n<p><strong>A:</strong> Each single-serving packet contains a precisely measured dose of THC (check package label for exact mg). This ensures consistent, predictable effects with every cup you make.</p>\n<h3>How long does Euphoria Hot Cocoa take to work?</h3>\n<p><strong>A:</strong> As a cannabis-infused beverage, effects typically begin within 45-90 minutes of consumption. The warm liquid may lead to slightly faster absorption than solid edibles. Peak effects occur 2-3 hours after drinking, with total duration of 4-6 hours.</p>\n<h3>Can I make this with milk instead of water?</h3>\n<p><strong>A:</strong> Yes! Using milk (dairy or plant-based) creates a richer, creamier hot chocolate and may enhance cannabinoid absorption due to the fat content. Whole milk, oat milk, or coconut milk work particularly well.</p>\n<h3>Is Euphoria Hot Cocoa suitable for beginners?</h3>\n<p><strong>A:</strong> If you’re new to cannabis edibles, start with half a packet and wait at least 2 hours before consuming more. The delicious taste can be tempting, but remember that edibles are potent and long-lasting. Always start low and go slow.</p>\n<h3>How should I store Euphoria Hot Cocoa packets?</h3>\n<p><strong>A:</strong> Store packets in a cool, dry place away from direct sunlight and heat. Keep in original packaging to maintain freshness and potency. Always store securely out of reach of children and pets. Properly stored, packets remain fresh for 6-12 months.</p>\n<h3>Does Mohawk Medibles ship Euphoria Hot Cocoa across Canada?</h3>\n<p><strong>A:</strong> Yes! We offer fast, discreet Canada-wide shipping with same-day processing on orders placed before 2 PM EST. All packages arrive in plain, unmarked packaging to ensure your privacy.</p>\n<h3>Can I drink multiple cups or save half for later?</h3>\n<p><strong>A:</strong> You can prepare half a packet if you want a lower dose—simply save the remaining powder in a sealed container or bag. However, we don’t recommend drinking multiple full servings in one session, especially if you’re new to edibles. Wait at least 2-3 hours to assess effects before considering additional consumption.</p>\n</div>\n</div>",
