        "descriptionHTML": "<div class=\"tab-pane active\" id=\"tab-description\">\n<div class=\"detail-tab-desc detail-content-wrap\">\n<p>**Buy Pineapple Express Meds Live Resin Cartridge online in Canada at Mohawk Medibles**, your trusted Indigenous-owned cannabis dispensary. Shop this premium 100% live resin vape cartridge with no additives or cutting agents, and enjoy fast Canada-wide shipping with same-day processing. Order now for discreet delivery of authentic, full-spectrum cannabis concentrates sourced from quality producers. Experience pure, terpene-rich vapour with every draw from this 510-thread compatible cartridge.</p>\n<p>–</p>\n<h2>💡 Usage Guide</h2>\n<h3>Recommended Dosage</h3>\n<ul>\n<li><strong>Beginners:</strong> Start with 1-2 short inhalations (1-2 seconds each) and wait 10-15 minutes to assess effects</li>\n<li><strong>Experienced Users:</strong> 2-4 moderate inhalations per session</li>\n<li><strong>High Tolerance:</strong> Adjust based on personal needs; live resin is more potent than distillate cartridges</li>\n</ul>\n<h3>How to Use</h3>\n<ul>\n<li><strong>Battery Setup:</strong> Attach to any standard 510-thread battery (not included)</li>\n<li><strong>Temperature:</strong> Use low to medium voltage settings (2.4-3.2V) to preserve terpene flavour</li>\n<li><strong>Inhalation:</strong> Take slow, steady draws for 2-3 seconds; avoid rapid or forceful pulling</li>\n<li><strong>Priming:</strong> Take 1-2 primer puffs without inhaling when first using to activate the coil</li>\n</ul>\n<h3>Onset &amp; Duration</h3>\n<ul>\n<li><strong>Onset:</strong> 1-5 minutes</li>\n<li><strong>Peak Effects:</strong> 15-30 minutes</li>\n<li><strong>Duration:</strong> 1-3 hours depending on dosage and tolerance</li>\n</ul>\n<h3>Best Use Cases</h3>\n<p>Ideal for on-the-go convenience and discreet consumption. Perfect for users seeking full-spectrum effects with authentic strain flavour profiles. The live resin extraction preserves natural terpenes for superior taste and entourage effects compared to standard distillate cartridges.</p>\n<p><strong>⚠️ Storage Tip:</strong> Store upright in a cool, dark place. Avoid extreme temperatures which can affect oil viscosity and flavour quality.</p>\n<h2>❓ Frequently Asked Questions</h2>\n<h3>What makes live resin cartridges different from regular vape cartridges?</h3>\n<p><strong>A:</strong> Live resin is extracted from fresh-frozen cannabis plants, preserving the full terpene profile and natural flavours. Unlike distillate cartridges that use reintroduced terpenes, Pineapple Express Meds Live Resin contains the plant’s original terpenes for authentic taste and enhanced entourage effects. This results in a more flavourful, aromatic, and potentially more effective experience.</p>\n<h3>Is the Pineapple Express Meds cartridge compatible with my battery?</h3>\n<p><strong>A:</strong> Yes! This cartridge features a universal 510-thread connection, compatible with virtually all standard vape pen batteries. For best results, use a variable voltage battery set between 2.4-3.2V to preserve the delicate terpenes and prevent burnt taste.</p>\n<h3>Does this cartridge contain any additives or cutting agents?</h3>\n<p><strong>A:</strong> Absolutely not. Pineapple Express Meds Live Resin Cartridges contain 100% pure live resin with no VG, PG, MCT oil, vitamin E acetate, synthetic terpenes, or any other additives. What you get is pure, full-spectrum cannabis oil in its most natural form.</p>\n<h3>How should I store my live resin cartridge?</h3>\n<p><strong>A:</strong> Store your cartridge upright in a cool, dark place away from direct sunlight and heat sources. Avoid leaving it in hot cars or cold environments. Keep the mouthpiece covered when not in use to prevent clogging. Proper storage maintains oil viscosity, flavour quality, and potency for the life of the cartridge.</p>\n<h3>How many uses can I get from a 1ml cartridge?</h3>\n<p><strong>A:</strong> A 1ml cartridge typically provides 200-400 inhalations depending on draw length and frequency. For moderate users taking 2-4 draws per session, this translates to approximately 50-100 sessions. Actual usage varies based on individual consumption habits and tolerance levels.</p>\n<h3>Does Mohawk Medibles ship vape cartridges across Canada?</h3>\n<p><strong>A:</strong> Yes! We offer fast, discreet Canada-wide shipping on all vape products including the Pineapple Express Meds Live Resin Cartridge. Orders are processed the same day when placed before 2 PM EST and shipped in plain, unmarked packaging to ensure privacy and product protection during transit.</p>\n<h3>Why does my cartridge sometimes clog or leak?</h3>\n<p><strong>A:</strong> Live resin has a thicker consistency than distillate. Clogs can occur in cold temperatures—gently warm the cartridge in your hands before use. To prevent leaking, always store upright and avoid over-tightening onto your battery. If clogging occurs, try taking a few primer puffs or briefly warming the cartridge. Never store horizontally for extended periods.</p>\n</div>\n</div>",
