        "descriptionHTML": "<div class=\"tab-pane active\" id=\"tab-description\">\n<div class=\"detail-tab-desc detail-content-wrap\">\n<p>**Buy authentic BACKWOODS Cigars online in Canada at Mohawk Medibles**, your trusted Indigenous-owned cannabis accessory retailer. Shop these legendary, all-natural tobacco leaf cigars—perfect for rolling enthusiasts—and enjoy fast Canada-wide shipping with same-day processing. Order now for discreet delivery from Tyendinaga Mohawk Territory. Whether you’re looking for the classic rustic flavour or rare varieties, we keep BACKWOODS in stock year-round when others can’t.</p>\n<p>–</p>\n<h2>💡 Usage Guide</h2>\n<h3>How to Use BACKWOODS Cigars</h3>\n<ul>\n<li><strong>Unrolling:</strong> Carefully unwrap the natural tobacco leaf by gently unrolling from the sealed end. The leaf is delicate, so work slowly to avoid tearing.</li>\n<li><strong>Filling:</strong> Remove original tobacco if desired. Fill with your preferred dry herb material, distributing evenly along the leaf.</li>\n<li><strong>Rolling:</strong> Roll the leaf back into shape, tucking and sealing with the natural adhesive along the edge. The rustic, uneven shape is part of the authentic BACKWOODS experience.</li>\n<li><strong>Sealing:</strong> Lightly moisten the edge to activate the natural leaf seal. Allow 30-60 seconds to set before lighting.</li>\n</ul>\n<h3>Tips for Best Results</h3>\n<ul>\n<li><strong>Moisture Control:</strong> If cigars feel dry, place in a humidity-controlled container for 24 hours before use</li>\n<li><strong>Practice:</strong> BACKWOODS have a learning curve—your first few rolls may be imperfect, and that’s normal</li>\n<li><strong>Slow Burn:</strong> These natural leaf wraps burn slower than papers, providing a longer session</li>\n</ul>\n<h3>Best Use Cases</h3>\n<p>Ideal for experienced rollers who appreciate the rich, rustic tobacco flavour and slow-burning qualities of natural leaf wraps. Perfect for social sessions, outdoor activities, or any time you want a premium, authentic rolling experience. The larger size makes BACKWOODS perfect for group sharing.</p>\n<h2>❓ Frequently Asked Questions</h2>\n<h3>Are BACKWOODS Cigars legal to buy in Canada?</h3>\n<p><strong>A:</strong> Yes, BACKWOODS tobacco cigars are legal tobacco products available for purchase across Canada. You must be of legal smoking age in your province (18 or 19+) to order. Mohawk Medibles ships these accessories Canada-wide with fast, discreet delivery.</p>\n<h3>Why are BACKWOODS so hard to find in Canada?</h3>\n<p><strong>A:</strong> BACKWOODS have limited distribution in Canada and often sell out quickly due to high demand. At Mohawk Medibles, we maintain consistent stock of authentic BACKWOODS cigars, including rare flavours that are difficult to find elsewhere. We source directly to ensure availability year-round.</p>\n<h3>Are these authentic BACKWOODS or imitations?</h3>\n<p><strong>A:</strong> We sell only 100% authentic BACKWOODS Cigars, never imitations or knockoffs. Each cigar features the genuine all-natural Connecticut Broadleaf tobacco wrapper that BACKWOODS is famous for, with that distinctive rustic, uneven appearance and rich flavour.</p>\n<h3>How should I store BACKWOODS Cigars?</h3>\n<p><strong>A:</strong> Store BACKWOODS in their original foil pouch in a cool, dry place away from direct sunlight. For optimal freshness, keep them in an airtight container or humidor at 65-70% humidity. Properly stored cigars maintain their quality for several months. Avoid refrigeration, as this can dry out the natural tobacco leaf.</p>\n<h3>Are BACKWOODS difficult to roll for beginners?</h3>\n<p><strong>A:</strong> BACKWOODS have a steeper learning curve than rolling papers due to the natural, uneven tobacco leaf. Beginners should expect their first few attempts to be imperfect. The leaf is thicker and less forgiving than papers, but with practice, most users master the technique. Many enthusiasts prefer BACKWOODS specifically for the authentic, rustic rolling experience.</p>\n<h3>What flavours of BACKWOODS does Mohawk Medibles carry?</h3>\n<p><strong>A:</strong> We stock a rotating selection of BACKWOODS flavours based on availability, including classic Original, Sweet Aromatic, Honey, and other varieties when available. Check our current product listing for available flavours, as rare varieties sell out quickly. We restock regularly to maintain the best selection in Canada.</p>\n<h3>Does Mohawk Medibles ship BACKWOODS across Canada?</h3>\n<p><strong>A:</strong> Yes! We offer fast Canada-wide shipping on all BACKWOODS Cigars with same-day processing on orders placed before 2 PM EST. All packages are shipped in plain, discreet packaging with no indication of contents. Tracking information is provided for all orders.</p>\n</div>\n</div>",
