        "descriptionHTML": "<div class=\"tab-pane active\" id=\"tab-description\">\n<div class=\"detail-tab-desc detail-content-wrap\">\n<p>**Buy Don Cristo Salt Nicotine Vape online in Canada at Mohawk Medibles**, your trusted Indigenous-owned cannabis dispensary. Shop this premium rechargeable vape device featuring 10,000 puffs of smooth, satisfying vapour and enjoy fast Canada-wide shipping with same-day processing. Order now for discreet delivery and experience the convenience of a high-performance vape with dual mesh coil technology and LCD display. Perfect for on-the-go use with 2% nicotine strength.</p>\n<p>–</p>\n<h2>💡 Usage Guide</h2>\n<h3>How to Use Your Don Cristo Vape</h3>\n<ul>\n<li><strong>First Use:</strong> Remove device from packaging and remove any protective seals. The device is pre-filled and ready to use immediately.</li>\n<li><strong>Activation:</strong> Simply inhale from the mouthpiece to activate – no buttons required. The LCD display will show your puff count and battery level.</li>\n<li><strong>Charging:</strong> When battery runs low, connect to USB-C charger (not included). Full charge typically takes 45-60 minutes.</li>\n<li><strong>Storage:</strong> Keep device upright when not in use to prevent leaking. Store in a cool, dry place away from direct sunlight.</li>\n</ul>\n<h3>Recommended Usage</h3>\n<ul>\n<li><strong>New Users:</strong> Start with 1-2 short puffs and wait 5 minutes to assess effects before continuing.</li>\n<li><strong>Experienced Users:</strong> Use as needed throughout the day. Monitor LCD display to track usage.</li>\n<li><strong>Maintenance:</strong> Keep mouthpiece clean and wipe device exterior regularly with dry cloth.</li>\n</ul>\n<h3>Onset &amp; Duration</h3>\n<ul>\n<li><strong>Onset:</strong> Immediate to 2 minutes</li>\n<li><strong>Peak Effects:</strong> 5-10 minutes</li>\n<li><strong>Duration:</strong> 15-30 minutes per session</li>\n</ul>\n<h3>Best Use Cases</h3>\n<p>Ideal for discreet, convenient vaping throughout the day. Perfect for users transitioning from traditional cigarettes or seeking a portable, mess-free alternative. The 10,000 puff capacity ensures long-lasting use without constant replacements, while the rechargeable design provides excellent value.</p>\n<p><strong>⚠️ Important:</strong> This product contains nicotine. Nicotine is an addictive substance. Not for use by non-smokers, minors, pregnant or breastfeeding women, or individuals with heart conditions. Keep out of reach of children and pets.</p>\n<h2>❓ Frequently Asked Questions</h2>\n<h3>How many puffs does the Don Cristo vape provide?</h3>\n<p><strong>A:</strong> The Don Cristo Salt Nicotine Vape delivers approximately 10,000 puffs from its 20mL e-liquid capacity. Actual puff count may vary based on individual usage patterns and puff duration. The built-in LCD display tracks your usage in real-time.</p>\n<h3>What nicotine strength is the Don Cristo vape?</h3>\n<p><strong>A:</strong> This device contains 2% (20mg/mL) salt nicotine, providing a smooth throat hit with satisfying nicotine delivery. Salt nicotine absorbs more quickly than traditional freebase nicotine, making it ideal for users seeking efficient nicotine satisfaction.</p>\n<h3>Is the Don Cristo vape rechargeable?</h3>\n<p><strong>A:</strong> Yes, the Don Cristo features a rechargeable battery with USB-C charging capability. Simply connect to any USB-C cable (not included) when the battery indicator shows low power. The device is designed to last through the entire 10,000 puffs with periodic recharging.</p>\n<h3>What makes the dual mesh coil special?</h3>\n<p><strong>A:</strong> The dual mesh coil technology provides superior vapour production, enhanced flavour delivery, and more consistent performance compared to standard single coils. This results in smoother draws and better e-liquid utilization throughout the device’s lifespan.</p>\n<h3>Does Mohawk Medibles ship the Don Cristo vape across Canada?</h3>\n<p><strong>A:</strong> Yes! We offer fast, discreet Canada-wide shipping with same-day processing on orders placed before 2 PM EST. All vape products are shipped in plain, unmarked packaging to ensure privacy. Please note: You must be of legal age in your province to purchase nicotine products.</p>\n<h3>How should I store my Don Cristo vape?</h3>\n<p><strong>A:</strong> Store your device upright in a cool, dry place away from direct sunlight and extreme temperatures. Avoid leaving in hot vehicles or freezing conditions, as this can affect e-liquid consistency and battery performance. Keep away from children and pets at all times.</p>\n<h3>What do I do when the vape is finished?</h3>\n<p><strong>A:</strong> When you’ve reached the 10,000 puff limit or notice significantly reduced vapour production and flavour, the device is depleted. Dispose of responsibly according to your local electronic waste regulations, as the device contains a lithium battery. Many communities offer e-waste recycling programmes.</p>\n</div>\n</div>",
