        "descriptionHTML": "<div class=\"tab-pane active\" id=\"tab-description\">\n<div class=\"detail-tab-desc detail-content-wrap\">\n<p data-end=\"867\" data-start=\"502\"><strong data-end=\"534\" data-start=\"502\">Styrofoam Cup LA Mousse Hash</strong>, also known as <strong data-end=\"557\" data-start=\"550\">MSG</strong>, blends <strong data-end=\"582\" data-start=\"566\">bold flavour</strong>, <strong data-end=\"602\" data-start=\"584\">strong potency</strong>, and <strong data-end=\"644\" data-start=\"608\">premium California craftsmanship</strong> into one smooth concentrate. To begin with, this <strong data-end=\"746\" data-start=\"694\">indica-dominant hybrid (70% indica / 30% sativa)</strong> comes from the powerful cross of <strong data-end=\"804\" data-start=\"780\">Sunset Sherbet × GMO</strong>, a lineage famous for rich terpenes and heavy-hitting effects.</p>\n<p data-end=\"1249\" data-start=\"869\">Right from the first pull, the experience opens with a motivating mental lift 🧠⚡. At first, mood improves, stress fades, and focus sharpens slightly. Soon after, that initial energy gives way to a soothing body calm, spreading steadily through the limbs. Because of this transition, Styrofoam Cup works perfectly for easing into the evening without feeling rushed or overwhelmed.</p>\n<p data-end=\"1560\" data-start=\"1251\">As the session deepens, the indica side takes over 😌🛋️. Muscles loosen, tension melts away, and the body settles into a deeply relaxed state. At higher doses, sedation becomes more noticeable, making this hash especially effective for nighttime use, pain management, or full mental shutdown after long days.</p>\n<p data-end=\"1861\" data-start=\"1562\">Meanwhile, the flavour profile remains bold and complex 🧀🍋. Sweet, sugary notes lead the way, followed by citrus brightness and a distinct herbal-cheese funk from its GMO genetics. Underneath, earthy and peppery tones add depth, creating a smooth, lingering finish that keeps every hit satisfying.</p>\n<p data-end=\"2082\" data-start=\"1863\">Because this is <strong data-end=\"1897\" data-start=\"1879\">LA Mousse Hash</strong>, the texture stays <strong data-end=\"1947\" data-start=\"1917\">light, fluffy, and aerated</strong>. As a result, it’s easy to handle, melts cleanly, and delivers consistent flavour whether sprinkled into flower or enjoyed on its own.</p>\n<hr data-end=\"2087\" data-start=\"2084\"/>\n<h3 data-end=\"2114\" data-start=\"2089\">✨ Effects You’ll Feel</h3>\n<ul data-end=\"2234\" data-start=\"2115\">\n<li data-end=\"2137\" data-start=\"2115\">\n<p data-end=\"2137\" data-start=\"2117\">😌 Deep relaxation</p>\n</li>\n<li data-end=\"2163\" data-start=\"2138\">\n<p data-end=\"2163\" data-start=\"2140\">⚡ Initial mental lift</p>\n</li>\n<li data-end=\"2187\" data-start=\"2164\">\n<p data-end=\"2187\" data-start=\"2166\">🛋️ Heavy body calm</p>\n</li>\n<li data-end=\"2211\" data-start=\"2188\">\n<p data-end=\"2211\" data-start=\"2190\">😊 Mood enhancement</p>\n</li>\n<li data-end=\"2234\" data-start=\"2212\">\n<p data-end=\"2234\" data-start=\"2214\">🌙 Sedative finish</p>\n</li>\n</ul>\n<hr data-end=\"2239\" data-start=\"2236\"/>\n<h3 data-end=\"2267\" data-start=\"2241\">🩺 Commonly Chosen For</h3>\n<ul data-end=\"2361\" data-start=\"2268\">\n<li data-end=\"2288\" data-start=\"2268\">\n<p data-end=\"2288\" data-start=\"2270\">Stress &amp; anxiety</p>\n</li>\n<li data-end=\"2305\" data-start=\"2289\">\n<p data-end=\"2305\" data-start=\"2291\">Chronic pain</p>\n</li>\n<li data-end=\"2320\" data-start=\"2306\">\n<p data-end=\"2320\" data-start=\"2308\">Depression</p>\n</li>\n<li data-end=\"2339\" data-start=\"2321\">\n<p data-end=\"2339\" data-start=\"2323\">Muscle tension</p>\n</li>\n<li data-end=\"2361\" data-start=\"2340\">\n<p data-end=\"2361\" data-start=\"2342\">Evening wind-down</p>\n</li>\n</ul>\n<hr data-end=\"2366\" data-start=\"2363\"/>\n<h3 data-end=\"2388\" data-start=\"2368\">🍬 Flavour Notes</h3>\n<ul data-end=\"2453\" data-start=\"2389\">\n<li data-end=\"2407\" data-start=\"2389\">\n<p data-end=\"2407\" data-start=\"2391\">Sweet &amp; sugary</p>\n</li>\n<li data-end=\"2418\" data-start=\"2408\">\n<p data-end=\"2418\" data-start=\"2410\">Citrus</p>\n</li>\n<li data-end=\"2436\" data-start=\"2419\">\n<p data-end=\"2436\" data-start=\"2421\">Herbal cheese</p>\n</li>\n<li data-end=\"2453\" data-start=\"2437\">\n<p data-end=\"2453\" data-start=\"2439\">Earthy spice</p>\n</li>\n</ul>\n<hr data-end=\"2458\" data-start=\"2455\"/>\n<h3 data-end=\"2481\" data-start=\"2460\">🌬️ Aroma Profile</h3>\n<ul data-end=\"2533\" data-start=\"2482\">\n<li data-end=\"2493\" data-start=\"2482\">\n<p data-end=\"2493\" data-start=\"2484\">Peppery</p>\n</li>\n<li data-end=\"2504\" data-start=\"2494\">\n<p data-end=\"2504\" data-start=\"2496\">Earthy</p>\n</li>\n<li data-end=\"2516\" data-start=\"2505\">\n<p data-end=\"2516\" data-start=\"2507\">Pungent</p>\n</li>\n<li data-end=\"2533\" data-start=\"2517\">\n<p data-end=\"2533\" data-start=\"2519\">Kush-forward</p>\n</li>\n</ul>\n<hr data-end=\"2538\" data-start=\"2535\"/>\n<h3 data-end=\"2590\" data-start=\"2540\">💎 Why Styrofoam Cup LA Mousse Hash Stands Out</h3>\n<ul data-end=\"2770\" data-start=\"2591\">\n<li data-end=\"2615\" data-start=\"2591\">\n<p data-end=\"2615\" data-start=\"2593\"><strong data-end=\"2615\" data-start=\"2593\">24–26% THC potency</strong></p>\n</li>\n<li data-end=\"2650\" data-start=\"2616\">\n<p data-end=\"2650\" data-start=\"2618\">Premium <strong data-end=\"2650\" data-start=\"2626\">solventless dry sift</strong></p>\n</li>\n<li data-end=\"2692\" data-start=\"2651\">\n<p data-end=\"2692\" data-start=\"2653\">Light, aerated <strong data-end=\"2692\" data-start=\"2668\">French Touch texture</strong></p>\n</li>\n<li data-end=\"2726\" data-start=\"2693\">\n<p data-end=\"2726\" data-start=\"2695\">GMO dessert-gas terpene profile</p>\n</li>\n<li data-end=\"2770\" data-start=\"2727\">\n<p data-end=\"2770\" data-start=\"2729\">Ideal for stress relief and nighttime use</p>\n</li>\n</ul>\n<hr/>\n<h2>💡 Usage Guide</h2>\n<h3>Recommended Dosage</h3>\n<ul>\n<li><strong>Beginners:</strong> Start with a rice grain-sized piece (approximately 0.025-0.05g). Hash is significantly more potent than flower.</li>\n<li><strong>Experienced Users:</strong> 0.1-0.2g per session, adjusting based on tolerance and desired effects.</li>\n<li><strong>High Tolerance:</strong> Up to 0.3g per session for seasoned concentrate consumers.</li>\n</ul>\n<h3>Consumption Methods</h3>\n<ul>\n<li><strong>Smoking:</strong> Crumble and mix with flower in joints, pipes, or bongs for enhanced potency and traditional experience.</li>\n<li><strong>Vaporizing:</strong> Use hash-compatible vaporizer at 180-210°C for smooth, flavourful vapour with maximum terpene preservation.</li>\n<li><strong>Hot Knives:</strong> Traditional method heating two knives and pressing hash between them for immediate effects.</li>\n<li><strong>Topping Bowls:</strong> Add small pieces atop flower bowls for elevated potency without altering your regular routine.</li>\n<li><strong>Hash Edibles (Advanced):</strong> To make edibles, decarboxylate hash at 110-120°C (230-250°F) for 30-40 minutes to activate THC. Mix into butter or oil-based recipes. Effects take 30-120 minutes and last 6-12 hours. Hash edibles are significantly more potent than flower edibles—start with 1/4 of your normal flower edible dose.</li>\n</ul>\n<h3>Onset &amp; Duration</h3>\n<ul>\n<li><strong>Onset (Smoking/Vaping):</strong> 2-10 minutes</li>\n<li><strong>Onset (Edibles):</strong> 30-120 minutes</li>\n<li><strong>Peak Effects:</strong> 15-45 minutes (inhaled) or 2-4 hours (edibles)</li>\n<li><strong>Duration:</strong> 2-4 hours (inhaled) or 6-12 hours (edibles)</li>\n</ul>\n<p><strong>⚠️ Important:</strong> Hash is significantly more potent than regular flower. Start with minimal amounts and wait to assess effects before consuming more. for experienced users – beginners should start with lower doses or those new to concentrates.</p>\n</div>\n</div>",
