        "descriptionHTML": "<div class=\"tab-pane active\" id=\"tab-description\">\n<div class=\"detail-tab-desc detail-content-wrap\">\n<p>**Buy MOBO 18k Nicotine Vape online in Canada at Mohawk Medibles**, your trusted Indigenous-owned dispensary. Shop this high-capacity disposable vape and enjoy fast Canada-wide shipping with same-day processing. Order now for discreet delivery and experience 18,000 puffs of smooth, satisfying vapor with advanced mesh coil technology and adjustable airflow. Perfect for vapers seeking convenience, performance, and exceptional value.</p>\n<p>–</p>\n<h2>💡 Usage Guide</h2>\n<h3>How to Use Your MOBO 18K</h3>\n<ul>\n<li><strong>First Use:</strong> Remove device from packaging and remove any protective caps or stickers. No charging or filling required—ready to vape immediately</li>\n<li><strong>Activation:</strong> Simply inhale through the mouthpiece to activate. The device is draw-activated with no buttons needed</li>\n<li><strong>Airflow Adjustment:</strong> Rotate the airflow control ring at the base to customize your draw from tight MTL to loose DTL</li>\n<li><strong>Monitoring:</strong> Check the dual LED display screens to track battery life and e-liquid levels in real-time</li>\n<li><strong>Charging:</strong> Connect the included USB-C cable when battery indicator is low. Fully charges in approximately 60-90 minutes</li>\n</ul>\n<h3>Recommended Usage</h3>\n<ul>\n<li><strong>New Vapers:</strong> Start with 3-5 short puffs and wait 5-10 minutes to assess nicotine satisfaction</li>\n<li><strong>Experienced Users:</strong> Use as needed throughout the day; 18,000 puffs typically lasts 2-4 weeks with moderate use</li>\n<li><strong>Optimal Performance:</strong> Take 2-3 second draws for best flavor and vapor production</li>\n</ul>\n<h3>Lifespan &amp; Maintenance</h3>\n<ul>\n<li><strong>Expected Duration:</strong> 18,000 puffs equals approximately 2-4 weeks for average users</li>\n<li><strong>Storage:</strong> Keep in cool, dry place away from direct sunlight when not in use</li>\n<li><strong>Disposal:</strong> When depleted, dispose of responsibly according to local electronic waste regulations</li>\n</ul>\n<h3>Best Use Cases</h3>\n<p>The MOBO 18K is ideal for all-day vaping, travel, and anyone seeking a hassle-free alternative to traditional cigarettes. The large 25mL capacity and rechargeable battery make it perfect for extended use without frequent replacements. The adjustable airflow suits both mouth-to-lung (MTL) and direct-to-lung (DTL) vaping styles.</p>\n<p><strong>⚠️ Important Safety Information:</strong> This product contains nicotine, a highly addictive substance. Not intended for non-smokers, pregnant or breastfeeding women, or individuals with heart conditions. Keep out of reach of children and pets. For adult use only (19+ in Canada).</p>\n<h2>❓ Frequently Asked Questions</h2>\n<h3>How many puffs does the MOBO 18K provide?</h3>\n<p><strong>A:</strong> The MOBO 18K delivers up to 18,000 puffs, making it one of the highest-capacity disposable vapes available. With moderate use (400-600 puffs per day), this device typically lasts 2-4 weeks, offering exceptional value and convenience.</p>\n<h3>What nicotine strength is the MOBO 18K?</h3>\n<p><strong>A:</strong> The MOBO 18K contains 20mg/mL (2%) nicotine salt e-liquid, providing smooth throat hit and fast nicotine satisfaction. This strength is ideal for former smokers and experienced vapers seeking effective nicotine delivery without harshness.</p>\n<h3>Is the MOBO 18K rechargeable?</h3>\n<p><strong>A:</strong> Yes! The MOBO 18K features a rechargeable 650mAh battery with USB-C fast charging. This ensures you can use all 25mL of e-liquid without the battery dying prematurely. The dual LED displays show battery level so you know when to recharge.</p>\n<h3>How do I adjust the airflow on the MOBO 18K?</h3>\n<p><strong>A:</strong> The MOBO 18K features an adjustable airflow control ring located at the base of the device. Simply rotate the ring to customize your draw resistance—tighten for a cigarette-like MTL experience or open for increased vapor production and a looser DTL draw.</p>\n<h3>What flavors are available for the MOBO 18K?</h3>\n<p><strong>A:</strong> The MOBO 18K comes in a variety of delicious flavors crafted with premium Nic Salt e-liquid. Browse our selection to find your perfect flavor profile, from refreshing fruits to classic tobacco and menthol options. Each flavor is optimized for the advanced mesh coil technology.</p>\n<h3>Does Mohawk Medibles ship the MOBO 18K across Canada?</h3>\n<p><strong>A:</strong> Yes! We offer fast, discreet Canada-wide shipping on all MOBO 18K vapes. Orders placed before 2 PM EST are processed the same day. All packages arrive in plain, unmarked packaging to ensure privacy. Must be 19+ with valid ID for delivery.</p>\n<h3>How should I store my MOBO 18K vape?</h3>\n<p><strong>A:</strong> Store your MOBO 18K in a cool, dry place away from direct sunlight and extreme temperatures. Keep upright when possible to prevent leaking. Always keep out of reach of children and pets. When not in use for extended periods, store in a protective case to prevent accidental activation.</p>\n</div>\n</div>",
