        "shortDescription": "**Buy Burn 2G Disposable THC Vape online in Canada at Mohawk Medibles**, your trusted Indigenous-owned cannabis dispensary. Shop this premium solventless distillate vape pen featuring natural terpen...",
        "descriptionHTML": "<div class=\"tab-pane active\" id=\"tab-description\">\n<div class=\"detail-tab-desc detail-content-wrap\">\n<p>**Buy Burn 2G Disposable THC Vape online in Canada at Mohawk Medibles**, your trusted Indigenous-owned cannabis dispensary. Shop this premium solventless distillate vape pen featuring natural terpenes and BC’s finest flower extracts. Order now for fast Canada-wide shipping with same-day processing and discreet delivery. Experience convenient, pull-activated vaping with 2,000mg of quality distillate oil in every pen.</p>\n<p>–</p>\n<h2>💡 Usage Guide</h2>\n<h3>Recommended Dosage</h3>\n<ul>\n<li><strong>Beginners:</strong> Start with 1-2 second draws and wait 10-15 minutes to assess effects before continuing</li>\n<li><strong>Experienced Users:</strong> 3-5 second draws as needed, spacing sessions by 30-60 minutes</li>\n<li><strong>High Tolerance:</strong> Standard 5 second draws with breaks between sessions to monitor effects</li>\n</ul>\n<h3>How to Use Your Disposable Vape</h3>\n<ul>\n<li><strong>Pull-Activated:</strong> No buttons required—simply inhale from the mouthpiece to activate</li>\n<li><strong>Draw Technique:</strong> Take slow, steady draws for up to 5 seconds for optimal vapour production</li>\n<li><strong>Inhale Method:</strong> Draw vapour into mouth first, then inhale to lungs for smoother experience</li>\n<li><strong>Between Uses:</strong> Store upright in cool, dry place away from direct sunlight</li>\n</ul>\n<h3>Onset &amp; Duration</h3>\n<ul>\n<li><strong>Onset:</strong> 2-5 minutes (one of the fastest delivery methods)</li>\n<li><strong>Peak Effects:</strong> 15-30 minutes after consumption</li>\n<li><strong>Duration:</strong> 1-3 hours depending on dosage and tolerance</li>\n</ul>\n<h3>Best Use Cases</h3>\n<p>Perfect for on-the-go convenience and discreet consumption. The 2-gram capacity provides excellent value for regular users, while the pull-activated design makes it ideal for both beginners and experienced consumers. Great for quick relief throughout the day or relaxing evening sessions. The solventless extraction and natural terpene infusion ensure clean flavour with every draw.</p>\n<p><strong>⚠️ Important:</strong> Do not attempt to recharge or refill this disposable device. Discontinue use if device becomes hot or produces burnt taste. Keep away from extreme temperatures. Not for use by persons under 19 years of age.</p>\n<h2>❓ Frequently Asked Questions</h2>\n<h3>What makes Burn disposable vapes different from other brands?</h3>\n<p><strong>A:</strong> Burn uses solventless extraction methods and sources exclusively from premium BC flower growers. Their “fire in, fire out” philosophy ensures only the highest quality starting material, resulting in clean-tasting distillate infused with natural terpenes rather than artificial flavouring.</p>\n<h3>How many draws can I get from a 2G Burn disposable?</h3>\n<p><strong>A:</strong> A 2-gram (2,000mg) disposable typically provides 400-600 draws depending on draw length and technique. With standard 3-5 second draws, expect several weeks of regular use for most consumers, making this an excellent value option.</p>\n<h3>Is the Burn 2G disposable vape pull-activated or button-activated?</h3>\n<p><strong>A:</strong> The Burn disposable is pull-activated for maximum convenience. Simply draw from the mouthpiece and the device automatically activates. No buttons, no charging, no maintenance required—just inhale and enjoy.</p>\n<h3>What does “solventless” mean and why does it matter?</h3>\n<p><strong>A:</strong> Solventless extraction means no chemical solvents (like butane or propane) are used in the extraction process. This results in a cleaner, purer product that better preserves the natural cannabinoids and terpenes from the original flower, providing superior flavour and effects.</p>\n<h3>How should I store my Burn disposable vape?</h3>\n<p><strong>A:</strong> Store your vape upright in a cool, dry place away from direct sunlight and extreme temperatures. Avoid leaving it in hot cars or cold environments. Proper storage maintains oil viscosity and device performance throughout its lifespan.</p>\n<h3>Does Mohawk Medibles ship Burn vapes across Canada?</h3>\n<p><strong>A:</strong> Yes! We offer fast, discreet Canada-wide shipping on all Burn products with same-day processing on orders placed before 2 PM EST. All packages arrive in plain, unmarked packaging to ensure privacy and discretion.</p>\n<h3>Can I take this vape on a plane within Canada?</h3>\n<p><strong>A:</strong> While cannabis is legal in Canada, you cannot fly with cannabis products between provinces or territories. Transport Canada prohibits cannabis on all domestic and international flights, regardless of packaging or amount. Plan accordingly for travel.</p>\n</div>\n</div>",
