        "descriptionHTML": "<div class=\"tab-pane active\" id=\"tab-description\">\n<div class=\"detail-tab-desc detail-content-wrap\">\n<p data-end=\"811\" data-start=\"490\"><strong data-end=\"517\" data-start=\"490\">Zealousy LA Mousse Hash</strong> brings together <strong data-end=\"560\" data-start=\"534\">modern hybrid genetics</strong> and <strong data-end=\"603\" data-start=\"565\">premium French Touch craftsmanship</strong> for a refined, versatile hash experience. To start, this balanced hybrid comes from the flavorful cross of <strong data-end=\"730\" data-start=\"711\">Jealousy × Zoap</strong>, a pairing known for complexity, smooth potency, and layered terpene expression.</p>\n<p data-end=\"1183\" data-start=\"813\">Right away, the effects feel even and controlled 🧠✨. First, a gentle mental lift improves mood and sharpens awareness. Focus feels easier, thoughts stay calm, and stress begins to fade. Soon after, a light body relaxation follows, smoothing out tension without dragging you down. Because of this balance, Zealousy works well for both daytime and early evening sessions.</p>\n<p data-end=\"1402\" data-start=\"1185\">As the experience continues, the high remains steady and functional 😌. You stay clear-headed yet relaxed, making this hash a great option for social settings, creative work, or simply staying present while unwinding.</p>\n<p data-end=\"1751\" data-start=\"1404\">Meanwhile, the flavour profile evolves with every pull 🍬🧀. Sweet, fruity notes lead on the inhale, thanks to its limonene-rich terpene profile. Then, on the exhale, those bright flavours shift into a savory, slightly cheesy finish that adds depth and character. Earthy undertones tie everything together, keeping the smoke smooth and satisfying.</p>\n<p data-end=\"1972\" data-start=\"1753\">Because this is <strong data-end=\"1787\" data-start=\"1769\">LA Mousse Hash</strong>, the texture stays <strong data-end=\"1837\" data-start=\"1807\">light, fluffy, and aerated</strong>. As a result, it’s easy to handle, melts cleanly, and delivers consistent flavour whether sprinkled into flower or enjoyed on its own.</p>\n<hr data-end=\"1977\" data-start=\"1974\"/>\n<h3 data-end=\"2004\" data-start=\"1979\">✨ Effects You’ll Feel</h3>\n<ul data-end=\"2145\" data-start=\"2005\">\n<li data-end=\"2033\" data-start=\"2005\">\n<p data-end=\"2033\" data-start=\"2007\">😊 Uplifted and balanced</p>\n</li>\n<li data-end=\"2058\" data-start=\"2034\">\n<p data-end=\"2058\" data-start=\"2036\">🧠 Clear, calm focus</p>\n</li>\n<li data-end=\"2087\" data-start=\"2059\">\n<p data-end=\"2087\" data-start=\"2061\">😌 Light body relaxation</p>\n</li>\n<li data-end=\"2115\" data-start=\"2088\">\n<p data-end=\"2115\" data-start=\"2090\">🌤️ Smooth, steady high</p>\n</li>\n<li data-end=\"2145\" data-start=\"2116\">\n<p data-end=\"2145\" data-start=\"2118\">🗣️ Social and functional</p>\n</li>\n</ul>\n<hr data-end=\"2150\" data-start=\"2147\"/>\n<h3 data-end=\"2178\" data-start=\"2152\">🩺 Commonly Chosen For</h3>\n<ul data-end=\"2287\" data-start=\"2179\">\n<li data-end=\"2200\" data-start=\"2179\">\n<p data-end=\"2200\" data-start=\"2181\">Stress management</p>\n</li>\n<li data-end=\"2217\" data-start=\"2201\">\n<p data-end=\"2217\" data-start=\"2203\">Mood balance</p>\n</li>\n<li data-end=\"2236\" data-start=\"2218\">\n<p data-end=\"2236\" data-start=\"2220\">Mental fatigue</p>\n</li>\n<li data-end=\"2254\" data-start=\"2237\">\n<p data-end=\"2254\" data-start=\"2239\">Light anxiety</p>\n</li>\n<li data-end=\"2287\" data-start=\"2255\">\n<p data-end=\"2287\" data-start=\"2257\">Daytime or early evening use</p>\n</li>\n</ul>\n<hr data-end=\"2292\" data-start=\"2289\"/>\n<h3 data-end=\"2314\" data-start=\"2294\">🍬 Flavour Notes</h3>\n<ul data-end=\"2380\" data-start=\"2315\">\n<li data-end=\"2330\" data-start=\"2315\">\n<p data-end=\"2330\" data-start=\"2317\">Sweet fruit</p>\n</li>\n<li data-end=\"2346\" data-start=\"2331\">\n<p data-end=\"2346\" data-start=\"2333\">Citrus zest</p>\n</li>\n<li data-end=\"2364\" data-start=\"2347\">\n<p data-end=\"2364\" data-start=\"2349\">Savory cheese</p>\n</li>\n<li data-end=\"2380\" data-start=\"2365\">\n<p data-end=\"2380\" data-start=\"2367\">Light earth</p>\n</li>\n</ul>\n<hr data-end=\"2385\" data-start=\"2382\"/>\n<h3 data-end=\"2408\" data-start=\"2387\">🌬️ Aroma Profile</h3>\n<ul data-end=\"2468\" data-start=\"2409\">\n<li data-end=\"2427\" data-start=\"2409\">\n<p data-end=\"2427\" data-start=\"2411\">Citrus-forward</p>\n</li>\n<li data-end=\"2448\" data-start=\"2428\">\n<p data-end=\"2448\" data-start=\"2430\">Fruity sweetness</p>\n</li>\n<li data-end=\"2468\" data-start=\"2449\">\n<p data-end=\"2468\" data-start=\"2451\">Earthy &amp; savory</p>\n</li>\n</ul>\n<hr data-end=\"2473\" data-start=\"2470\"/>\n<h3 data-end=\"2520\" data-start=\"2475\">💎 Why Zealousy LA Mousse Hash Stands Out</h3>\n<ul data-end=\"2700\" data-start=\"2521\">\n<li data-end=\"2554\" data-start=\"2521\">\n<p data-end=\"2554\" data-start=\"2523\"><strong data-end=\"2535\" data-start=\"2523\">~21% THC</strong> balanced potency</p>\n</li>\n<li data-end=\"2588\" data-start=\"2555\">\n<p data-end=\"2588\" data-start=\"2557\">Limonene-rich terpene profile</p>\n</li>\n<li data-end=\"2623\" data-start=\"2589\">\n<p data-end=\"2623\" data-start=\"2591\">Premium <strong data-end=\"2623\" data-start=\"2599\">solventless dry sift</strong></p>\n</li>\n<li data-end=\"2665\" data-start=\"2624\">\n<p data-end=\"2665\" data-start=\"2626\">Light, aerated <strong data-end=\"2665\" data-start=\"2641\">French Touch texture</strong></p>\n</li>\n<li data-end=\"2700\" data-start=\"2666\">\n<p data-end=\"2700\" data-start=\"2668\">Smooth, versatile hybrid effects</p>\n</li>\n</ul>\n<hr/>\n<h2>💡 Usage Guide</h2>\n<h3>Recommended Dosage</h3>\n<ul>\n<li><strong>Beginners:</strong> Start with a rice grain-sized piece (approximately 0.025-0.05g). Hash is significantly more potent than flower.</li>\n<li><strong>Experienced Users:</strong> 0.1-0.2g per session, adjusting based on tolerance and desired effects.</li>\n<li><strong>High Tolerance:</strong> Up to 0.3g per session for seasoned concentrate consumers.</li>\n</ul>\n<h3>Consumption Methods</h3>\n<ul>\n<li><strong>Smoking:</strong> Crumble and mix with flower in joints, pipes, or bongs for enhanced potency and traditional experience.</li>\n<li><strong>Vaporizing:</strong> Use hash-compatible vaporizer at 180-210°C for smooth, flavourful vapour with maximum terpene preservation.</li>\n<li><strong>Hot Knives:</strong> Traditional method heating two knives and pressing hash between them for immediate effects.</li>\n<li><strong>Topping Bowls:</strong> Add small pieces atop flower bowls for elevated potency without altering your regular routine.</li>\n<li><strong>Hash Edibles (Advanced):</strong> To make edibles, decarboxylate hash at 110-120°C (230-250°F) for 30-40 minutes to activate THC. Mix into butter or oil-based recipes. Effects take 30-120 minutes and last 6-12 hours. Hash edibles are significantly more potent than flower edibles—start with 1/4 of your normal flower edible dose.</li>\n</ul>\n<h3>Onset &amp; Duration</h3>\n<ul>\n<li><strong>Onset (Smoking/Vaping):</strong> 2-10 minutes</li>\n<li><strong>Onset (Edibles):</strong> 30-120 minutes</li>\n<li><strong>Peak Effects:</strong> 15-45 minutes (inhaled) or 2-4 hours (edibles)</li>\n<li><strong>Duration:</strong> 2-4 hours (inhaled) or 6-12 hours (edibles)</li>\n</ul>\n<p><strong>⚠️ Important:</strong> Hash is significantly more potent than regular flower. Start with minimal amounts and wait to assess effects before consuming more. for experienced users – beginners should start with lower doses or those new to concentrates.</p>\n</div>\n</div>",
