        "descriptionHTML": "<div class=\"tab-pane active\" id=\"tab-description\">\n<div class=\"detail-tab-desc detail-content-wrap\">\n<p>**Buy RAW Classic 1¼ Cones online in Canada at Mohawk Medibles**, your trusted Indigenous-owned cannabis dispensary. Shop these premium pre-rolled cones made from unrefined, unbleached paper and enjoy fast Canada-wide shipping with same-day processing. Order now for discreet delivery of authentic RAW rolling accessories from Tyendinaga Mohawk Territory. Perfect for cannabis enthusiasts who value natural, chemical-free smoking experiences.</p>\n<p>–</p>\n<h2>💡 Usage Guide</h2>\n<h3>How to Fill Your RAW Cones</h3>\n<ul>\n<li><strong>Step 1:</strong> Hold the cone upright and gently fill with ground cannabis, leaving 3-4mm space at the top</li>\n<li><strong>Step 2:</strong> Tap the cone gently on a flat surface to settle the material evenly</li>\n<li><strong>Step 3:</strong> Use the included packing stick or a pen to pack down lightly—don’t over-pack or airflow will be restricted</li>\n<li><strong>Step 4:</strong> Twist the open end to seal and create a lighting tip</li>\n</ul>\n<h3>Recommended Amount</h3>\n<ul>\n<li><strong>Beginners:</strong> Fill halfway (approximately 0.4-0.5g) for a lighter session</li>\n<li><strong>Experienced Users:</strong> Fill completely (approximately 0.7-0.9g) for a full session</li>\n<li><strong>Sharing:</strong> One fully-packed 1¼ cone is ideal for 1-2 people</li>\n</ul>\n<h3>Best Practices</h3>\n<ul>\n<li><strong>Grind Consistency:</strong> Use a medium grind—not too fine (restricts airflow) or too coarse (burns unevenly)</li>\n<li><strong>Storage:</strong> Keep unused cones in original packaging away from moisture to maintain freshness</li>\n<li><strong>Lighting:</strong> Light the twisted tip evenly, rotating while lighting for a smooth, even burn</li>\n</ul>\n<h3>Why Choose RAW Classic Cones?</h3>\n<p>These cones eliminate the learning curve of rolling while delivering the authentic experience of unbleached, additive-free paper. The 1¼ size offers the perfect balance between portability and capacity, making them ideal for solo sessions or sharing with a friend. The natural gum line ensures a secure seal every time.</p>\n<h2>❓ Frequently Asked Questions</h2>\n<h3>What size are RAW Classic 1¼ Cones?</h3>\n<p><strong>A:</strong> RAW Classic 1¼ cones are 84mm in length when filled, making them slightly larger than a standard cigarette. They hold approximately 0.7-0.9g of ground cannabis when fully packed, perfect for personal use or sharing between two people.</p>\n<h3>Are RAW cones better than regular rolling papers?</h3>\n<p><strong>A:</strong> RAW cones offer convenience without sacrificing quality. They’re pre-rolled to perfection, eliminating the skill required for hand-rolling while using the same premium unrefined, unbleached paper. Ideal for beginners or anyone who wants consistent, perfectly-shaped joints every time.</p>\n<h3>How many cones come in a pack?</h3>\n<p><strong>A:</strong> Pack quantities vary by product option. Check the product specifications for exact count. RAW Classic 1¼ Cones are typically available in packs of 6, 32, or bulk boxes for regular users.</p>\n<h3>What makes RAW papers different from other brands?</h3>\n<p><strong>A:</strong> RAW papers are made from unrefined, unbleached plant fibres with no added chalk or dyes. They’re naturally brown in colour and use a natural tree sap gum line. This chemical-free composition provides a cleaner, purer smoking experience that lets you taste your cannabis, not the paper.</p>\n<h3>Do RAW Classic Cones burn evenly?</h3>\n<p><strong>A:</strong> Yes, when properly filled and packed. RAW’s patented criss-cross watermark helps ensure even burning. For best results, use a medium grind, pack evenly without over-compacting, and light the twisted tip uniformly while rotating.</p>\n<h3>Does Mohawk Medibles ship RAW Cones across Canada?</h3>\n<p><strong>A:</strong> Absolutely! We offer fast, discreet Canada-wide shipping on all smoking accessories including RAW Classic 1¼ Cones. Orders placed before 2 PM EST are processed the same day. All packages arrive in plain, unmarked packaging to protect your privacy.</p>\n<h3>Can I use RAW Cones for tobacco?</h3>\n<p><strong>A:</strong> While RAW Cones are designed and marketed for legal cannabis use, they’re suitable for any legal smoking material. The unbleached paper and natural gum provide a clean smoking experience regardless of content. Always comply with local laws regarding cannabis and tobacco use.</p>\n</div>\n</div>",
