        "descriptionHTML": "<div class=\"tab-pane active\" id=\"tab-description\">\n<div class=\"detail-tab-desc detail-content-wrap\">\n<p data-end=\"728\" data-start=\"451\">Nepalese Temple Ball Hash is one of the <strong data-end=\"550\" data-start=\"491\">oldest and most respected forms of hashish in the world</strong> 🌿. Crafted for generations in the Himalayan regions of Nepal, this iconic concentrate stands apart for its <strong data-end=\"727\" data-start=\"659\">traditional production, striking appearance, and extreme potency</strong>.</p>\n<p data-end=\"1036\" data-start=\"730\">First, fresh cannabis resin is carefully collected by hand. Then, skilled artisans slowly roll the resin into <strong data-end=\"865\" data-start=\"840\">dense, polished balls</strong>, allowing heat, pressure, and time to work naturally. Because of this process, each temple ball develops a <strong data-end=\"1035\" data-start=\"973\">shiny exterior, soft interior, and incredibly smooth smoke</strong>.</p>\n<p data-end=\"1373\" data-start=\"1038\">Once consumed, the experience unfolds steadily. At first, rich earthy flavours coat the palate. Shortly after, subtle sweetness appears. Soon after that, a <strong data-end=\"1223\" data-start=\"1194\">deep body calm settles in</strong>, easing tension while quieting the mind. With THC levels ranging from <strong data-end=\"1308\" data-start=\"1294\">55% to 80%</strong>, even a small amount delivers powerful, long-lasting effects 🔥.</p>\n<p data-end=\"1518\" data-start=\"1375\">For this reason, Nepalese Temple Ball Hash is best suited for <strong data-end=\"1458\" data-start=\"1437\">experienced users</strong> seeking a classic, full-bodied, old-school hash experience.</p>\n<hr data-end=\"1523\" data-start=\"1520\"/>\n<h3 data-end=\"1553\" data-start=\"1525\">✨ Effects You Can Expect</h3>\n<ul data-end=\"1686\" data-start=\"1554\">\n<li data-end=\"1585\" data-start=\"1554\">\n<p data-end=\"1585\" data-start=\"1556\">😌 Deep physical relaxation</p>\n</li>\n<li data-end=\"1615\" data-start=\"1586\">\n<p data-end=\"1615\" data-start=\"1588\">🧠 Calm, euphoric mindset</p>\n</li>\n<li data-end=\"1652\" data-start=\"1616\">\n<p data-end=\"1652\" data-start=\"1618\">🌙 Long-lasting sedative effects</p>\n</li>\n<li data-end=\"1686\" data-start=\"1653\">\n<p data-end=\"1686\" data-start=\"1655\">🧘 Grounded, peaceful feeling</p>\n</li>\n</ul>\n<hr data-end=\"1691\" data-start=\"1688\"/>\n<h3 data-end=\"1713\" data-start=\"1693\">🩺 May Help With</h3>\n<ul data-end=\"1801\" data-start=\"1714\">\n<li data-end=\"1730\" data-start=\"1714\">\n<p data-end=\"1730\" data-start=\"1716\">Chronic pain</p>\n</li>\n<li data-end=\"1751\" data-start=\"1731\">\n<p data-end=\"1751\" data-start=\"1733\">Stress &amp; anxiety</p>\n</li>\n<li data-end=\"1764\" data-start=\"1752\">\n<p data-end=\"1764\" data-start=\"1754\">Insomnia</p>\n</li>\n<li data-end=\"1783\" data-start=\"1765\">\n<p data-end=\"1783\" data-start=\"1767\">Muscle tension</p>\n</li>\n<li data-end=\"1801\" data-start=\"1784\">\n<p data-end=\"1801\" data-start=\"1786\">Appetite loss</p>\n</li>\n</ul>\n<hr data-end=\"1806\" data-start=\"1803\"/>\n<h3 data-end=\"1830\" data-start=\"1808\">🌿 Flavour Profile</h3>\n<ul data-end=\"1888\" data-start=\"1831\">\n<li data-end=\"1841\" data-start=\"1831\">\n<p data-end=\"1841\" data-start=\"1833\">Earthy</p>\n</li>\n<li data-end=\"1851\" data-start=\"1842\">\n<p data-end=\"1851\" data-start=\"1844\">Woody</p>\n</li>\n<li data-end=\"1871\" data-start=\"1852\">\n<p data-end=\"1871\" data-start=\"1854\">Light sweetness</p>\n</li>\n<li data-end=\"1888\" data-start=\"1872\">\n<p data-end=\"1888\" data-start=\"1874\">Herbal resin</p>\n</li>\n</ul>\n<hr data-end=\"1893\" data-start=\"1890\"/>\n<h3 data-end=\"1908\" data-start=\"1895\">🌬️ Aroma</h3>\n<ul data-end=\"1967\" data-start=\"1909\">\n<li data-end=\"1923\" data-start=\"1909\">\n<p data-end=\"1923\" data-start=\"1911\">Warm earth</p>\n</li>\n<li data-end=\"1946\" data-start=\"1924\">\n<p data-end=\"1946\" data-start=\"1926\">Natural hash resin</p>\n</li>\n<li data-end=\"1967\" data-start=\"1947\">\n<p data-end=\"1967\" data-start=\"1949\">Subtle sweetness</p>\n</li>\n</ul>\n<hr data-end=\"1972\" data-start=\"1969\"/>\n<h3 data-end=\"1993\" data-start=\"1974\">🔥 How to Enjoy</h3>\n<ul data-end=\"2121\" data-start=\"1994\">\n<li data-end=\"2042\" data-start=\"1994\">\n<p data-end=\"2042\" data-start=\"1996\">Smoke or vaporize for fast, powerful effects</p>\n</li>\n<li data-end=\"2077\" data-start=\"2043\">\n<p data-end=\"2077\" data-start=\"2045\">Add to flower to boost potency</p>\n</li>\n<li data-end=\"2121\" data-start=\"2078\">\n<p data-end=\"2121\" data-start=\"2080\">Infuse into edibles for extended relief</p>\n</li>\n</ul>\n</div>\n</div>",
