        "shortDescription": "🍦 Vanilla Hash – $5/Gram Special\nIndica-Dominant • Smooth • Sweet Vanilla + Earthy Woods • THC: 18%–22%\n\nVanilla Hash delivers a rustic, powerful hash experience with a soft, sweet twist.From the fi...",
        "descriptionHTML": "<div class=\"tab-pane active\" id=\"tab-description\">\n<div class=\"detail-tab-desc detail-content-wrap\">\n<h2 data-end=\"242\" data-start=\"201\">🍦 <strong data-end=\"240\" data-start=\"206\">Vanilla Hash – $5/Gram Special</strong></h2>\n<p data-end=\"302\" data-start=\"243\"><strong data-end=\"302\" data-start=\"243\">Indica-Dominant • Smooth • Sweet Vanilla + Earthy Woods • THC: 18%–22%</strong></p>\n<hr/>\n<p data-end=\"900\" data-start=\"666\">Vanilla Hash delivers a <strong data-end=\"726\" data-start=\"690\">rustic, powerful hash experience</strong> with a soft, sweet twist.<br data-end=\"755\" data-start=\"752\"/><strong data-end=\"780\" data-start=\"755\">From the first smell,</strong> you’re greeted with warm vanilla notes layered over deep earthy tones—giving this hash a comforting and inviting scent.</p>\n<p data-end=\"1149\" data-start=\"902\"><strong data-end=\"923\" data-start=\"902\">As you handle it,</strong> the natural woody aroma becomes richer, blending smoothly with the vanilla sweetness.<br data-end=\"1012\" data-start=\"1009\"/><strong data-end=\"1025\" data-start=\"1012\">Once lit,</strong> the flavour unfolds gently, offering an earthy base with a creamy vanilla finish that makes each pull smooth and enjoyable.</p>\n<p data-end=\"1488\" data-start=\"1151\"><strong data-end=\"1184\" data-start=\"1151\">Soon after your first inhale,</strong> the Indica-heavy effects begin to settle into your body. A calm wave spreads through your muscles, easing tension and quieting stress.<br data-end=\"1322\" data-start=\"1319\"/><strong data-end=\"1348\" data-start=\"1322\">As the high continues,</strong> your mind stays clear enough to relax without feeling overwhelmed, making it perfect for evening sessions or winding down after a long day.</p>\n<p data-end=\"1662\" data-start=\"1490\">Vanilla Hash is ideal for smokers who want <strong data-end=\"1596\" data-start=\"1533\">classic Backwoods hash power with a sweet, aromatic upgrade</strong>—smooth texture, steady potency, and a relaxing, full-bodied high.</p>\n<hr data-end=\"1667\" data-start=\"1664\"/>\n<h3 data-end=\"1687\" data-start=\"1669\">🔥 <strong data-end=\"1685\" data-start=\"1674\">EFFECTS</strong></h3>\n<ul data-end=\"1803\" data-start=\"1688\">\n<li data-end=\"1717\" data-start=\"1688\">\n<p data-end=\"1717\" data-start=\"1690\">Deep full-body relaxation</p>\n</li>\n<li data-end=\"1741\" data-start=\"1718\">\n<p data-end=\"1741\" data-start=\"1720\">Calm, clear mindset</p>\n</li>\n<li data-end=\"1759\" data-start=\"1742\">\n<p data-end=\"1759\" data-start=\"1744\">Stress relief</p>\n</li>\n<li data-end=\"1779\" data-start=\"1760\">\n<p data-end=\"1779\" data-start=\"1762\">Gentle euphoria</p>\n</li>\n<li data-end=\"1803\" data-start=\"1780\">\n<p data-end=\"1803\" data-start=\"1782\">Evening tranquility</p>\n</li>\n</ul>\n<hr data-end=\"1808\" data-start=\"1805\"/>\n<h3 data-end=\"1834\" data-start=\"1810\">🌿 <strong data-end=\"1832\" data-start=\"1815\">MAY HELP WITH</strong></h3>\n<ul data-end=\"1928\" data-start=\"1835\">\n<li data-end=\"1845\" data-start=\"1835\">\n<p data-end=\"1845\" data-start=\"1837\">Stress</p>\n</li>\n<li data-end=\"1857\" data-start=\"1846\">\n<p data-end=\"1857\" data-start=\"1848\">Anxiety</p>\n</li>\n<li data-end=\"1874\" data-start=\"1858\">\n<p data-end=\"1874\" data-start=\"1860\">Chronic pain</p>\n</li>\n<li data-end=\"1893\" data-start=\"1875\">\n<p data-end=\"1893\" data-start=\"1877\">Muscle tension</p>\n</li>\n<li data-end=\"1910\" data-start=\"1894\">\n<p data-end=\"1910\" data-start=\"1896\">Restlessness</p>\n</li>\n<li data-end=\"1928\" data-start=\"1911\">\n<p data-end=\"1928\" data-start=\"1913\">Sleep support</p>\n</li>\n</ul>\n<hr data-end=\"1933\" data-start=\"1930\"/>\n<h3 data-end=\"1953\" data-start=\"1935\">🍦 <strong data-end=\"1951\" data-start=\"1940\">FLAVORS</strong></h3>\n<ul data-end=\"2008\" data-start=\"1954\">\n<li data-end=\"1971\" data-start=\"1954\">\n<p data-end=\"1971\" data-start=\"1956\">Sweet vanilla</p>\n</li>\n<li data-end=\"1982\" data-start=\"1972\">\n<p data-end=\"1982\" data-start=\"1974\">Earthy</p>\n</li>\n<li data-end=\"1992\" data-start=\"1983\">\n<p data-end=\"1992\" data-start=\"1985\">Woody</p>\n</li>\n<li data-end=\"2008\" data-start=\"1993\">\n<p data-end=\"2008\" data-start=\"1995\">Smooth hash</p>\n</li>\n</ul>\n<hr data-end=\"2013\" data-start=\"2010\"/>\n<h3 data-end=\"2033\" data-start=\"2015\">🌬️ <strong data-end=\"2031\" data-start=\"2021\">AROMAS</strong></h3>\n<ul data-end=\"2107\" data-start=\"2034\">\n<li data-end=\"2050\" data-start=\"2034\">\n<p data-end=\"2050\" data-start=\"2036\">Warm vanilla</p>\n</li>\n<li data-end=\"2065\" data-start=\"2051\">\n<p data-end=\"2065\" data-start=\"2053\">Deep woods</p>\n</li>\n<li data-end=\"2088\" data-start=\"2066\">\n<p data-end=\"2088\" data-start=\"2068\">Natural hash spice</p>\n</li>\n<li data-end=\"2107\" data-start=\"2089\">\n<p data-end=\"2107\" data-start=\"2091\">Soft sweetness</p>\n</li>\n</ul>\n<hr/>\n<h2>💡 Usage Guide</h2>\n<h3>Recommended Dosage</h3>\n<ul>\n<li><strong>Beginners:</strong> Start with a rice grain-sized piece (approximately 0.025-0.05g). Hash is significantly more potent than flower.</li>\n<li><strong>Experienced Users:</strong> 0.1-0.2g per session, adjusting based on tolerance and desired effects.</li>\n<li><strong>High Tolerance:</strong> Up to 0.3g per session for seasoned concentrate consumers.</li>\n</ul>\n<h3>Consumption Methods</h3>\n<ul>\n<li><strong>Smoking:</strong> Crumble and mix with flower in joints, pipes, or bongs for enhanced potency and traditional experience.</li>\n<li><strong>Vaporizing:</strong> Use hash-compatible vaporizer at 180-210°C for smooth, flavourful vapour with maximum terpene preservation.</li>\n<li><strong>Hot Knives:</strong> Traditional method heating two knives and pressing hash between them for immediate effects.</li>\n<li><strong>Topping Bowls:</strong> Add small pieces atop flower bowls for elevated potency without altering your regular routine.</li>\n<li><strong>Hash Edibles (Advanced):</strong> To make edibles, decarboxylate hash at 110-120°C (230-250°F) for 30-40 minutes to activate THC. Mix into butter or oil-based recipes. Effects take 30-120 minutes and last 6-12 hours. Hash edibles are significantly more potent than flower edibles—start with 1/4 of your normal flower edible dose.</li>\n</ul>\n<h3>Onset &amp; Duration</h3>\n<ul>\n<li><strong>Onset (Smoking/Vaping):</strong> 2-10 minutes</li>\n<li><strong>Onset (Edibles):</strong> 30-120 minutes</li>\n<li><strong>Peak Effects:</strong> 15-45 minutes (inhaled) or 2-4 hours (edibles)</li>\n<li><strong>Duration:</strong> 2-4 hours (inhaled) or 6-12 hours (edibles)</li>\n</ul>\n<p><strong>⚠️ Important:</strong> Hash is significantly more potent than regular flower. Start with minimal amounts and wait to assess effects before consuming more. for experienced users – beginners should start with lower doses or those new to concentrates.</p>\n</div>\n</div>",
