        "shortDescription": "Ice Cream LA Mousse Hash blends dessert-smooth flavour with balanced indica relaxation in a premium, solventless concentrate. To start, this indica-dominant hybrid (60% indica / 40% sativa) comes fr...",
        "descriptionHTML": "<div class=\"tab-pane active\" id=\"tab-description\">\n<div class=\"detail-tab-desc detail-content-wrap\">\n<p data-end=\"852\" data-start=\"485\"><strong data-end=\"513\" data-start=\"485\">Ice Cream LA Mousse Hash</strong> blends <strong data-end=\"547\" data-start=\"521\">dessert-smooth flavour</strong> with <strong data-end=\"583\" data-start=\"553\">balanced indica relaxation</strong> in a premium, solventless concentrate. To start, this indica-dominant hybrid (60% indica / 40% sativa) comes from Paradise Seeds genetics, known for consistency, quality, and rich terpene expression. Because of this, every session feels smooth, calming, and indulgent.</p>\n<p data-end=\"1202\" data-start=\"854\">Right from the first hit, the effects spread evenly through both mind and body 🧠💆‍♂️. First, a gentle wave of euphoria lifts the mood and softens stress. Soon after, a calming body buzz settles in, easing tension without hitting too hard. As the experience continues, relaxation deepens, making it easy to unwind, slow down, and enjoy the moment.</p>\n<p data-end=\"1472\" data-start=\"1204\">Meanwhile, the flavour truly shines 🍨✨. Each pull delivers <strong data-end=\"1292\" data-start=\"1264\">creamy vanilla sweetness</strong>, layered with <strong data-end=\"1324\" data-start=\"1307\">honeyed notes</strong> and a <strong data-end=\"1347\" data-start=\"1331\">nutty finish</strong>. Altogether, it tastes just like smooth, melting ice cream, leaving a soft, dessert-like aftertaste that lingers pleasantly.</p>\n<p data-end=\"1792\" data-start=\"1474\">Because this is <strong data-end=\"1508\" data-start=\"1490\">LA Mousse Hash</strong>, the texture stays <strong data-end=\"1566\" data-start=\"1528\">light, airy, and easy to work with</strong>. As a result, it crumbles effortlessly, melts cleanly, and burns smoothly. Whether you sprinkle it into a bowl, roll it into a joint, or press it gently, Ice Cream LA Mousse delivers consistent flavour and potency every time.</p>\n<hr data-end=\"1797\" data-start=\"1794\"/>\n<h3 data-end=\"1824\" data-start=\"1799\">✨ Effects You’ll Feel</h3>\n<ul data-end=\"1949\" data-start=\"1825\">\n<li data-end=\"1850\" data-start=\"1825\">\n<p data-end=\"1850\" data-start=\"1827\">😊 Euphoric and happy</p>\n</li>\n<li data-end=\"1873\" data-start=\"1851\">\n<p data-end=\"1873\" data-start=\"1853\">😌 Deep relaxation</p>\n</li>\n<li data-end=\"1904\" data-start=\"1874\">\n<p data-end=\"1904\" data-start=\"1876\">🛋️ Calm, mellow body high</p>\n</li>\n<li data-end=\"1949\" data-start=\"1905\">\n<p data-end=\"1949\" data-start=\"1907\">🌙 Slightly sleepy, perfect for evenings</p>\n</li>\n</ul>\n<hr data-end=\"1954\" data-start=\"1951\"/>\n<h3 data-end=\"1982\" data-start=\"1956\">🩺 Commonly Chosen For</h3>\n<ul data-end=\"2087\" data-start=\"1983\">\n<li data-end=\"2003\" data-start=\"1983\">\n<p data-end=\"2003\" data-start=\"1985\">Stress &amp; anxiety</p>\n</li>\n<li data-end=\"2032\" data-start=\"2004\">\n<p data-end=\"2032\" data-start=\"2006\">Chronic pain &amp; arthritis</p>\n</li>\n<li data-end=\"2047\" data-start=\"2033\">\n<p data-end=\"2047\" data-start=\"2035\">Depression</p>\n</li>\n<li data-end=\"2060\" data-start=\"2048\">\n<p data-end=\"2060\" data-start=\"2050\">Insomnia</p>\n</li>\n<li data-end=\"2087\" data-start=\"2061\">\n<p data-end=\"2087\" data-start=\"2063\">Nausea &amp; appetite loss</p>\n</li>\n</ul>\n<hr data-end=\"2092\" data-start=\"2089\"/>\n<h3 data-end=\"2114\" data-start=\"2094\">🍬 Flavour Notes</h3>\n<ul data-end=\"2196\" data-start=\"2115\">\n<li data-end=\"2133\" data-start=\"2115\">\n<p data-end=\"2133\" data-start=\"2117\">Creamy vanilla</p>\n</li>\n<li data-end=\"2149\" data-start=\"2134\">\n<p data-end=\"2149\" data-start=\"2136\">Sweet honey</p>\n</li>\n<li data-end=\"2170\" data-start=\"2150\">\n<p data-end=\"2170\" data-start=\"2152\">Nutty undertones</p>\n</li>\n<li data-end=\"2196\" data-start=\"2171\">\n<p data-end=\"2196\" data-start=\"2173\">Smooth dessert finish</p>\n</li>\n</ul>\n<hr data-end=\"2201\" data-start=\"2198\"/>\n<h3 data-end=\"2224\" data-start=\"2203\">🌬️ Aroma Profile</h3>\n<ul data-end=\"2288\" data-start=\"2225\">\n<li data-end=\"2245\" data-start=\"2225\">\n<p data-end=\"2245\" data-start=\"2227\">Sweet &amp; fragrant</p>\n</li>\n<li data-end=\"2265\" data-start=\"2246\">\n<p data-end=\"2265\" data-start=\"2248\">Vanilla forward</p>\n</li>\n<li data-end=\"2288\" data-start=\"2266\">\n<p data-end=\"2288\" data-start=\"2268\">Soft, creamy notes</p>\n</li>\n</ul>\n<hr data-end=\"2293\" data-start=\"2290\"/>\n<h3 data-end=\"2341\" data-start=\"2295\">💎 Why Ice Cream LA Mousse Hash Stands Out</h3>\n<ul data-end=\"2533\" data-start=\"2342\">\n<li data-end=\"2376\" data-start=\"2342\">\n<p data-end=\"2376\" data-start=\"2344\">Premium <strong data-end=\"2376\" data-start=\"2352\">solventless dry sift</strong></p>\n</li>\n<li data-end=\"2418\" data-start=\"2377\">\n<p data-end=\"2418\" data-start=\"2379\">Light, aerated <strong data-end=\"2418\" data-start=\"2394\">French Touch texture</strong></p>\n</li>\n<li data-end=\"2450\" data-start=\"2419\">\n<p data-end=\"2450\" data-start=\"2421\">Smooth, dessert-style flavour</p>\n</li>\n<li data-end=\"2481\" data-start=\"2451\">\n<p data-end=\"2481\" data-start=\"2453\">Balanced <strong data-end=\"2481\" data-start=\"2462\">19% THC potency</strong></p>\n</li>\n<li data-end=\"2533\" data-start=\"2482\">\n<p data-end=\"2533\" data-start=\"2484\">Ideal for relaxed evenings and wind-down sessions</p>\n</li>\n</ul>\n<hr/>\n<h2>💡 Usage Guide</h2>\n<h3>Recommended Dosage</h3>\n<ul>\n<li><strong>Beginners:</strong> Start with a rice grain-sized piece (approximately 0.025-0.05g). Hash is significantly more potent than flower.</li>\n<li><strong>Experienced Users:</strong> 0.1-0.2g per session, adjusting based on tolerance and desired effects.</li>\n<li><strong>High Tolerance:</strong> Up to 0.3g per session for seasoned concentrate consumers.</li>\n</ul>\n<h3>Consumption Methods</h3>\n<ul>\n<li><strong>Smoking:</strong> Crumble and mix with flower in joints, pipes, or bongs for enhanced potency and traditional experience.</li>\n<li><strong>Vaporizing:</strong> Use hash-compatible vaporizer at 180-210°C for smooth, flavourful vapour with maximum terpene preservation.</li>\n<li><strong>Hot Knives:</strong> Traditional method heating two knives and pressing hash between them for immediate effects.</li>\n<li><strong>Topping Bowls:</strong> Add small pieces atop flower bowls for elevated potency without altering your regular routine.</li>\n<li><strong>Hash Edibles (Advanced):</strong> To make edibles, decarboxylate hash at 110-120°C (230-250°F) for 30-40 minutes to activate THC. Mix into butter or oil-based recipes. Effects take 30-120 minutes and last 6-12 hours. Hash edibles are significantly more potent than flower edibles—start with 1/4 of your normal flower edible dose.</li>\n</ul>\n<h3>Onset &amp; Duration</h3>\n<ul>\n<li><strong>Onset (Smoking/Vaping):</strong> 2-10 minutes</li>\n<li><strong>Onset (Edibles):</strong> 30-120 minutes</li>\n<li><strong>Peak Effects:</strong> 15-45 minutes (inhaled) or 2-4 hours (edibles)</li>\n<li><strong>Duration:</strong> 2-4 hours (inhaled) or 6-12 hours (edibles)</li>\n</ul>\n<p><strong>⚠️ Important:</strong> Hash is significantly more potent than regular flower. Start with minimal amounts and wait to assess effects before consuming more. for experienced users – beginners should start with lower doses or those new to concentrates.</p>\n</div>\n</div>",
