        "descriptionHTML": "<div class=\"tab-pane active\" id=\"tab-description\">\n<div class=\"detail-tab-desc detail-content-wrap\">\n<p>**Buy Cactus Labs 5D Blend THC Gummies online in Canada at Mohawk Medibles**, your trusted Indigenous-owned cannabis dispensary. Shop these premium 3000mg multi-cannabinoid edibles and experience the synergistic power of five delta compounds in one revolutionary gummy. Order now for fast Canada-wide shipping with same-day processing and discreet delivery. Perfect for experienced consumers seeking next-level effects and unmatched potency.</p>\n<p>–</p>\n<h2>💡 Usage Guide</h2>\n<h3>Recommended Dosage</h3>\n<ul>\n<li><strong>Experienced Users Only:</strong> Start with half a gummy (approximately 50mg total cannabinoids) and wait 90-120 minutes before considering more</li>\n<li><strong>High Tolerance Consumers:</strong> One full gummy (approximately 100mg total cannabinoids) per session</li>\n<li><strong>Important:</strong> These are ultra-potent gummies combining five cannabinoids. Do NOT use if you are new to edibles or have low THC tolerance</li>\n</ul>\n<h3>Consumption Tips</h3>\n<ul>\n<li><strong>Start Low, Go Slow:</strong> The 5D blend creates unique synergistic effects that may be stronger than traditional edibles at similar doses</li>\n<li><strong>Take with Food:</strong> Consume with a light meal to improve absorption and reduce potential nausea</li>\n<li><strong>Stay Hydrated:</strong> Keep water nearby throughout your experience</li>\n<li><strong>Plan Ahead:</strong> Clear your schedule for 6-10 hours; the multi-cannabinoid blend may produce longer-lasting effects</li>\n<li><strong>Safe Environment:</strong> Use in a comfortable, familiar setting where you can relax completely</li>\n</ul>\n<h3>Onset &amp; Duration</h3>\n<ul>\n<li><strong>Onset:</strong> 45-120 minutes (the blend of cannabinoids may create staggered onset effects)</li>\n<li><strong>Peak Effects:</strong> 2-4 hours after consumption</li>\n<li><strong>Duration:</strong> 6-10 hours total (longer than standard edibles due to multiple cannabinoid profiles)</li>\n</ul>\n<h3>Best Use Cases</h3>\n<p>Ideal for experienced consumers seeking profound, long-lasting effects for deep relaxation, creative exploration, or extended relief. Best reserved for days off, evening use, or special occasions. The unique 5D blend offers a multi-layered experience that evolves throughout the duration. Not suitable for work, driving, or situations requiring focus and coordination.</p>\n<p><strong>⚠️ Important Safety Notice:</strong> These gummies contain extremely high potency levels across five different cannabinoids. Only for experienced cannabis consumers with established tolerance. Do not operate vehicles or machinery. Keep out of reach of children and pets. Start with the lowest possible dose and wait at least 2 hours before consuming more.</p>\n<h2>❓ Frequently Asked Questions</h2>\n<h3>What makes the 5D Blend different from regular THC gummies?</h3>\n<p><strong>A:</strong> Cactus Labs 5D Blend combines five distinct delta cannabinoids (Delta-6, Delta-8, Delta-9, Delta-10, and Delta-11) in one gummy, creating an entourage effect that’s more complex and potentially more potent than single-cannabinoid edibles. Each delta compound interacts with your endocannabinoid system differently, producing layered, evolving effects throughout the experience.</p>\n<h3>How many gummies come in the 3000mg package?</h3>\n<p><strong>A:</strong> Each package contains multiple gummies with a total of 3000mg of combined cannabinoids. The exact count depends on the per-gummy dosage, but each piece is precisely dosed for consistent effects. Always check the package label for specific gummy count and individual serving size.</p>\n<h3>Are Cactus Labs 5D Blend Gummies safe for beginners?</h3>\n<p><strong>A:</strong> No, these gummies are formulated for experienced cannabis consumers only. The high potency and multi-cannabinoid blend create intense effects that can be overwhelming for those new to edibles or with low THC tolerance. Beginners should start with traditional 5-10mg THC edibles before considering products like the 5D Blend.</p>\n<h3>How long do Cactus Labs 5D Blend Gummies take to work?</h3>\n<p><strong>A:</strong> Onset typically occurs within 45-120 minutes, though this varies based on metabolism, body weight, and whether you’ve eaten recently. The multi-cannabinoid formula may create staggered onset, with different effects emerging at different times. Always wait at least 2 hours before consuming more.</p>\n<h3>How should I store my 5D Blend Gummies?</h3>\n<p><strong>A:</strong> Store in a cool, dry place away from direct sunlight and heat. Keep sealed in the original child-resistant packaging to maintain freshness and potency. Refrigeration can extend shelf life, especially in warm climates. Always store securely out of reach of children and pets.</p>\n<h3>Does Mohawk Medibles ship Cactus Labs 5D Blend Gummies across Canada?</h3>\n<p><strong>A:</strong> Yes! We offer fast, discreet Canada-wide shipping on all Cactus Labs products. Orders placed before 2 PM EST are processed the same day. All packages arrive in plain, unmarked packaging with no indication of contents, ensuring complete privacy and discretion.</p>\n<h3>Can I take 5D Blend Gummies with other cannabis products?</h3>\n<p><strong>A:</strong> Exercise extreme caution when combining these gummies with other cannabis products. The 5D Blend is already highly potent, and adding flower, vapes, or other edibles can lead to uncomfortably intense effects. If you do combine products, use minimal amounts and allow full onset time to assess effects before consuming more.</p>\n</div>\n</div>",
