        "descriptionHTML": "<div class=\"tab-pane active\" id=\"tab-description\">\n<div class=\"detail-tab-desc detail-content-wrap\">\n<p>**Buy Drizzle Factory Slims Live Resin Infused Pre-Rolls online in Canada at Mohawk Medibles**, your trusted Indigenous-owned cannabis dispensary. Shop these premium infused pre-rolls featuring authentic live resin for enhanced potency and flavour, and enjoy fast Canada-wide shipping with same-day processing. Order now for discreet delivery straight from Tyendinaga Mohawk Territory. Each pack contains 10 convenient 0.7g pre-rolls (7g total) – perfect for sharing or enjoying throughout the week.</p>\n<p>–</p>\n<h2>💡 Usage Guide</h2>\n<h3>Recommended Dosage</h3>\n<ul>\n<li><strong>Beginners:</strong> Start with 2-3 small puffs and wait 10-15 minutes to assess effects. Live resin infusion increases potency significantly.</li>\n<li><strong>Experienced Users:</strong> Enjoy half to a full pre-roll per session, depending on tolerance and desired effects.</li>\n<li><strong>High Tolerance:</strong> One full pre-roll (0.7g) or more as needed. These infused pre-rolls deliver elevated potency compared to standard flower.</li>\n</ul>\n<h3>Consumption Tips</h3>\n<ul>\n<li><strong>Light Evenly:</strong> Rotate the pre-roll while lighting to ensure an even burn and optimal flavour release.</li>\n<li><strong>Pace Yourself:</strong> Live resin infusion means higher THC content – take your time between puffs.</li>\n<li><strong>Store Properly:</strong> Keep remaining pre-rolls in original packaging in a cool, dry place to maintain freshness.</li>\n<li><strong>Use a Filter:</strong> Pre-rolls come ready to smoke with built-in filters for smooth, comfortable draws.</li>\n</ul>\n<h3>Onset &amp; Duration</h3>\n<ul>\n<li><strong>Onset:</strong> 2-10 minutes after first inhalation</li>\n<li><strong>Peak Effects:</strong> 30-60 minutes after consumption</li>\n<li><strong>Duration:</strong> 2-4 hours depending on amount consumed and individual tolerance</li>\n</ul>\n<h3>Best Use Cases</h3>\n<p>Drizzle Factory Slims are perfect for convenient, no-preparation cannabis enjoyment. Ideal for social gatherings, outdoor adventures, or relaxing evenings at home. The live resin infusion provides enhanced flavour and potency, making these pre-rolls excellent for experienced consumers seeking premium quality without the hassle of rolling. The slim format offers a refined smoking experience with consistent burn and smooth draw.</p>\n<h2>❓ Frequently Asked Questions</h2>\n<h3>What makes Drizzle Factory Slims different from regular pre-rolls?</h3>\n<p><strong>A:</strong> Drizzle Factory Slims are infused with live resin, a premium cannabis concentrate that preserves the plant’s full terpene profile. This infusion significantly enhances both potency and flavour compared to standard flower-only pre-rolls, delivering a more robust and aromatic smoking experience.</p>\n<h3>How many pre-rolls come in each pack?</h3>\n<p><strong>A:</strong> Each pack contains 10 pre-rolls at 0.7g each, for a total of 7 grams. This convenient format is perfect for sharing with friends or enjoying multiple sessions throughout the week without needing to re-order frequently.</p>\n<h3>Are these pre-rolls suitable for beginners?</h3>\n<p><strong>A:</strong> Due to the live resin infusion, these pre-rolls are more potent than standard flower. Beginners should start with just 2-3 small puffs and wait 15 minutes to assess effects before consuming more. Experienced consumers will appreciate the elevated potency and rich flavour profile.</p>\n<h3>How should I store Drizzle Factory Slims to maintain freshness?</h3>\n<p><strong>A:</strong> Keep your pre-rolls in their original packaging and store in a cool, dry place away from direct sunlight and heat. Avoid humid environments to prevent the paper from becoming damp. Properly stored, these pre-rolls will maintain their quality and potency for several months.</p>\n<h3>Does Mohawk Medibles ship Drizzle Factory Slims across Canada?</h3>\n<p><strong>A:</strong> Yes! We offer fast, discreet Canada-wide shipping on all our products, including Drizzle Factory Slims. Orders placed before 2 PM EST are processed the same day. All packages arrive in plain, unmarked packaging to ensure your privacy and discretion.</p>\n<h3>What’s the benefit of live resin infusion?</h3>\n<p><strong>A:</strong> Live resin is extracted from fresh-frozen cannabis plants, preserving the full spectrum of terpenes and cannabinoids that are often lost in traditional drying and curing. This results in superior flavour, aroma, and entourage effects, making each puff more flavourful and potent than standard pre-rolls.</p>\n<h3>Can I take these pre-rolls on the go?</h3>\n<p><strong>A:</strong> Absolutely! The slim format and sturdy packaging make Drizzle Factory Slims perfect for portable use. Whether you’re heading to a concert, camping trip, or friend’s house, these pre-rolls travel well. Always consume responsibly and follow local cannabis consumption laws regarding public use.</p>\n</div>\n</div>",
