        "descriptionHTML": "<div class=\"tab-pane active\" id=\"tab-description\">\n<div class=\"detail-tab-desc detail-content-wrap\">\n<h2 data-end=\"227\" data-start=\"185\">🕌 <strong data-end=\"225\" data-start=\"190\">Pakistan Hash – $6/Gram Special</strong></h2>\n<p data-end=\"288\" data-start=\"228\"><strong data-end=\"288\" data-start=\"228\">100% Pure Indica • Traditional Landrace • Potent + Heavy</strong></p>\n<hr/>\n<p data-end=\"937\" data-start=\"717\">Pakistan Hash is crafted from <strong data-end=\"788\" data-start=\"747\">pure Pakistani Indica landrace plants</strong>, grown in the rugged hills and mountains of Pakistan—a region known worldwide for producing some of the <strong data-end=\"936\" data-start=\"893\">richest and strongest hash in the world</strong>.</p>\n<p data-end=\"1228\" data-start=\"939\"><strong data-end=\"954\" data-start=\"939\">Right away,</strong> the aroma captures your attention: bold, hashy, earthy, and slightly sour, with herbal and berry notes rising through the spice.<br data-end=\"1086\" data-start=\"1083\"/><strong data-end=\"1112\" data-start=\"1086\">As you break it apart,</strong> the scent grows deeper, filling the air with that classic old-world hash smell that experienced smokers appreciate.</p>\n<p data-end=\"1540\" data-start=\"1230\"><strong data-end=\"1243\" data-start=\"1230\">Once lit,</strong> the flavour becomes smooth and full—sweet earth, sour citrus, and warm herbal tones blending together for a rich, satisfying smoke.<br data-end=\"1378\" data-start=\"1375\"/><strong data-end=\"1406\" data-start=\"1378\">After your first inhale,</strong> the heavy Indica effects begin to creep in. A slow wave of calm spreads through your body, easing stress and loosening tight muscles.</p>\n<p data-end=\"1823\" data-start=\"1542\"><strong data-end=\"1577\" data-start=\"1542\">As the high continues to build,</strong> expect a powerful sedation that melts away tension and quiets your mind. With <strong data-end=\"1670\" data-start=\"1656\">24–26% THC</strong>, Pakistan Hash is strong enough to flatten even seasoned users if taken in large amounts—ideal for nighttime sessions, deep relaxation, and pain relief.</p>\n<p data-end=\"1984\" data-start=\"1825\">This hash is perfect for anyone who wants that <strong data-end=\"1915\" data-start=\"1872\">traditional South Asian hash experience</strong> with strong effects, smooth flavour, and a deep, peaceful body high.</p>\n<hr data-end=\"1989\" data-start=\"1986\"/>\n<h3 data-end=\"2009\" data-start=\"1991\">🔥 <strong data-end=\"2007\" data-start=\"1996\">EFFECTS</strong></h3>\n<ul data-end=\"2131\" data-start=\"2010\">\n<li data-end=\"2030\" data-start=\"2010\">\n<p data-end=\"2030\" data-start=\"2012\">Heavy relaxation</p>\n</li>\n<li data-end=\"2049\" data-start=\"2031\">\n<p data-end=\"2049\" data-start=\"2033\">Deep body calm</p>\n</li>\n<li data-end=\"2062\" data-start=\"2050\">\n<p data-end=\"2062\" data-start=\"2052\">Sedating</p>\n</li>\n<li data-end=\"2081\" data-start=\"2063\">\n<p data-end=\"2081\" data-start=\"2065\">Euphoric waves</p>\n</li>\n<li data-end=\"2103\" data-start=\"2082\">\n<p data-end=\"2103\" data-start=\"2084\">Full mental quiet</p>\n</li>\n<li data-end=\"2131\" data-start=\"2104\">\n<p data-end=\"2131\" data-start=\"2106\">Strong nighttime unwind</p>\n</li>\n</ul>\n<hr data-end=\"2136\" data-start=\"2133\"/>\n<h3 data-end=\"2162\" data-start=\"2138\">🌿 <strong data-end=\"2160\" data-start=\"2143\">MAY HELP WITH</strong></h3>\n<ul data-end=\"2262\" data-start=\"2163\">\n<li data-end=\"2179\" data-start=\"2163\">\n<p data-end=\"2179\" data-start=\"2165\">Chronic pain</p>\n</li>\n<li data-end=\"2192\" data-start=\"2180\">\n<p data-end=\"2192\" data-start=\"2182\">Insomnia</p>\n</li>\n<li data-end=\"2203\" data-start=\"2193\">\n<p data-end=\"2203\" data-start=\"2195\">Stress</p>\n</li>\n<li data-end=\"2218\" data-start=\"2204\">\n<p data-end=\"2218\" data-start=\"2206\">Depression</p>\n</li>\n<li data-end=\"2245\" data-start=\"2219\">\n<p data-end=\"2245\" data-start=\"2221\">Muscle spasms / cramps</p>\n</li>\n<li data-end=\"2262\" data-start=\"2246\">\n<p data-end=\"2262\" data-start=\"2248\">Inflammation</p>\n</li>\n</ul>\n<hr data-end=\"2267\" data-start=\"2264\"/>\n<h3 data-end=\"2287\" data-start=\"2269\">🕌 <strong data-end=\"2285\" data-start=\"2274\">FLAVORS</strong></h3>\n<ul data-end=\"2346\" data-start=\"2288\">\n<li data-end=\"2303\" data-start=\"2288\">\n<p data-end=\"2303\" data-start=\"2290\">Sweet earth</p>\n</li>\n<li data-end=\"2319\" data-start=\"2304\">\n<p data-end=\"2319\" data-start=\"2306\">Sour citrus</p>\n</li>\n<li data-end=\"2330\" data-start=\"2320\">\n<p data-end=\"2330\" data-start=\"2322\">Herbal</p>\n</li>\n<li data-end=\"2346\" data-start=\"2331\">\n<p data-end=\"2346\" data-start=\"2333\">Hashy spice</p>\n</li>\n</ul>\n<hr data-end=\"2351\" data-start=\"2348\"/>\n<h3 data-end=\"2371\" data-start=\"2353\">🌬️ <strong data-end=\"2369\" data-start=\"2359\">AROMAS</strong></h3>\n<ul data-end=\"2449\" data-start=\"2372\">\n<li data-end=\"2388\" data-start=\"2372\">\n<p data-end=\"2388\" data-start=\"2374\">Pungent hash</p>\n</li>\n<li data-end=\"2399\" data-start=\"2389\">\n<p data-end=\"2399\" data-start=\"2391\">Earthy</p>\n</li>\n<li data-end=\"2421\" data-start=\"2400\">\n<p data-end=\"2421\" data-start=\"2402\">Sour herbal berry</p>\n</li>\n<li data-end=\"2449\" data-start=\"2422\">\n<p data-end=\"2449\" data-start=\"2424\">Classic Pakistani scent</p>\n</li>\n</ul>\n<hr/>\n<h2>💡 Usage Guide</h2>\n<h3>Recommended Dosage</h3>\n<ul>\n<li><strong>Beginners:</strong> Start with a rice grain-sized piece (approximately 0.025-0.05g). Hash is significantly more potent than flower.</li>\n<li><strong>Experienced Users:</strong> 0.1-0.2g per session, adjusting based on tolerance and desired effects.</li>\n<li><strong>High Tolerance:</strong> Up to 0.3g per session for seasoned concentrate consumers.</li>\n</ul>\n<h3>Consumption Methods</h3>\n<ul>\n<li><strong>Smoking:</strong> Crumble and mix with flower in joints, pipes, or bongs for enhanced potency and traditional experience.</li>\n<li><strong>Vaporizing:</strong> Use hash-compatible vaporizer at 180-210°C for smooth, flavourful vapour with maximum terpene preservation.</li>\n<li><strong>Hot Knives:</strong> Traditional method heating two knives and pressing hash between them for immediate effects.</li>\n<li><strong>Topping Bowls:</strong> Add small pieces atop flower bowls for elevated potency without altering your regular routine.</li>\n<li><strong>Hash Edibles (Advanced):</strong> To make edibles, decarboxylate hash at 110-120°C (230-250°F) for 30-40 minutes to activate THC. Mix into butter or oil-based recipes. Effects take 30-120 minutes and last 6-12 hours. Hash edibles are significantly more potent than flower edibles—start with 1/4 of your normal flower edible dose.</li>\n</ul>\n<h3>Onset &amp; Duration</h3>\n<ul>\n<li><strong>Onset (Smoking/Vaping):</strong> 2-10 minutes</li>\n<li><strong>Onset (Edibles):</strong> 30-120 minutes</li>\n<li><strong>Peak Effects:</strong> 15-45 minutes (inhaled) or 2-4 hours (edibles)</li>\n<li><strong>Duration:</strong> 2-4 hours (inhaled) or 6-12 hours (edibles)</li>\n</ul>\n<p><strong>⚠️ Important:</strong> Hash is significantly more potent than regular flower. Start with minimal amounts and wait to assess effects before consuming more. for experienced users – beginners should start with lower doses or those new to concentrates.</p>\n</div>\n</div>",
