        "descriptionHTML": "<div class=\"tab-pane active\" id=\"tab-description\">\n<div class=\"detail-tab-desc detail-content-wrap\">\n<h3 data-end=\"698\" data-start=\"639\"><strong data-end=\"698\" data-start=\"643\">DC OG Magic Mushroom | Deep Calm &amp; Organic Goodness</strong></h3>\n<p data-end=\"1036\" data-start=\"700\"><strong data-end=\"747\" data-start=\"700\">Experience grounded tranquility with DC OG.</strong><br data-end=\"750\" data-start=\"747\"/>DC OG Magic Mushroom is a premium <em data-end=\"804\" data-start=\"784\">Psilocybe Cubensis</em> strain celebrated for its mellow yet mentally enriching effects. With its earthy aroma, thick stems, and medium-sized caps, this strain is ideal for users looking for a more relaxed psychedelic journey without overwhelming visuals.</p>\n<p data-end=\"1266\" data-start=\"1038\">Crafted for those seeking calm introspection, DC OG is a go-to strain for stress relief, emotional reset, and peaceful meditations. Whether you’re new to psilocybin or prefer a smooth ride, this strain delivers reliable results.</p>\n<hr class=\"\" data-end=\"1271\" data-start=\"1268\"/>\n<h3 data-end=\"1295\" data-start=\"1273\">🔍 <strong data-end=\"1295\" data-start=\"1280\">Highlights:</strong></h3>\n<ul data-end=\"1708\" data-start=\"1297\">\n<li data-end=\"1341\" data-start=\"1297\">\n<p data-end=\"1341\" data-start=\"1299\"><strong data-end=\"1310\" data-start=\"1299\">Strain:</strong> DC OG (<em data-end=\"1338\" data-start=\"1318\">Psilocybe Cubensis</em>)</p>\n</li>\n<li data-end=\"1413\" data-start=\"1342\">\n<p data-end=\"1413\" data-start=\"1344\"><strong data-end=\"1356\" data-start=\"1344\">Potency:</strong> Moderate – Ideal for beginners or relaxing experiences</p>\n</li>\n<li data-end=\"1486\" data-start=\"1414\">\n<p data-end=\"1486\" data-start=\"1416\"><strong data-end=\"1428\" data-start=\"1416\">Effects:</strong> Calm, clear-headed, introspective, and lightly euphoric</p>\n</li>\n<li data-end=\"1553\" data-start=\"1487\">\n<p data-end=\"1553\" data-start=\"1489\"><strong data-end=\"1504\" data-start=\"1489\">Appearance:</strong> Earth-toned caps, firm stems, minimal bruising</p>\n</li>\n<li data-end=\"1631\" data-start=\"1554\">\n<p data-end=\"1631\" data-start=\"1556\"><strong data-end=\"1576\" data-start=\"1556\">Recommended Use:</strong> Stress relief, evening meditations, mood enhancement</p>\n</li>\n<li data-end=\"1708\" data-start=\"1632\">\n<p data-end=\"1708\" data-start=\"1634\"><strong data-end=\"1646\" data-start=\"1634\">Storage:</strong> Keep in a cool, dry place, sealed away from direct sunlight</p>\n</li>\n</ul>\n<hr class=\"\" data-end=\"1713\" data-start=\"1710\"/>\n<h3 data-end=\"1743\" data-start=\"1715\">🌿 <strong data-end=\"1743\" data-start=\"1722\">Why Choose DC OG?</strong></h3>\n<ul data-end=\"1959\" data-start=\"1745\">\n<li data-end=\"1786\" data-start=\"1745\">\n<p data-end=\"1786\" data-start=\"1747\">Milder trip with therapeutic benefits</p>\n</li>\n<li data-end=\"1837\" data-start=\"1787\">\n<p data-end=\"1837\" data-start=\"1789\">Grown organically with zero chemical additives</p>\n</li>\n<li data-end=\"1891\" data-start=\"1838\">\n<p data-end=\"1891\" data-start=\"1840\">Ideal for microdosing or full-session exploration</p>\n</li>\n<li data-end=\"1959\" data-start=\"1892\">\n<p data-end=\"1959\" data-start=\"1894\">Perfect for mindful evenings, journaling, or light nature walks</p>\n</li>\n</ul>\n<hr class=\"\" data-end=\"1964\" data-start=\"1961\"/>\n<h3 data-end=\"1988\" data-start=\"1966\">⚠️ <strong data-end=\"1988\" data-start=\"1973\">Disclaimer:</strong></h3>\n<p data-end=\"2141\" data-start=\"1989\">For educational and spiritual use only. Must be 19+. Not intended to treat or diagnose medical conditions. Follow local laws and regulations before use.</p>\n</div>\n</div>",
