        "descriptionHTML": "<div class=\"tab-pane active\" id=\"tab-description\">\n<div class=\"detail-tab-desc detail-content-wrap\">\n<p>**Buy Stoned Leaf Gummies 3:1 CBD/THC online in Canada at Mohawk Medibles**, your trusted Indigenous-owned cannabis dispensary. Shop these perfectly balanced CBD-dominant gummies and enjoy fast Canada-wide shipping with same-day processing. Order now for discreet delivery and experience the therapeutic benefits of this carefully crafted 3:1 CBD to THC ratio, ideal for wellness-focused consumers seeking gentle relief without overwhelming psychoactive effects.</p>\n<p>–</p>\n<h2>💡 Usage Guide</h2>\n<h3>Recommended Dosage</h3>\n<ul>\n<li><strong>Beginners:</strong> Start with one half gummy (containing approximately 7.5mg CBD / 2.5mg THC) and wait at least 2 hours before consuming more</li>\n<li><strong>Experienced Users:</strong> One full gummy (15mg CBD / 5mg THC) provides balanced effects suitable for daily wellness</li>\n<li><strong>High Tolerance/Medical Users:</strong> 1-2 gummies as needed, not exceeding 3 gummies in a 24-hour period without healthcare provider guidance</li>\n</ul>\n<h3>Consumption Tips</h3>\n<ul>\n<li><strong>Start Low, Go Slow:</strong> The 3:1 CBD/THC ratio offers mild psychoactive effects, but edibles can take 30-120 minutes to take effect</li>\n<li><strong>Take with Food:</strong> Consuming with a light meal or snack can improve absorption and reduce potential stomach sensitivity</li>\n<li><strong>Stay Hydrated:</strong> Drink water throughout your experience to enhance comfort and well-being</li>\n<li><strong>Plan Accordingly:</strong> Effects typically last 4-6 hours; ensure you have no driving or important obligations</li>\n</ul>\n<h3>Onset &amp; Duration</h3>\n<ul>\n<li><strong>Onset:</strong> 30-90 minutes (varies by metabolism and whether taken with food)</li>\n<li><strong>Peak Effects:</strong> 2-3 hours after consumption</li>\n<li><strong>Duration:</strong> 4-6 hours total, with gentle tapering</li>\n</ul>\n<h3>Best Use Cases</h3>\n<p>Perfect for daytime wellness support, managing mild discomfort, reducing stress, and promoting relaxation without heavy sedation. The CBD-dominant formula makes these gummies ideal for consumers seeking therapeutic benefits with minimal intoxication. Suitable for work-from-home days, creative activities, light social gatherings, or evening relaxation. The balanced ratio provides the entourage effect while keeping you functional and clear-headed.</p>\n<h2>❓ Frequently Asked Questions</h2>\n<h3>What is the CBD to THC ratio in Stoned Leaf Gummies?</h3>\n<p><strong>A:</strong> Stoned Leaf Gummies feature a 3:1 CBD to THC ratio, meaning each gummy contains three times more CBD than THC. This balanced formulation provides therapeutic benefits with mild, manageable psychoactive effects, making them ideal for wellness-focused consumers or those new to cannabis edibles.</p>\n<h3>Will Stoned Leaf 3:1 CBD/THC Gummies make me high?</h3>\n<p><strong>A:</strong> These gummies produce mild, gentle psychoactive effects due to the THC content, but the higher CBD ratio helps modulate and soften the experience. Most users report feeling relaxed and calm rather than intensely intoxicated. The effects are significantly milder than THC-dominant edibles, making them suitable for daytime use and functional activities.</p>\n<h3>How long do Stoned Leaf Gummies take to work?</h3>\n<p><strong>A:</strong> Like all edibles, Stoned Leaf Gummies typically take 30-90 minutes to take effect, depending on your metabolism, body weight, and whether you’ve eaten recently. Effects peak around 2-3 hours after consumption and can last 4-6 hours total. Always wait at least 2 hours before consuming additional gummies.</p>\n<h3>Are these gummies suitable for beginners?</h3>\n<p><strong>A:</strong> Yes! The 3:1 CBD/THC ratio makes these gummies an excellent choice for beginners or cannabis-curious consumers. Start with half a gummy to assess your tolerance, and wait at least 2 hours before consuming more. The CBD content helps create a smoother, more comfortable experience compared to THC-only edibles.</p>\n<h3>What are the benefits of a 3:1 CBD/THC ratio?</h3>\n<p><strong>A:</strong> The 3:1 ratio provides the therapeutic benefits of CBD (relaxation, comfort, stress relief) enhanced by the entourage effect of THC, without overwhelming psychoactive effects. This combination is ideal for managing everyday stress, mild discomfort, and promoting overall wellness while remaining functional and clear-headed.</p>\n<h3>How should I store Stoned Leaf Gummies?</h3>\n<p><strong>A:</strong> Store your gummies in their original packaging in a cool, dry place away from direct sunlight and heat. Refrigeration can extend freshness and prevent gummies from sticking together in warm weather. Always keep out of reach of children and pets. Properly stored, gummies maintain potency and quality for 6-12 months.</p>\n<h3>Does Mohawk Medibles ship Stoned Leaf Gummies across Canada?</h3>\n<p><strong>A:</strong> Yes! We offer fast, discreet Canada-wide shipping on all Stoned Leaf products. Orders placed before 2 PM EST are processed the same day. All packages arrive in plain, unmarked packaging to ensure privacy. Track your order from our Tyendinaga Mohawk Territory facility directly to your door.</p>\n</div>\n</div>",
