        "descriptionHTML": "<div class=\"tab-pane active\" id=\"tab-description\">\n<div class=\"detail-tab-desc detail-content-wrap\">\n<p>**Buy Drizzle Factory Shatter 1 Gram online in Canada at Mohawk Medibles**, your trusted Indigenous-owned cannabis dispensary. Shop this premium cannabis concentrate and enjoy fast Canada-wide shipping with same-day processing on orders placed before 2 PM EST. Order now for discreet delivery of this high-potency shatter, expertly crafted by Drizzle Factory for an ultra-smooth dabbing experience. Experience the quality and potency that has made Drizzle Factory a go-to choice for concentrate enthusiasts across Canada.</p>\n<p>–</p>\n<h2>💡 Usage Guide</h2>\n<h3>Recommended Dosage</h3>\n<ul>\n<li><strong>Beginners:</strong> Start with a rice grain-sized amount (approximately 0.025g). Concentrates are extremely potent and beginners should start with smaller amounts and lower potency products first.</li>\n<li><strong>Experienced Users:</strong> 0.05-0.1g (50-100mg) per session, depending on tolerance and desired effects.</li>\n<li><strong>High Tolerance:</strong> Up to 0.2g per session for experienced concentrate consumers.</li>\n</ul>\n<h3>Consumption Methods</h3>\n<ul>\n<li><strong>Dabbing:</strong> Use a dab rig or e-nail heated to 315-400°C for optimal flavour preservation and smooth vapour production. Lower temperatures (315-350°C) preserve terpenes for enhanced flavour.</li>\n<li><strong>Vaporizing:</strong> Use a concentrate-compatible vaporizer or wax pen for portable, convenient consumption with precise temperature control.</li>\n<li><strong>Topping Flower:</strong> Add small pieces to bowls, bongs, or joints to significantly enhance potency and extend your flower’s effects.</li>\n</ul>\n<h3>Onset &amp; Duration</h3>\n<ul>\n<li><strong>Onset:</strong> Nearly immediate to 5 minutes when dabbed or vaporized.</li>\n<li><strong>Peak Effects:</strong> 10-30 minutes after consumption.</li>\n<li><strong>Duration:</strong> 1-3 hours, though effects may vary based on tolerance and dosage.</li>\n</ul>\n<h3>Best Use Cases</h3>\n<p>Drizzle Factory Shatter is ideal for experienced consumers seeking fast-acting, potent relief or recreational effects. The high THC concentration makes this perfect for those with higher tolerance levels or medical patients requiring strong symptom management. Best suited for evening use or times when you can fully relax and enjoy the experience. The smooth vapour quality makes it excellent for flavour enthusiasts who appreciate clean, terpene-rich concentrates.</p>\n<p><strong>⚠️ Important Safety Information:</strong> This concentrate contains very high THC levels (typically 70-90%+). for experienced users – beginners should start with lower doses or those new to cannabis concentrates. Start with minimal amounts and wait 10-15 minutes before consuming more. Avoid operating vehicles or heavy machinery. Store securely away from children and pets.</p>\n<h2>❓ Frequently Asked Questions</h2>\n<h3>What is Drizzle Factory Shatter and how is it made?</h3>\n<p><strong>A:</strong> Drizzle Factory Shatter is a premium cannabis concentrate with a glass-like, translucent consistency. It’s produced using solvent-based extraction methods that preserve cannabinoids and terpenes while removing plant material, resulting in a highly potent product with THC levels typically ranging from 70-90%. The “shatter” name comes from its brittle, glass-like texture that breaks cleanly when handled.</p>\n<h3>How do I use Drizzle Factory Shatter?</h3>\n<p><strong>A:</strong> Shatter is most commonly consumed by dabbing using a dab rig heated to 315-400°C. You can also use a concentrate vaporizer or wax pen for portable use. Advanced users sometimes add small pieces to flower in joints or bowls. Always start with a very small amount (rice grain-sized) as shatter is extremely potent compared to traditional flower.</p>\n<h3>How potent is Drizzle Factory Shatter compared to regular cannabis?</h3>\n<p><strong>A:</strong> Drizzle Factory Shatter is significantly more potent than cannabis flower, typically containing 70-90%+ THC compared to flower’s 15-25% THC. This means shatter is approximately 3-5 times stronger than high-grade flower. This high potency is why it’s recommended exclusively for experienced consumers with established tolerance levels.</p>\n<h3>Is Drizzle Factory Shatter safe for beginners?</h3>\n<p><strong>A:</strong> No, shatter and other concentrates are for experienced users – beginners should start with lower doses due to their extremely high THC content. If you’re new to cannabis, we recommend starting with lower-potency flower or precisely-dosed edibles to build your tolerance and understanding of cannabis effects. Experienced users transitioning to concentrates should start with minimal amounts.</p>\n<h3>How should I store my Drizzle Factory Shatter?</h3>\n<p><strong>A:</strong> Store your shatter in an airtight, non-stick silicone or glass container in a cool, dark place away from direct sunlight and heat sources. Proper storage preserves potency, flavour, and consistency. Refrigeration can help maintain texture in warmer climates, but allow it to reach room temperature before handling to prevent condensation. Properly stored shatter can maintain quality for 6-12 months.</p>\n<h3>Does Mohawk Medibles ship Drizzle Factory Shatter across Canada?</h3>\n<p><strong>A:</strong> Yes! We offer fast, discreet Canada-wide shipping on all Drizzle Factory products. Orders placed before 2 PM EST are processed the same day. All packages arrive in plain, unmarked packaging with no indication of contents, ensuring complete privacy. We use reliable courier services to ensure your concentrate arrives safely and securely.</p>\n<h3>What makes Drizzle Factory Shatter different from other concentrates?</h3>\n<p><strong>A:</strong> Drizzle Factory has earned widespread recognition for consistently high potency, exceptional purity, and smooth vapour quality. Their extraction process preserves the full spectrum of terpenes for enhanced flavour profiles, while rigorous quality control ensures a clean, residue-free product. The brand’s commitment to craft-quality concentrates at accessible prices has made them a favourite among Canadian concentrate enthusiasts.</p>\n</div>\n</div>",
