        "descriptionHTML": "<div class=\"tab-pane active\" id=\"tab-description\">\n<div class=\"detail-tab-desc detail-content-wrap\">\n<p data-end=\"848\" data-start=\"511\"><strong data-end=\"542\" data-start=\"511\">Grumpy Tiger LA Mousse Hash</strong> brings together <strong data-end=\"588\" data-start=\"559\">elite California genetics</strong>, <strong data-end=\"614\" data-start=\"590\">French Touch texture</strong>, and <strong data-end=\"639\" data-start=\"620\">serious potency</strong> in one refined concentrate. To begin with, this strain—also known as <strong data-end=\"727\" data-start=\"709\">Cowboy Cookies</strong>—is grown by Snowtill in San Francisco and is famous for its <strong data-end=\"818\" data-start=\"788\">sweet, gassy dessert aroma</strong> and <strong data-end=\"847\" data-start=\"823\">very high THC levels</strong>.</p>\n<p data-end=\"1205\" data-start=\"850\">Right away, the effects make their presence known 🧠⚡. First, the mind lifts into a calm yet energized state, easing stress while sharpening awareness. Soon after, a deeper relaxation settles in, grounding the body without knocking you out. Because of this balance, Grumpy Tiger works well for experienced users who enjoy intensity without losing control.</p>\n<p data-end=\"1534\" data-start=\"1207\">As the session continues, the experience can feel immersive and introspective 🌌. Many users describe enhanced visuals, deeper thought patterns, and a strong sense of presence. At the same time, the body stays relaxed and comfortable, making this hash ideal for late-day sessions, creative exploration, or intentional downtime.</p>\n<p data-end=\"1815\" data-start=\"1536\">Meanwhile, the flavour profile keeps things rich and indulgent 🍪⛽. Sweet cookie notes lead the way, followed closely by creamy dessert tones and a bold gassy finish. Underneath it all, subtle earthy and spicy notes round out the smoke, keeping every pull smooth and full-bodied.</p>\n<p data-end=\"2041\" data-start=\"1817\">Because this is <strong data-end=\"1851\" data-start=\"1833\">LA Mousse Hash</strong>, the texture remains <strong data-end=\"1903\" data-start=\"1873\">light, fluffy, and aerated</strong>. As a result, it’s easy to work with, melts cleanly, and delivers consistent flavour whether mixed with flower, rolled, or gently heated.</p>\n<hr data-end=\"2046\" data-start=\"2043\"/>\n<h3 data-end=\"2073\" data-start=\"2048\">✨ Effects You’ll Feel</h3>\n<ul data-end=\"2234\" data-start=\"2074\">\n<li data-end=\"2105\" data-start=\"2074\">\n<p data-end=\"2105\" data-start=\"2076\">😌 Deep calm and relaxation</p>\n</li>\n<li data-end=\"2134\" data-start=\"2106\">\n<p data-end=\"2134\" data-start=\"2108\">⚡ Balanced mental energy</p>\n</li>\n<li data-end=\"2176\" data-start=\"2135\">\n<p data-end=\"2176\" data-start=\"2137\">🌌 Introspective, immersive headspace</p>\n</li>\n<li data-end=\"2203\" data-start=\"2177\">\n<p data-end=\"2203\" data-start=\"2179\">🧘 Smooth body comfort</p>\n</li>\n<li data-end=\"2234\" data-start=\"2204\">\n<p data-end=\"2234\" data-start=\"2206\">🎯 Clear yet powerful high</p>\n</li>\n</ul>\n<hr data-end=\"2239\" data-start=\"2236\"/>\n<h3 data-end=\"2267\" data-start=\"2241\">🩺 Commonly Chosen For</h3>\n<ul data-end=\"2384\" data-start=\"2268\">\n<li data-end=\"2288\" data-start=\"2268\">\n<p data-end=\"2288\" data-start=\"2270\">Stress &amp; anxiety</p>\n</li>\n<li data-end=\"2307\" data-start=\"2289\">\n<p data-end=\"2307\" data-start=\"2291\">Mental fatigue</p>\n</li>\n<li data-end=\"2327\" data-start=\"2308\">\n<p data-end=\"2327\" data-start=\"2310\">Mood regulation</p>\n</li>\n<li data-end=\"2346\" data-start=\"2328\">\n<p data-end=\"2346\" data-start=\"2330\">Creative focus</p>\n</li>\n<li data-end=\"2384\" data-start=\"2347\">\n<p data-end=\"2384\" data-start=\"2349\">Experienced users seeking potency</p>\n</li>\n</ul>\n<hr data-end=\"2389\" data-start=\"2386\"/>\n<h3 data-end=\"2411\" data-start=\"2391\">🍪 Flavour Notes</h3>\n<ul data-end=\"2485\" data-start=\"2412\">\n<li data-end=\"2429\" data-start=\"2412\">\n<p data-end=\"2429\" data-start=\"2414\">Sweet dessert</p>\n</li>\n<li data-end=\"2446\" data-start=\"2430\">\n<p data-end=\"2446\" data-start=\"2432\">Cookie dough</p>\n</li>\n<li data-end=\"2468\" data-start=\"2447\">\n<p data-end=\"2468\" data-start=\"2449\">Creamy undertones</p>\n</li>\n<li data-end=\"2485\" data-start=\"2469\">\n<p data-end=\"2485\" data-start=\"2471\">Gassy finish</p>\n</li>\n</ul>\n<hr data-end=\"2490\" data-start=\"2487\"/>\n<h3 data-end=\"2513\" data-start=\"2492\">🌬️ Aroma Profile</h3>\n<ul data-end=\"2583\" data-start=\"2514\">\n<li data-end=\"2531\" data-start=\"2514\">\n<p data-end=\"2531\" data-start=\"2516\">Dessert-sweet</p>\n</li>\n<li data-end=\"2551\" data-start=\"2532\">\n<p data-end=\"2551\" data-start=\"2534\">Gassy &amp; pungent</p>\n</li>\n<li data-end=\"2567\" data-start=\"2552\">\n<p data-end=\"2567\" data-start=\"2554\">Earthy base</p>\n</li>\n<li data-end=\"2583\" data-start=\"2568\">\n<p data-end=\"2583\" data-start=\"2570\">Light spice</p>\n</li>\n</ul>\n<hr data-end=\"2588\" data-start=\"2585\"/>\n<h3 data-end=\"2639\" data-start=\"2590\">💎 Why Grumpy Tiger LA Mousse Hash Stands Out</h3>\n<ul data-end=\"2819\" data-start=\"2640\">\n<li data-end=\"2673\" data-start=\"2640\">\n<p data-end=\"2673\" data-start=\"2642\">Very high THC potency (≈29–33%)</p>\n</li>\n<li data-end=\"2708\" data-start=\"2674\">\n<p data-end=\"2708\" data-start=\"2676\">Premium <strong data-end=\"2708\" data-start=\"2684\">solventless dry sift</strong></p>\n</li>\n<li data-end=\"2750\" data-start=\"2709\">\n<p data-end=\"2750\" data-start=\"2711\">Light, aerated <strong data-end=\"2750\" data-start=\"2726\">French Touch texture</strong></p>\n</li>\n<li data-end=\"2783\" data-start=\"2751\">\n<p data-end=\"2783\" data-start=\"2753\">California-grown craft quality</p>\n</li>\n<li data-end=\"2819\" data-start=\"2784\">\n<p data-end=\"2819\" data-start=\"2786\">Ideal for experienced hash lovers</p>\n</li>\n</ul>\n<hr/>\n<h2>💡 Usage Guide</h2>\n<h3>Recommended Dosage</h3>\n<ul>\n<li><strong>Beginners:</strong> Start with a rice grain-sized piece (approximately 0.025-0.05g). Hash is significantly more potent than flower.</li>\n<li><strong>Experienced Users:</strong> 0.1-0.2g per session, adjusting based on tolerance and desired effects.</li>\n<li><strong>High Tolerance:</strong> Up to 0.3g per session for seasoned concentrate consumers.</li>\n</ul>\n<h3>Consumption Methods</h3>\n<ul>\n<li><strong>Smoking:</strong> Crumble and mix with flower in joints, pipes, or bongs for enhanced potency and traditional experience.</li>\n<li><strong>Vaporizing:</strong> Use hash-compatible vaporizer at 180-210°C for smooth, flavourful vapour with maximum terpene preservation.</li>\n<li><strong>Hot Knives:</strong> Traditional method heating two knives and pressing hash between them for immediate effects.</li>\n<li><strong>Topping Bowls:</strong> Add small pieces atop flower bowls for elevated potency without altering your regular routine.</li>\n<li><strong>Hash Edibles (Advanced):</strong> To make edibles, decarboxylate hash at 110-120°C (230-250°F) for 30-40 minutes to activate THC. Mix into butter or oil-based recipes. Effects take 30-120 minutes and last 6-12 hours. Hash edibles are significantly more potent than flower edibles—start with 1/4 of your normal flower edible dose.</li>\n</ul>\n<h3>Onset &amp; Duration</h3>\n<ul>\n<li><strong>Onset (Smoking/Vaping):</strong> 2-10 minutes</li>\n<li><strong>Onset (Edibles):</strong> 30-120 minutes</li>\n<li><strong>Peak Effects:</strong> 15-45 minutes (inhaled) or 2-4 hours (edibles)</li>\n<li><strong>Duration:</strong> 2-4 hours (inhaled) or 6-12 hours (edibles)</li>\n</ul>\n<p><strong>⚠️ Important:</strong> Hash is significantly more potent than regular flower. Start with minimal amounts and wait to assess effects before consuming more. for experienced users – beginners should start with lower doses or those new to concentrates.</p>\n</div>\n</div>",
