        "descriptionHTML": "<div class=\"tab-pane active\" id=\"tab-description\">\n<div class=\"detail-tab-desc detail-content-wrap\">\n<p>**Buy Do-Si-Dos 24k Full Melt Hash online in Canada at Mohawk Medibles**, your trusted Indigenous-owned cannabis dispensary. Shop this premium full spectrum hash with an impressive 75-80% THC concentration and enjoy fast Canada-wide shipping with same-day processing. Order now for discreet delivery of this exceptional concentrate sourced from Tyendinaga Mohawk Territory. Experience the pinnacle of hash craftsmanship with our 24k Full Melt collection.</p>\n<h2>🧬 Strain Profile</h2>\n<h3>Genetics &amp; Lineage</h3>\n<p>Do-Si-Dos is a premium indica-dominant hybrid born from the legendary Girl Scout Cookies lineage, created by crossing Face Off OG with OG Kush Breath (OGKB). This exceptional genetic background delivers a complex cannabinoid and terpene profile that translates beautifully into full melt hash form. The 24k Full Melt extraction process preserves the strain’s natural characteristics while concentrating its potency to 75-80% THC.</p>\n<h3>Dominant Terpenes</h3>\n<ul>\n<li><strong>Caryophyllene:</strong> Provides spicy, peppery notes and potential anti-inflammatory properties</li>\n<li><strong>Limonene:</strong> Contributes bright citrus aromas and uplifting effects</li>\n<li><strong>Linalool:</strong> Delivers floral, lavender-like notes with calming qualities</li>\n</ul>\n<h3>Cannabinoid Profile</h3>\n<p>This full spectrum hash contains 75-80% THC, representing one of the most potent concentrations available. The full melt extraction preserves the complete cannabinoid spectrum, including minor cannabinoids and terpenes that work synergistically through the entourage effect. This is a highly concentrated product suitable for experienced consumers only.</p>\n<h3>Appearance &amp; Structure</h3>\n<p>24k Full Melt Hash features a rich, golden-amber appearance with a soft, pliable texture that melts cleanly when heated. The “full melt” designation indicates premium quality that vaporizes completely without leaving residue, a hallmark of solventless extraction excellence. The hash exhibits a sticky, resinous consistency that speaks to its high trichome content.</p>\n<h3>Similar Strains</h3>\n<p>If you enjoy Do-Si-Dos 24k Full Melt Hash, consider exploring Wedding Cake hash, Gelato concentrates, or other Girl Scout Cookies family extracts for comparable flavour profiles and potent indica-dominant effects.</p>\n<p>–</p>\n<h2>💡 Usage Guide</h2>\n<h3>Recommended Dosage</h3>\n<ul>\n<li><strong>Beginners:</strong> Start with a tiny piece (0.02-0.05g) and wait 10-15 minutes between hits</li>\n<li><strong>Experienced Users:</strong> Start with a rice grain-sized amount (0.025-0.05g)</li>\n<li><strong>High Tolerance:</strong> 0.05-0.1g per session, adjust based on experience</li>\n</ul>\n<h3>Consumption Methods</h3>\n<ul>\n<li><strong>Dabbing:</strong> Use a dab rig or e-nail at 315-370°C for optimal flavour and full melt characteristics</li>\n<li><strong>Vaporizing:</strong> Use a concentrate-compatible vaporizer designed for hash and extracts</li>\n<li><strong>Topping Flower:</strong> Add small amounts to bowls or joints for significantly enhanced potency</li>\n<li><strong>Hot Knifing:</strong> Traditional method using heated metal surfaces (experienced users only)</li>\n<li><strong>Hash Edibles (Advanced):</strong> To make edibles, decarboxylate hash at 110-120°C (230-250°F) for 30-40 minutes to activate THC. Mix into butter or oil-based recipes. Effects take 30-120 minutes and last 6-12 hours. Hash edibles are significantly more potent than flower edibles—start with 1/4 of your normal flower edible dose.</li>\n</ul>\n<h3>Onset &amp; Duration</h3>\n<ul>\n<li><strong>Onset:</strong> Immediate to 5 minutes</li>\n<li><strong>Peak Effects:</strong> 15-45 minutes</li>\n<li><strong>Duration:</strong> 2-4 hours depending on dosage and tolerance</li>\n</ul>\n<h3>Best Use Cases</h3>\n<p>Ideal for evening relaxation, deep meditation, or managing discomfort. The indica-dominant effects make this perfect for unwinding after a long day or preparing for restful sleep. Best consumed when you have no obligations and can fully appreciate the potent, long-lasting effects.</p>\n<p><strong>⚠️ Important Safety Information:</strong> This is an extremely potent concentrate containing 75-80% THC. Not suitable for beginners or those with low tolerance. Start with minimal amounts and wait 15-20 minutes before consuming more. Do not drive or operate machinery after use. Keep out of reach of children and pets.</p>\n<h2>❓ Frequently Asked Questions</h2>\n<h3>What is full melt hash and how is it different from regular hash?</h3>\n<p><strong>A:</strong> Full melt hash is the highest grade of solventless concentrate, named for its ability to melt completely when heated without leaving residue. Unlike traditional pressed hash, full melt is made from pure trichome heads (typically 5-star or 6-star rated), resulting in superior flavour, potency, and purity. This 24k Full Melt contains 75-80% THC compared to 20-40% in traditional hash.</p>\n<h3>How potent is Do-Si-Dos 24k Full Melt Hash?</h3>\n<p><strong>A:</strong> With 75-80% THC, this is an extremely potent concentrate recommended for experienced consumers only. It’s approximately 3-4 times stronger than premium cannabis flower and delivers immediate, powerful effects. Always start with a very small amount if you’re new to concentrates.</p>\n<h3>What’s the best way to consume this full melt hash?</h3>\n<p><strong>A:</strong> Dabbing at 315-370°C provides the optimal experience, preserving the full spectrum terpene profile while ensuring complete vaporization. You can also use a concentrate vaporizer or add small amounts to flower. Avoid combustion methods as they don’t fully utilize the “full melt” characteristics.</p>\n<h3>Is Do-Si-Dos hash suitable for beginners?</h3>\n<p><strong>A:</strong> No, this concentrate is for experienced users – beginners should start with lower doses due to its extremely high THC content (75-80%). We suggest starting with cannabis flower (15-25% THC) or low-dose edibles before progressing to concentrates. If you’re experienced with concentrates, start with a rice grain-sized amount.</p>\n<h3>How should I store Do-Si-Dos 24k Full Melt Hash?</h3>\n<p><strong>A:</strong> Store in an airtight silicone or glass container in a cool, dark place away from heat and direct sunlight. Refrigeration can help maintain consistency and preserve terpenes. Properly stored, full melt hash maintains potency and quality for 6-12 months. Always handle with clean tools to avoid contamination.</p>\n<h3>Does Mohawk Medibles ship Do-Si-Dos hash across Canada?</h3>\n<p><strong>A:</strong> Yes! We offer fast, discreet Canada-wide shipping with same-day processing on orders placed before 2 PM EST. All packages arrive in plain, unmarked packaging with secure, temperature-appropriate materials to ensure your hash arrives in perfect condition.</p>\n<h3>What effects can I expect from Do-Si-Dos full melt hash?</h3>\n<p><strong>A:</strong> As an indica-dominant concentrate, expect powerful full-body relaxation, deep mental calm, and potential sedative effects at higher doses. Users report stress relief, physical comfort, and strong euphoria. The high THC content delivers fast-acting, long-lasting effects ideal for evening use or experienced consumers seeking potent relief.</p>\n</div>\n</div>",
