        "descriptionHTML": "<div class=\"tab-pane active\" id=\"tab-description\">\n<div class=\"detail-tab-desc detail-content-wrap\">\n<p data-end=\"693\" data-start=\"446\">Chara Temple Coins Hash represents one of the <strong data-end=\"540\" data-start=\"492\">purest and most traditional forms of hashish</strong> still available today 🌄. Crafted using <strong data-end=\"606\" data-start=\"581\">fresh cannabis plants</strong>, this hash follows time-honoured Himalayan techniques passed down through generations.</p>\n<p data-end=\"995\" data-start=\"695\">To begin with, artisans gently hand-roll fresh resin into <strong data-end=\"783\" data-start=\"753\">compact coin-shaped pieces</strong>. Because the resin is never dried before processing, the final result stays <strong data-end=\"912\" data-start=\"860\">soft, sticky, and extremely rich in cannabinoids</strong>. As a result, Chara Temple Coins retain an unmatched depth of flavour and potency.</p>\n<p data-end=\"1399\" data-start=\"997\">Once heated, the experience unfolds smoothly. First, bold earthy notes appear. Shortly after, hints of spice and pine come through, followed by a subtle citrus finish. Meanwhile, the effects settle into the body, delivering <strong data-end=\"1249\" data-start=\"1221\">deep physical relaxation</strong> while keeping the mind <strong data-end=\"1291\" data-start=\"1273\">clear and calm</strong>. With THC levels ranging from <strong data-end=\"1336\" data-start=\"1322\">55% to 80%</strong>, even small amounts provide powerful, long-lasting results 🔥.</p>\n<p data-end=\"1551\" data-start=\"1401\">For this reason, Chara Temple Coins are best enjoyed by <strong data-end=\"1478\" data-start=\"1457\">experienced users</strong> who appreciate authentic hash with strong effects and cultural heritage.</p>\n<hr data-end=\"1556\" data-start=\"1553\"/>\n<h3 data-end=\"1586\" data-start=\"1558\">✨ Effects You Can Expect</h3>\n<ul data-end=\"1708\" data-start=\"1587\">\n<li data-end=\"1614\" data-start=\"1587\">\n<p data-end=\"1614\" data-start=\"1589\">😌 Deep body relaxation</p>\n</li>\n<li data-end=\"1641\" data-start=\"1615\">\n<p data-end=\"1641\" data-start=\"1617\">🧠 Calm mental clarity</p>\n</li>\n<li data-end=\"1676\" data-start=\"1642\">\n<p data-end=\"1676\" data-start=\"1644\">🌙 Long-lasting, soothing high</p>\n</li>\n<li data-end=\"1708\" data-start=\"1677\">\n<p data-end=\"1708\" data-start=\"1679\">🧘 Grounded, peaceful state</p>\n</li>\n</ul>\n<hr data-end=\"1713\" data-start=\"1710\"/>\n<h3 data-end=\"1735\" data-start=\"1715\">🩺 May Help With</h3>\n<ul data-end=\"1823\" data-start=\"1736\">\n<li data-end=\"1752\" data-start=\"1736\">\n<p data-end=\"1752\" data-start=\"1738\">Chronic pain</p>\n</li>\n<li data-end=\"1773\" data-start=\"1753\">\n<p data-end=\"1773\" data-start=\"1755\">Stress &amp; anxiety</p>\n</li>\n<li data-end=\"1786\" data-start=\"1774\">\n<p data-end=\"1786\" data-start=\"1776\">Insomnia</p>\n</li>\n<li data-end=\"1805\" data-start=\"1787\">\n<p data-end=\"1805\" data-start=\"1789\">Muscle tension</p>\n</li>\n<li data-end=\"1823\" data-start=\"1806\">\n<p data-end=\"1823\" data-start=\"1808\">Appetite loss</p>\n</li>\n</ul>\n<hr data-end=\"1828\" data-start=\"1825\"/>\n<h3 data-end=\"1852\" data-start=\"1830\">🌿 Flavour Profile</h3>\n<ul data-end=\"1899\" data-start=\"1853\">\n<li data-end=\"1863\" data-start=\"1853\">\n<p data-end=\"1863\" data-start=\"1855\">Earthy</p>\n</li>\n<li data-end=\"1873\" data-start=\"1864\">\n<p data-end=\"1873\" data-start=\"1866\">Spicy</p>\n</li>\n<li data-end=\"1882\" data-start=\"1874\">\n<p data-end=\"1882\" data-start=\"1876\">Pine</p>\n</li>\n<li data-end=\"1899\" data-start=\"1883\">\n<p data-end=\"1899\" data-start=\"1885\">Light citrus</p>\n</li>\n</ul>\n<hr data-end=\"1904\" data-start=\"1901\"/>\n<h3 data-end=\"1919\" data-start=\"1906\">🌬️ Aroma</h3>\n<ul data-end=\"1968\" data-start=\"1920\">\n<li data-end=\"1935\" data-start=\"1920\">\n<p data-end=\"1935\" data-start=\"1922\">Fresh resin</p>\n</li>\n<li data-end=\"1952\" data-start=\"1936\">\n<p data-end=\"1952\" data-start=\"1938\">Earthy spice</p>\n</li>\n<li data-end=\"1968\" data-start=\"1953\">\n<p data-end=\"1968\" data-start=\"1955\">Herbal pine</p>\n</li>\n</ul>\n<hr data-end=\"1973\" data-start=\"1970\"/>\n<h3 data-end=\"1994\" data-start=\"1975\">🔥 How to Enjoy</h3>\n<ul data-end=\"2132\" data-start=\"1995\">\n<li data-end=\"2043\" data-start=\"1995\">\n<p data-end=\"2043\" data-start=\"1997\">Smoke or vaporize for smooth, potent effects</p>\n</li>\n<li data-end=\"2088\" data-start=\"2044\">\n<p data-end=\"2088\" data-start=\"2046\">Add to flower for an enhanced experience</p>\n</li>\n<li data-end=\"2132\" data-start=\"2089\">\n<p data-end=\"2132\" data-start=\"2091\">Ideal for evening or wind-down sessions</p>\n</li>\n</ul>\n</div>\n</div>",
