        "descriptionHTML": "<div class=\"tab-pane active\" id=\"tab-description\">\n<div class=\"detail-tab-desc detail-content-wrap\">\n<p>**Buy Slim Shady’s Pre-Rolls online in Canada at Mohawk Medibles**, your trusted Indigenous-owned cannabis dispensary. Shop this premium Fire House Blend and enjoy the convenience of 10 expertly rolled pre-rolls per pack, delivering +25% THC potency with every session. Order now for fast Canada-wide shipping, same-day processing, and discreet delivery straight from Tyendinaga Mohawk Territory. Perfect for sharing with friends or stocking up for personal use.</p>\n<h2>🧬 Strain Profile</h2>\n<h3>Genetics &amp; Lineage</h3>\n<p>Slim Shady’s Pre-Rolls feature our signature Fire House Blend, a carefully curated combination of premium cannabis strains selected for consistent potency and exceptional flavour profiles. This proprietary blend brings together complementary genetics to deliver a well-rounded experience that satisfies both recreational and experienced consumers.</p>\n<h3>Cannabinoid Profile</h3>\n<ul>\n<li><strong>THC Content:</strong> +25% (high potency)</li>\n<li><strong>CBD Content:</strong> &lt;1%</li>\n<li><strong>Potency Level:</strong> Strong – recommended for experienced users</li>\n</ul>\n<h3>Appearance &amp; Quality</h3>\n<p>Each pre-roll is expertly crafted using quality flower, ensuring an even burn and smooth draw. Our Fire House Blend showcases vibrant green hues with visible trichome coverage, rolled to perfection in premium papers. Each pack contains 10 consistently sized pre-rolls, professionally sealed for freshness.</p>\n<h3>Why Choose Pre-Rolls?</h3>\n<p>Pre-rolls offer ultimate convenience for cannabis consumers who want quality without the hassle of grinding and rolling. Slim Shady’s Pre-Rolls are perfect for on-the-go sessions, social gatherings, or when you simply want a ready-to-enjoy experience. With 100 pre-rolls per case (10 packs), this bulk option provides exceptional value for regular consumers.</p>\n<p>–</p>\n<h2>💡 Usage Guide</h2>\n<h3>Recommended Dosage</h3>\n<ul>\n<li><strong>Beginners:</strong> Due to +25% THC content, start with 2-3 small puffs and wait 10-15 minutes to assess effects</li>\n<li><strong>Experienced Users:</strong> Enjoy half to one full pre-roll per session</li>\n<li><strong>High Tolerance:</strong> One to two pre-rolls as desired</li>\n</ul>\n<h3>Consumption Methods</h3>\n<ul>\n<li><strong>Direct Smoking:</strong> Light the pre-roll and inhale gently for immediate effects. Each pre-roll is designed for optimal airflow and even burning</li>\n<li><strong>Sharing:</strong> Perfect size for passing around in social settings – one pre-roll typically serves 2-3 people</li>\n<li><strong>Partial Consumption:</strong> Extinguish carefully and save the remainder for later use</li>\n</ul>\n<h3>Onset &amp; Duration</h3>\n<ul>\n<li><strong>Onset:</strong> 2-10 minutes after first inhalation</li>\n<li><strong>Peak Effects:</strong> 30-60 minutes</li>\n<li><strong>Duration:</strong> 2-4 hours depending on tolerance and amount consumed</li>\n</ul>\n<h3>Best Use Cases</h3>\n<p>Slim Shady’s Pre-Rolls are ideal for experienced consumers seeking convenient, potent sessions. Perfect for social gatherings, outdoor activities, concerts, or relaxing evenings. The high THC content makes these pre-rolls excellent for users with established tolerance who want reliable, strong effects without preparation time.</p>\n<p><strong>⚠️ Safety Reminder:</strong> With +25% THC, these pre-rolls are potent. Start slow if you’re unfamiliar with high-THC products. Do not operate vehicles or machinery after consumption. Store securely away from children and pets.</p>\n<h2>❓ Frequently Asked Questions</h2>\n<h3>How strong are Slim Shady’s Pre-Rolls?</h3>\n<p><strong>A:</strong> With +25% THC content, these pre-rolls are considered high potency and are best suited for experienced cannabis consumers. If you’re new to pre-rolls or have lower tolerance, start with just a few puffs and wait to assess the effects before consuming more.</p>\n<h3>How many pre-rolls come in each pack?</h3>\n<p><strong>A:</strong> Each pack contains 10 pre-rolls, and each case contains 10 packs for a total of 100 pre-rolls. This bulk format offers excellent value for regular consumers or those looking to stock up.</p>\n<h3>What is the Fire House Blend?</h3>\n<p><strong>A:</strong> Fire House Blend is our signature proprietary mix of premium cannabis strains, carefully selected and blended for consistent potency, flavour, and effects. This curated combination ensures you get a reliable, high-quality experience with every pre-roll.</p>\n<h3>How should I store Slim Shady’s Pre-Rolls?</h3>\n<p><strong>A:</strong> Keep your pre-rolls in their original packaging in a cool, dry place away from direct sunlight and heat. An airtight container in a dark cupboard works perfectly. Proper storage maintains freshness and potency for several months. Always store out of reach of children and pets.</p>\n<h3>Are these pre-rolls good for beginners?</h3>\n<p><strong>A:</strong> Due to the high THC content (+25%), these pre-rolls are recommended for experienced users. Beginners should consider starting with lower-potency options or consume very small amounts (2-3 puffs) and wait at least 15 minutes before deciding to consume more.</p>\n<h3>Does Mohawk Medibles ship Slim Shady’s Pre-Rolls across Canada?</h3>\n<p><strong>A:</strong> Yes! We offer fast, discreet Canada-wide shipping with same-day processing on orders placed before 2 PM EST. All packages arrive in plain, unmarked packaging to ensure your privacy. Track your order from Tyendinaga Mohawk Territory right to your door.</p>\n<h3>Can I buy individual packs or do I need to order a full case?</h3>\n<p><strong>A:</strong> You can purchase Slim Shady’s Pre-Rolls by the individual pack (10 pre-rolls) or save more by ordering a full case (100 pre-rolls). Check our product options for current pricing and availability on both single packs and bulk cases.</p>\n</div>\n</div>",
