        "descriptionHTML": "<div class=\"tab-pane active\" id=\"tab-description\">\n<div class=\"detail-tab-desc detail-content-wrap\">\n<p data-end=\"859\" data-start=\"533\"><strong data-end=\"566\" data-start=\"533\">Banana Sherbet LA Mousse Hash</strong> blends <strong data-end=\"596\" data-start=\"574\">tropical sweetness</strong>, <strong data-end=\"617\" data-start=\"598\">creative energy</strong>, and <strong data-end=\"660\" data-start=\"623\">premium solventless craftsmanship</strong> into one standout concentrate. To start, this balanced hybrid comes from the flavorful cross of <strong data-end=\"789\" data-start=\"757\">Sunset Sherbet × Banana Kush</strong>, a pairing celebrated for terpene richness and mood-boosting effects.</p>\n<p data-end=\"1232\" data-start=\"861\">Right away, the experience opens with a bright mental lift 🧠⚡. Almost immediately, mood rises, stress fades, and creative thoughts begin to flow. Soon after, a sociable energy takes over, making conversation easier and ideas more fluid. Because of this balance, Banana Sherbet is a favorite among artists, creators, and anyone chasing inspiration without heavy sedation.</p>\n<p data-end=\"1529\" data-start=\"1234\">As the session continues, a gentle body calm settles in 😌. Instead of couch-lock, the body stays light and comfortable, allowing you to stay engaged while still relaxed. As a result, this hash works beautifully for daytime or early evening use when you want to feel good, focused, and uplifted.</p>\n<p data-end=\"1779\" data-start=\"1531\">Meanwhile, the flavour steals the spotlight 🍌🍧. Sweet banana hits first, followed by creamy sherbet notes and soft fruity undertones. Subtle earthiness and light spice round out the profile, keeping each pull smooth, rich, and never overpowering.</p>\n<p data-end=\"2006\" data-start=\"1781\">Because this is <strong data-end=\"1815\" data-start=\"1797\">LA Mousse Hash</strong>, the texture remains <strong data-end=\"1867\" data-start=\"1837\">light, fluffy, and aerated</strong>. As a result, it’s easy to handle, melts cleanly, and delivers consistent flavour whether sprinkled into flower, rolled, or gently heated.</p>\n<hr data-end=\"2011\" data-start=\"2008\"/>\n<h3 data-end=\"2038\" data-start=\"2013\">✨ Effects You’ll Feel</h3>\n<ul data-end=\"2179\" data-start=\"2039\">\n<li data-end=\"2064\" data-start=\"2039\">\n<p data-end=\"2064\" data-start=\"2041\">😄 Euphoric and happy</p>\n</li>\n<li data-end=\"2093\" data-start=\"2065\">\n<p data-end=\"2093\" data-start=\"2067\">🎨 Creative and inspired</p>\n</li>\n<li data-end=\"2121\" data-start=\"2094\">\n<p data-end=\"2121\" data-start=\"2096\">🗣️ Sociable and upbeat</p>\n</li>\n<li data-end=\"2147\" data-start=\"2122\">\n<p data-end=\"2147\" data-start=\"2124\">⚡ Light mental energy</p>\n</li>\n<li data-end=\"2179\" data-start=\"2148\">\n<p data-end=\"2179\" data-start=\"2150\">😌 Calm, balanced body feel</p>\n</li>\n</ul>\n<hr data-end=\"2184\" data-start=\"2181\"/>\n<h3 data-end=\"2212\" data-start=\"2186\">🩺 Commonly Chosen For</h3>\n<ul data-end=\"2302\" data-start=\"2213\">\n<li data-end=\"2231\" data-start=\"2213\">\n<p data-end=\"2231\" data-start=\"2215\">Chronic stress</p>\n</li>\n<li data-end=\"2246\" data-start=\"2232\">\n<p data-end=\"2246\" data-start=\"2234\">Depression</p>\n</li>\n<li data-end=\"2262\" data-start=\"2247\">\n<p data-end=\"2262\" data-start=\"2249\">Mood swings</p>\n</li>\n<li data-end=\"2283\" data-start=\"2263\">\n<p data-end=\"2283\" data-start=\"2265\">Creative fatigue</p>\n</li>\n<li data-end=\"2302\" data-start=\"2284\">\n<p data-end=\"2302\" data-start=\"2286\">Mental burnout</p>\n</li>\n</ul>\n<hr data-end=\"2307\" data-start=\"2304\"/>\n<h3 data-end=\"2329\" data-start=\"2309\">🍌 Flavour Notes</h3>\n<ul data-end=\"2398\" data-start=\"2330\">\n<li data-end=\"2346\" data-start=\"2330\">\n<p data-end=\"2346\" data-start=\"2332\">Sweet banana</p>\n</li>\n<li data-end=\"2365\" data-start=\"2347\">\n<p data-end=\"2365\" data-start=\"2349\">Creamy sherbet</p>\n</li>\n<li data-end=\"2382\" data-start=\"2366\">\n<p data-end=\"2382\" data-start=\"2368\">Fruity candy</p>\n</li>\n<li data-end=\"2398\" data-start=\"2383\">\n<p data-end=\"2398\" data-start=\"2385\">Light earth</p>\n</li>\n</ul>\n<hr data-end=\"2403\" data-start=\"2400\"/>\n<h3 data-end=\"2426\" data-start=\"2405\">🌬️ Aroma Profile</h3>\n<ul data-end=\"2494\" data-start=\"2427\">\n<li data-end=\"2447\" data-start=\"2427\">\n<p data-end=\"2447\" data-start=\"2429\">Fruity and sweet</p>\n</li>\n<li data-end=\"2468\" data-start=\"2448\">\n<p data-end=\"2468\" data-start=\"2450\">Tropical dessert</p>\n</li>\n<li data-end=\"2494\" data-start=\"2469\">\n<p data-end=\"2494\" data-start=\"2471\">Soft earthy undertone</p>\n</li>\n</ul>\n<hr data-end=\"2499\" data-start=\"2496\"/>\n<h3 data-end=\"2552\" data-start=\"2501\">💎 Why Banana Sherbet LA Mousse Hash Stands Out</h3>\n<ul data-end=\"2740\" data-start=\"2553\">\n<li data-end=\"2588\" data-start=\"2553\">\n<p data-end=\"2588\" data-start=\"2555\"><strong data-end=\"2569\" data-start=\"2555\">20–23% THC</strong> balanced potency</p>\n</li>\n<li data-end=\"2623\" data-start=\"2589\">\n<p data-end=\"2623\" data-start=\"2591\">Premium <strong data-end=\"2623\" data-start=\"2599\">solventless dry sift</strong></p>\n</li>\n<li data-end=\"2665\" data-start=\"2624\">\n<p data-end=\"2665\" data-start=\"2626\">Light, aerated <strong data-end=\"2665\" data-start=\"2641\">French Touch texture</strong></p>\n</li>\n<li data-end=\"2697\" data-start=\"2666\">\n<p data-end=\"2697\" data-start=\"2668\">Dessert-style terpene profile</p>\n</li>\n<li data-end=\"2740\" data-start=\"2698\">\n<p data-end=\"2740\" data-start=\"2700\">Ideal for creativity and social sessions</p>\n</li>\n</ul>\n<hr/>\n<h2>💡 Usage Guide</h2>\n<h3>Recommended Dosage</h3>\n<ul>\n<li><strong>Beginners:</strong> Start with a rice grain-sized piece (approximately 0.025-0.05g). Hash is significantly more potent than flower.</li>\n<li><strong>Experienced Users:</strong> 0.1-0.2g per session, adjusting based on tolerance and desired effects.</li>\n<li><strong>High Tolerance:</strong> Up to 0.3g per session for seasoned concentrate consumers.</li>\n</ul>\n<h3>Consumption Methods</h3>\n<ul>\n<li><strong>Smoking:</strong> Crumble and mix with flower in joints, pipes, or bongs for enhanced potency and traditional experience.</li>\n<li><strong>Vaporizing:</strong> Use hash-compatible vaporizer at 180-210°C for smooth, flavourful vapour with maximum terpene preservation.</li>\n<li><strong>Hot Knives:</strong> Traditional method heating two knives and pressing hash between them for immediate effects.</li>\n<li><strong>Topping Bowls:</strong> Add small pieces atop flower bowls for elevated potency without altering your regular routine.</li>\n<li><strong>Hash Edibles (Advanced):</strong> To make edibles, decarboxylate hash at 110-120°C (230-250°F) for 30-40 minutes to activate THC. Mix into butter or oil-based recipes. Effects take 30-120 minutes and last 6-12 hours. Hash edibles are significantly more potent than flower edibles—start with 1/4 of your normal flower edible dose.</li>\n</ul>\n<h3>Onset &amp; Duration</h3>\n<ul>\n<li><strong>Onset (Smoking/Vaping):</strong> 2-10 minutes</li>\n<li><strong>Onset (Edibles):</strong> 30-120 minutes</li>\n<li><strong>Peak Effects:</strong> 15-45 minutes (inhaled) or 2-4 hours (edibles)</li>\n<li><strong>Duration:</strong> 2-4 hours (inhaled) or 6-12 hours (edibles)</li>\n</ul>\n<p><strong>⚠️ Important:</strong> Hash is significantly more potent than regular flower. Start with minimal amounts and wait to assess effects before consuming more. for experienced users – beginners should start with lower doses or those new to concentrates.</p>\n</div>\n</div>",
