        "descriptionHTML": "<div class=\"tab-pane active\" id=\"tab-description\">\n<div class=\"detail-tab-desc detail-content-wrap\">\n<p>**Buy Wesley THC Wintergreen Mints online in Canada at Mohawk Medibles**, your trusted Indigenous-owned cannabis dispensary. Shop these discreet, refreshing cannabis mints and enjoy fast Canada-wide shipping with same-day processing. Order now for convenient microdosing or on-the-go relief, delivered discreetly from Tyendinaga Mohawk Territory. Perfect for experienced consumers seeking a portable, breath-freshening cannabis experience.</p>\n<p>–</p>\n<h2>💡 Usage Guide</h2>\n<h3>Recommended Dosage</h3>\n<ul>\n<li><strong>Beginners:</strong> Start with half a mint (2.5mg THC) and wait at least 2 hours before consuming more</li>\n<li><strong>Experienced Users:</strong> 1-2 mints (5-10mg THC) per serving, adjusting based on tolerance</li>\n<li><strong>High Tolerance:</strong> 2-4 mints (10-20mg THC) for desired effects</li>\n</ul>\n<h3>Consumption Tips</h3>\n<ul>\n<li><strong>Discreet Use:</strong> Mints look and smell like regular breath mints, perfect for public settings</li>\n<li><strong>Allow to Dissolve:</strong> Let mint dissolve slowly in mouth for optimal sublingual absorption</li>\n<li><strong>Start Low, Go Slow:</strong> Edibles can take 30-90 minutes to take effect; be patient</li>\n<li><strong>Stay Hydrated:</strong> Drink water throughout your experience to enhance comfort</li>\n<li><strong>Store Properly:</strong> Keep in original container away from heat to maintain potency</li>\n</ul>\n<h3>Onset &amp; Duration</h3>\n<ul>\n<li><strong>Onset:</strong> 30-90 minutes (faster if allowed to dissolve sublingually)</li>\n<li><strong>Peak Effects:</strong> 2-3 hours after consumption</li>\n<li><strong>Duration:</strong> 4-6 hours total, depending on dosage and metabolism</li>\n</ul>\n<h3>Best Use Cases</h3>\n<p>Ideal for discreet microdosing throughout the day or convenient relief on-the-go. The refreshing wintergreen flavour freshens breath while delivering consistent, measured doses. Perfect for social situations, outdoor activities, or anytime you need portable cannabis without drawing attention. Not recommended before driving or operating machinery.</p>\n<h2>❓ Frequently Asked Questions</h2>\n<h3>How many mg of THC are in each Wesley Wintergreen Mint?</h3>\n<p><strong>A:</strong> Each mint contains 5mg of THC. Packages are available in multiple sizes, allowing you to choose the quantity that suits your needs. Always check the label for total package THC content and number of mints included.</p>\n<h3>How long do Wesley THC Wintergreen Mints take to work?</h3>\n<p><strong>A:</strong> These mints typically take 30-90 minutes to take full effect. If you allow the mint to dissolve slowly in your mouth (sublingual absorption), you may feel effects slightly faster than swallowing immediately. Always wait at least 2 hours before consuming more.</p>\n<h3>Can I use Wesley Mints in public without anyone knowing?</h3>\n<p><strong>A:</strong> Yes! Wesley THC Wintergreen Mints are designed for discreet consumption. They look, smell, and taste like regular breath mints, with no cannabis odour. However, always consume responsibly and be aware of your surroundings and local regulations.</p>\n<h3>Are Wesley THC Mints suitable for beginners?</h3>\n<p><strong>A:</strong> These mints can work for beginners if dosed carefully. Start with half a mint (2.5mg THC) if you’re new to edibles, and wait at least 2 hours before considering more. The convenient format makes it easy to control your dose, but patience is essential with all cannabis edibles.</p>\n<h3>How should I store Wesley Wintergreen Mints?</h3>\n<p><strong>A:</strong> Store in the original container in a cool, dry place away from direct sunlight and heat. Keep the container tightly sealed to maintain freshness and potency. Always store out of reach of children and pets. Properly stored, these mints will maintain their quality for several months.</p>\n<h3>Does Mohawk Medibles ship Wesley Mints across Canada?</h3>\n<p><strong>A:</strong> Yes! We offer fast, discreet Canada-wide shipping on all Wesley THC Wintergreen Mints with same-day processing on orders placed before 2 PM EST. All packages arrive in plain, unmarked packaging to ensure your privacy.</p>\n<h3>What’s the difference between the 5mg and 10mg options?</h3>\n<p><strong>A:</strong> The 5mg option contains individual mints with 5mg THC each, ideal for precise microdosing and beginners. The 10mg option (if available) contains mints with 10mg THC each, better suited for experienced users with higher tolerance. Choose based on your experience level and desired effects.</p>\n</div>\n</div>",
